d. You get full compliance and reliability without the integration pain.\"},\"compliant\":{\"title\":\"We Handle the Hard Parts\",\"description\":\"Rate limits, token refresh, media processing, error handling - all managed for you. Focus on your product, not infrastructure.\"}}},\"howItWorks\":{\"title\":\"Three Steps to Instagram Automation\",\"steps\":{\"connect\":{\"title\":\"Connect Your Account\",\"description\":\"Link your Instagram Business account through our dashboard. One-click OAuth - we handle all the Meta permissions.\",\"warning\":\"Important: Only Business accounts supported. Personal/Creator accounts will be rejected during connection.\"},\"schedule\":{\"title\":\"Build Your Integration\",\"description\":\"Use our simple REST API to schedule posts, stories, reels, or carousels. Same pattern works for all 15 platforms.\"},\"publish\":{\"title\":\"We Handle the Rest\",\"description\":\"Zernio publishes at your scheduled time, retries on failures, and notifies you via webhooks. You never touch Instagram's API directly.\"}}},\"codeExample\":{\"title\":\"Get Started in 30 Seconds\",\"snippetTitle\":\"Schedule an Instagram Post\",\"language\":\"JavaScript\",\"snippet\":\"const response = await fetch('https://zernio.com/api/v1/posts', {\\n  method: 'POST',\\n  headers: {\\n    'Authorization': 'Bearer YOUR_API_KEY',\\n    'Content-Type': 'application/json'\\n  },\\n  body: JSON.stringify({\\n    platforms: [{\\n      platform: 'instagram',\\n      accountId: 'your-instagram-account-id'\\n    }],\\n    content: 'Beautiful sunset at the beach! 🌅 #sunset #photography',\\n    mediaItems: [{\\n      type: 'image',\\n      url: 'https://your-image-url.jpg'\\n    }],\\n    scheduledFor: '2024-01-15T19:00:00Z'\\n  })\\n});\\n\\nconst result = await response.json();\\nconsole.log('Scheduled successfully:', result.id);\"},\"contentTypes\":{\"title\":\"Every Instagram Format Supported\",\"items\":{\"photos\":{\"label\":\"Photos\",\"description\":\"JPEG, PNG, WebP. Auto-optimized.\"},\"videos\":{\"label\":\"Videos\",\"description\":\"MP4 up to 60 min. Any aspect ratio.\"},\"stories\":{\"label\":\"Stories\",\"description\":\"24-hour visibility. Full-screen format.\"},\"carousels\":{\"label\":\"Carousels\",\"description\":\"Up to 10 images or videos.\"},\"reels\":{\"label\":\"Reels\",\"description\":\"Short-form vertical video.\"}}},\"benefits\":{\"title\":\"Instagram Marketing Benefits\",\"list\":{\"consistency\":{\"title\":\"Consistent Posting\",\"description\":\"Maintain a consistent Instagram presence with automated posting. Schedule weeks of content in advance and never miss a post.\"},\"multiAccount\":{\"title\":\"Multi-Account Management\",\"description\":\"Manage multiple Instagram accounts from a single API. Perfect for agencies and businesses with multiple brands.\"},\"developer\":{\"title\":\"Developer-First\",\"description\":\"Built by developers for developers. Clean REST API, comprehensive docs, and SDKs for popular programming languages.\"}},\"featuresTitle\":\"Instagram Features Supported\",\"featuresList\":{\"photos\":\"Photo posts\",\"videos\":\"Video posts\",\"stories\":\"Stories publishing\",\"reels\":\"Reels publishing\",\"carousels\":\"Carousel posts\",\"scheduling\":\"Scheduled publishing\",\"accounts\":\"Multiple account support\",\"status\":\"Real-time status tracking\",\"hashtags\":\"Hashtags \u0026 mentions\"}},\"otherPlatforms\":{\"title\":\"One API, 15 Platforms\",\"subtitle\":\"Same integration pattern for all platforms\"},\"errorReference\":{\"title\":\"Instagram API Error Reference\",\"description\":\"Comprehensive guide to Instagram API error codes. Find solutions and troubleshoot common integration issues.\",\"cta\":\"View Error Reference\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Frequently Asked Questions\",\"items\":{\"isFree\":{\"question\":\"Is the Instagram API free to use?\",\"answer\":\"Instagram's Graph API is free but requires significant development investment: Facebook Business verification, OAuth flows, media hosting, and ongoing maintenance. Zernio is free up to 2 accounts (then pay only for what you use beyond that) and replaces all that build time with a single API call.\"},\"reelsSupport\":{\"question\":\"Can I post Instagram Reels via API?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Upload short-form video and Zernio publishes it as a Reel with captions, hashtags, and mentions. No separate Reels endpoint to manage.\"},\"rateLimits\":{\"question\":\"How does Zernio handle Instagram's rate limits?\",\"answer\":\"Zernio manages rate limits automatically with intelligent queuing and exponential backoff retries.\"},\"storiesSupport\":{\"question\":\"Can I schedule Instagram Stories via API?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Set the content type to 'story' in your API call and Zernio handles format optimization and scheduling.\"},\"inboxSupport\":{\"question\":\"Does Zernio support Instagram DMs and comments?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Zernio's \u003ca href='https://zernio.com/social-media-comments'\u003eInstagram Comment API\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href='https://zernio.com/social-media-dms'\u003eMessaging API\u003c/a\u003e are bundled with every connected account at no extra cost. Read, reply to, and moderate Instagram comments and DMs programmatically.\"},\"aiAgents\":{\"question\":\"Can I use Zernio's Instagram API with AI agents?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Zernio's MCP server gives AI agents like Claude, Cursor, and custom LLM workflows direct access to Instagram posting, scheduling, and analytics - no custom integration code needed.\"}}},\"learnMore\":{\"title\":\"Learn More\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"Instagram API Guide\",\"description\":\"Complete developer guide\",\"link\":\"/blog/instagram-api\"},{\"title\":\"Instagram Messaging API\",\"description\":\"Send Instagram DMs programmatically\",\"link\":\"/blog/instagram-messaging-api\"},{\"title\":\"Posting API\",\"description\":\"Post, schedule and analyze content\",\"link\":\"/social-media-api\"}]},\"finalCta\":{\"title\":\"Ready to Ship Your Instagram Integr