le retry logic for failed segments.\"},\"analytics\":{\"title\":\"Engagement Analytics\",\"description\":\"Track views, unique viewers, screenshots, shares, completion rates, and average view time per post.\"},\"multiPlatform\":{\"title\":\"Multi-Platform\",\"description\":\"Post the same vertical video to Snapchat Spotlight + TikTok + Instagram Reels + 12 more platforms.\"}}},\"howItWorks\":{\"title\":\"Three Steps to Snapchat Automation\",\"steps\":{\"connect\":{\"title\":\"Connect\",\"description\":\"Link your Public Profile - we handle the OAuth flow with Snap\"},\"create\":{\"title\":\"Create\",\"description\":\"POST your content and media URL to our simple endpoint\"},\"publish\":{\"title\":\"Publish\",\"description\":\"We encrypt, chunk, upload, and post. You get a webhook when it's live.\"}}},\"codeExample\":{\"title\":\"Simple API, Powerful Results\",\"snippetTitle\":\"post-to-snapchat-spotlight.ts\",\"language\":\"JavaScript\",\"snippet\":\"const response = await fetch('https://zernio.com/api/v1/posts', {\\n  method: 'POST',\\n  headers: {\\n    'Authorization': 'Bearer YOUR_API_KEY',\\n    'Content-Type': 'application/json'\\n  },\\n  body: JSON.stringify({\\n    platforms: [{\\n      platform: 'snapchat',\\n      accountId: 'snap_profile_abc123',\\n      options: { contentType: 'spotlight' }\\n    }],\\n    content: 'Behind the scenes of our new collection',\\n    mediaItems: [{\\n      type: 'video',\\n      url: 'https://cdn.example.com/bts-video.mp4'\\n    }]\\n  })\\n});\\n\\n// Zernio handles: OAuth, encryption, chunked upload, posting\\nconst { post } = await response.json();\\nconsole.log(post.platforms[0].platformPostId);\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Frequently Asked Questions\",\"items\":{\"publicProfile\":{\"question\":\"Do I need a Public Profile?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Snapchat's API only allows posting to Public Profiles (creator/business accounts). Personal accounts cannot post via API. The good news: Public Profiles are free to create in the Snapchat app under Profile → Settings → Public Profile.\"},\"allowlist\":{\"question\":\"Do I need to be on Snapchat's allowlist?\",\"answer\":\"No. Direct API access requires contacting Snap, setting up a Business Account/Organization, creating an OAuth app in Ads Manager, and waiting for allowlist approval. Zernio is already approved - you can start posting immediately with just an API key.\"},\"encryption\":{\"question\":\"What about media encryption requirements?\",\"answer\":\"Snapchat requires all uploaded media to be AES-256-CBC encrypted with proper key/IV handling. Zernio handles this automatically - just send us your media URL and we encrypt it before uploading to Snap's servers.\"},\"mediaSpecs\":{\"question\":\"What are the media requirements?\",\"answer\":\"Images: JPEG/PNG, max 20MB, 1080x1920 recommended. Videos: MP4, max 500MB, 5-60 seconds, 1080x1920 (9:16 vertical). Spotlight only accepts video. We automatically validate and can resize/convert if needed.\"},\"analytics\":{\"question\":\"Can I get post analytics?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Zernio normalizes Snapchat's analytics into our standard format: views, unique viewers, screenshots, shares, completion rate, and average view time. Available via API or dashboard.\"}}},\"errorReference\":{\"title\":\"Snapchat API Error Reference\",\"description\":\"Comprehensive guide to Snapchat API error codes. Find solutions and troubleshoot common integration issues.\",\"cta\":\"View Error Reference\"},\"otherPlatforms\":{\"title\":\"One API, 15 Platforms\",\"subtitle\":\"Same integration pattern for all platforms - post your vertical content everywhere\"},\"finalCta\":{\"title\":\"Skip the Snapchat API Complexity\",\"subtitle\":\"No allowlist. No encryption code. No chunked upload logic. Just POST your content and we handle the rest.\",\"primary\":\"Start Free Trial\",\"secondary\":\"View Docs\",\"footnote\":\"No credit card required • 99.97% uptime\"}},\"publer\":{\"meta\":{\"title\":\"Zernio vs Publer: Social Media API Pricing \u0026 Comparison 2026\",\"description\":\"Compare Zernio vs Publer APIs: 15 platforms, usage-based pricing (free up to 2 accounts), automation features \u0026 developer tools. Find the best Publer alternative for your project.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Zernio vs Publer: API-First Platform Comparison for Developers\",\"ogDescription\":\"Detailed comparison of Zernio and Publer social media APIs. Compare pricing, platforms, automation features, and developer tools to find the best fit for your project.\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"Zernio vs Publer\",\"highlight\":\"Social Media Scheduling API Showdown\",\"description\":\"Zernio and Publer take very different approaches to social media scheduling. Zernio is an API-first platform built for developers and automation. Publer is an all-in-one social media management tool with a robust UI and newly introduced API capabilities. This comprehensive comparison pits Zernio vs Publer across positioning, supported platforms, API design, scheduling, pricing, collaboration, and integrations-ideal if you're seeking a Publer API alternative or evaluating the best social media scheduling API.\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View API Docs\"}},\"tldr\":{\"title\":\"TL;DR\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Zernio and Publer take very different approaches to social media scheduling. Zernio is an API-first platform built for developers and automation, whereas Publer is an all-in-one social media management tool with a robust UI and newly introduced API capabilities.\",\"In this comprehensive comparison, we'll pit Zernio vs Publer for developers – covering product positioning, supported platforms, API design, scheduling logic, pricing, team collaboration, and integrations. If you're looking for a Publer API alternative or evaluating the best social media scheduling API for automated social media posting, read on!\"]},\"comparisonTable\":{\"title\":\"Head-to-Head Feature Comparison\",\"headers\":{\"feature\":\"Feature\",\"late\":\"Zernio\",\"competitor\":\"Publer\"},\"rows\":{\"approach\":{\"feature\":\"Approach\",\"late\":\"API-first platform (built for devs)\\nzernio.com\",\"competitor\":\"UI-first scheduler; API as add-on\\npubler.com\"},\"platforms\":{\"feature\":\"Supported Platforms\",\"late\":\"10 major networks (X, IG, TikTok, LinkedIn, FB, YouTube, Threads, Reddit, Pinterest, Bluesky)\",\"competitor\":\"13 networks (adds Google Business, WordPress, Telegram, Mastodon; no Reddit)\"},\"freePlan\":{\"feature\":\"Free Plan\",\"late\":\"Yes – first 2 accounts free, unlimited posts, API access included\",\"competitor\":\"Yes – 3 accounts, 10 posts/account (no X on free; API not included)\"},\"apiAvailability\":{\"feature\":\"API Availability\",\"late\":\"All plans (instant API key on signup)\",\"competitor\":\"Business \u0026 up only (API restricted to high-tier users)\"},\"multiPlatform\":{\"feature\":\"Multi-Platform Posting\",\"late\":\"One API call can post to all platforms at once\",\"competitor\":\"One post per account; bulk CSV upload supported\"},\"scheduling\":{\"feature\":\"Scheduling Features\",\"late\":\"Core scheduling via API/UI; reliability-focused\",\"competitor\":\"Auto-schedule, recurring, recycling, first-comment, analytics \u0026 calendar\"},\"collaboration\":{\"feature\":\"Team Collaboration\",\"late\":\"Unlimited team members on all plans; multi-client dashboard\",\"competitor\":\"Team members at extra cost; approvals \u0026 granular roles\"},\"pricing\":{\"feature\":\"Pricing (≈50 accounts)\",\"late\":\"Usage-based: ~$168/mo (free up to 2 accounts, then $6/account on tier 1, $3 on tier 2)\",\"competitor\":\"Business: $21/mo base + per-account add-on (rate not publicly listed; 50 accounts typically lands $200–$350/mo)\"},\"rateLimits\":{\"feature\":\"Rate Limits\",\"late\":\"~600 requests/min (higher on Enterprise)\",\"competitor\":\"100 requests/2 minutes/user (≈50/min)\"},\"integrations\":{\"feature\":\"Third-Party Integrations\",\"late\":\"Official n8n node; Zapier/Make via API \u0026 webhooks\",\"competitor\":\"Zapier/Make/n8n via API; native connectors planned\"}}},\"screenshot\":{\"title\":\"Publer's Social Media Management Suite\",\"description\":\"Publer presents a full-featured dashboard with content calendar, analytics, team collaboration, and comprehensive social media management tools.\",\"alt\":\"Publer homepage showing social media management dashboard with content calendar and multi-platform posting\"},\"overview\":{\"title\":\"Product Overview and Positioning\",\"sections\":{\"publer\":{\"title\":\"Publer's Positioning\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Publer's dashboard is a full-featured social media management suite emphasizing content planning and analytics via a user-friendly UI. Publer is an established all-in-one social media management solution (over 12 years in the industry, with 520k+ users) that lets you schedule and publish posts, collaborate with team members, and analyze performance from a single web platform.\",\"Until recently, Publer did not offer a public API, focusing on its web and mobile apps. In mid-2025, Publer introduced an API (initially in beta) now available for Business and Enterprise plan users, signaling a new focus on automation and developer use cases. Still, Publer's core positioning remains a full-featured social media toolkit for non-technical users, with the API as a powerful but add-on component.\"]},\"late\":{\"title\":\"Zernio's Positioning\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Zernio, by contrast, is the new kid on the block – an API-first upstart built from the ground up for developers and automation. Zernio's philosophy is essentially 'API as the product.' It provides a unified social media scheduling API that lets you programmatically post to multiple networks via a single integration, with an optional lightweight web UI for convenience.\",\"Zernio was designed to appeal to developers, SaaS companies, and agencies who want to embed social posting capabilities into their own apps or workflows without dealing with dozens of platform-specific APIs. While Zernio does have a simple dashboard for manual use, its primary positioning is a 'social media scheduling API for developers' (in fact, it's often pitched as a Publer or Buffer API alternative).\"]},\"summary\":\"In short: Zernio is the lean, code-friendly solution, whereas Publer is the feature-packed scheduling suite – each appealing to a different audience and use case.\"}},\"platforms\":{\"title\":\"Supported Platforms and Core Features\",\"intro\":\"When it comes to supported social networks, both Zernio and Publer cover the major bases – but Publer casts a wider net whereas Zernio focuses on the most common platforms:\",\"cards\":{\"late\":{\"title\":\"Zernio: 15 Major Platforms\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Supports Twitter (X), Instagram, TikTok, LinkedIn, Facebook, YouTube, Threads, Reddit, Pinterest, and Bluesky via a unified API. These are the big-name social networks most developers need for posting.\",\"Zernio's philosophy is to handle the intricacies of these APIs under the hood, giving devs one consistent way to publish content everywhere. All supported platforms are available on every plan (even free).\",\"Zernio's feature set is intentionally streamlined: it focuses on content publishing (single posts or batch scheduling) and basic media handling. It does not attempt to replicate a full social media management suite – for example, Zernio has no built-in content editor, social inbox, or detailed analytics dashboard.\"]},\"publer\":{\"title\":\"Publer: 15 Platforms + Rich Features\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Supports everything Zernio does plus WordPress (for blog posts) and Mastodon. Notably, Publer does not list Reddit in its supported networks – a platform Zernio does handle. Both platforms now support Google Business Profiles and Telegram.\",\"Along with support for standard post types, Publer's platform breadth allows for special content: Facebook Reels and Stories, TikTok videos, multi-photo carousels, LinkedIn PDFs, polls, and more.\",\"Publer offers a rich set of tools beyond just posting: a visual content calendar for planning, an AI Assistant for generating copy, hashtag suggestions, automatic RSS feed posting, post recycling and recurring schedules, first-comment scheduling, and in-depth analytics reports.\"]},\"summary\":\"Summary: Zernio covers similar platforms (15 vs Publer's 13) and sticks to core scheduling/posting, whereas Publer supports a wider array and layers on many extras. If your social media strategy involves publishing to WordPress blogs or Google My Business updates (which Zernio doesn't do), Publer has the advantage. But if your focus is the main social networks and you prefer a simpler toolkit, Zernio's pared-down approach may be sufficient.\"}},\"api\":{\"title\":\"API Availability, Design, and Developer Experience\",\"intro\":\"A key differentiator between Zernio and Publer is how they approach their APIs and developer-friendliness:\",\"sections\":{\"publer\":{\"title\":\"Publer API: Feature-Rich but Gated\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Historically, Publer did not have an open API for developers – it was a closed system used via its own UI. This changed in 2025: Publer launched a RESTful API after a beta period, but notably it's only available to Business and Enterprise users (and approved ambassadors). In other words, accessing Publer's API requires a paid high-tier plan; it's not accessible on the free or lower-tier plans.\",\"Assuming you do have access, Publer's API is quite comprehensive in scope: it exposes not just post scheduling endpoints, but also analytics data, media library management, workspaces/accounts management, and more. Essentially, Publer is exposing much of its internal platform functionality via API.\",\"The Publer API uses standard REST with JSON and requires an API token (with user's workspace context) for authentication. One limitation to note is rate limiting: Publer's API is rate-limited to 100 requests per 2 minutes per user (roughly 50 requests/min).\",\"For non-developers, Publer suggests using automation tools like Zapier, Make, or n8n to connect to the API without coding. In fact, Publer has indicated plans to build native integrations for Zapier/Make/n8n after the API launch.\"]},\"late\":{\"title\":\"Zernio API: Developer-First Design\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Zernio takes a radically different approach – the API is the core offering, and it's available on every plan, including free. You can literally sign up for Zernio's free tier and obtain an API key within minutes, which lowers the barrier to entry for developers experimenting or building prototypes.\",\"Zernio's API is a unified REST API that abstracts away the differences between platforms. For example, instead of juggling different payload formats or authentication flows for each social network, Zernio provides a consistent JSON format and handles the platform-specific nuances behind the scenes.\",\"You can specify your content and a list of target platforms (or simply \\\"platforms\\\": [\\\"all\\\"] to broadcast to every connected account) in one API call – Zernio will then fan-out and post to each network's API for you. This 'one payload to rule them all' design is a huge convenience; as the Zernio team likes to say, one API call can replace seven separate integrations in your codebase.\",\"The developer experience is clearly a priority: Zernio provides clean documentation with examples, SDKs in multiple languages, native webhook support, and generous throughput for high-volume use. In terms of rate limits, Zernio mentions ~600 requests/minute on standard plans and up to 1200/min on higher tiers – an order of magnitude higher than Publer's limit.\"]},\"summary\":\"The key takeaway: Zernio's API is designed by developers for developers – if you value a straightforward, well-documented API with high limits and the ability to plug into your CI or codebase, Zernio shines. By contrast, Publer's API is powerful in terms of features, but it feels like an extension of a larger product – it's tied to certain plans and may not be as open or immediately accessible for hacking around.\"}},\"scheduling\":{\"title\":\"Scheduling Logic, Reliability, and Automation Friendliness\",\"publer\":{\"title\":\"Publer's Smart Scheduling\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Publer provides a rich toolkit for scheduling flexibility. Users (or via API) can choose manual times for each post or use Auto-Scheduling features where Publer picks optimal times (based on your preset schedule or best-time analytics).\"],\"bullets\":[\"Recurring posts (repeat weekly/monthly)\",\"Post recycling - automatically repost top content\",\"First-comment scheduling for Instagram/Twitter threads\",\"Bulk CSV upload (500 posts) for batch scheduling\",\"Analytics-driven best time suggestions\"],\"note\":\"Limitation: Publer doesn't provide user-configurable webhooks for real-time updates, so integrating it into complex workflows might require periodic polling or using Zapier triggers for events.\"},\"late\":{\"title\":\"Zernio's Programmable Reliability\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Zernio's approach to scheduling is straightforward and developer-centric. Essentially, you tell the Zernio API what to post and when, and it takes care of scheduling it on the respective platforms. It's not a 'smart scheduler' that picks times for you – instead, you (or your code) define the schedule logic.\"],\"bullets\":[\"99.97% uptime SLA backing the service\",\"Native webhooks and callbacks for real-time updates\",\"High rate limits and infrastructure designed for scale\",\"Official n8n integration with community node package\",\"Handles platform-specific retries and rate limits under the hood\"],\"note\":\"Philosophy: Zernio provides the raw power and reliability; you implement scheduling logic in your app or via automation tools like cron + Zernio API calls.\"},\"verdict\":\"Reliability verdict: Both platforms aim for consistent performance. Zernio's explicit uptime guarantee and its focus on being infrastructure-heavy (enterprise-grade) might appeal if you require guaranteed performance. Publer, having a larger feature surface, might occasionally face more UI-level bugs, but it's battle-tested by a broad user base. If your primary concern is ensuring posts go out on time every time, Zernio's singular focus on that problem is reassuring.\"},\"pricing\":{\"title\":\"Pricing Tiers and Scalability\",\"intro\":\"When comparing Zernio and Publer, pricing and scalability can be a make-or-break factor – especially for agencies or businesses managing many social accounts. The two products have very different pricing models:\",\"cards\":{\"publer\":{\"title\":\"Publer's Per-Account Model\",\"items\":[\"Free: 3 accounts (no X, no API)\",\"Professional: ~$12/mo for 3 accounts\",\"Business: ~$21/mo base + per-extra-account add-on (rate scales with volume; not publicly listed in a flat table)\",\"Team members: +$3 each on Business\"]},\"late\":{\"title\":\"Zernio's Usage-Based Model\",\"items\":[\"Free: first 2 accounts, unlimited posts, full API access\",\"Then $6/account (1–10), $3/account (11–100)\",\"$$1/account for 101+, no cap\",\"Unlimited team members on all plans, no per-seat fees\"]},\"example\":{\"title\":\"Cost Example: 50 accounts\",\"items\":[\"Zernio: ~$168/mo ($6 × 8 + $3 × 40, first 2 free)\",\"Publer: ~$200–$350/month at 50 accounts (Business $21 base + per-account add-on; exact rate scales with volume)\",\"Savings: depends on Publer's per-account rate; the gap widens dramatically past 100 accounts where Zernio's per-account rate drops to $1, with custom enterprise pricing past 2,000 accounts\"]}},\"summary\":\"Summary: For small-scale usage, both platforms can be low-cost (Zernio is free up to 2 accounts). Zernio's per-account rate drops at higher tiers ($6 then $3 then $1, with the $1 rate continuing past 2,000, no cap), so a 25-account agency pays $93/mo on Zernio (8 accounts at $6 plus 15 at $3). Publer Business is $21/mo base plus a per-account add-on whose rate isn't published in a flat table; the cost grows roughly linearly with each extra account. The gap widens past 100 accounts, where Zernio's $1/account rate kicks in. Pay only for what you use; no fixed plan to outgrow.\"},\"collaboration\":{\"title\":\"Team Collaboration and User Experience\",\"cards\":{\"publer\":{\"title\":\"Publer – Built for UI Teamwork\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Publer offers a robust set of collaboration features ideal for marketing teams and agencies working through the Publer interface. It supports multiple workspaces (so an agency can have separate client workspaces), role-based permissions, content approval workflows, and a collaborative calendar.\",\"The Business plan allows adding team members (at $3 each extra) and client approval workflows. The user experience for a non-developer is quite polished – modern dashboard with drag-and-drop scheduling, post previews, and integrated tools (Canva integration, media library, etc.).\"],\"summary\":\"Best for: Teams that want a turnkey solution with rich in-app collaboration.\"},\"late\":{\"title\":\"Zernio – Developer-Oriented Collaboration\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Zernio's focus is not on in-app content collaboration (since many users integrate Zernio into other systems), but it supports teams using the service. You can create multiple clients/projects, invite unlimited team members, and set access permissions – all at no extra cost.\",\"Zernio's UI is comparatively minimal – a simple dashboard to connect social profiles and create/view posts. The assumption is that if you need complex collaboration, you might handle that outside (e.g., using project management tools or your own app).\"],\"summary\":\"Best for: Teams that want basic collaboration support but prefer to build their own user experience around the API.\"},\"verdict\":\"UX Summary: If you put a social media manager with no coding experience in front of both tools, Publer's interface will feel more immediately at home – everything they need is right there. Zernio's interface is straightforward but limited – that user might use it only to connect accounts and then prefer to schedule posts via another tool. Zernio's strength for UX comes when you embed it into your own workflow.\"}},\"integrations\":{\"title\":\"Integrations with Zapier, Make, and n8n\",\"intro\":\"In today's ecosystem, connecting to no-code automation platforms like Zapier, Make (Integromat), and n8n can greatly extend a tool's usefulness:\",\"cards\":{\"late\":{\"title\":\"Zernio Integrations\",\"items\":[\"n8n: Official node available - drag-and-drop Zernio actions\",\"Zapier/Make: Easy integration via webhooks/HTTP modules\",\"Community: Templates and 'n8n Arena' contest for workflows\",\"Webhooks: Two-way integration - Zernio can call your endpoints\"],\"summary\":\"Given Zernio's API-first nature, it is inherently friendly to integration. Zernio's documentation explicitly mentions no-code tools like Zapier, n8n, Make as integration options. Overall, Zernio provides the building blocks for integration and even some out-of-the-box connectors.\"},\"publer\":{\"title\":\"Publer Integrations\",\"items\":[\"Current: API usable via HTTP modules in automation tools\",\"Planned: Native Zapier/Make/n8n apps (Q3 2025 target)\",\"Built-in: Canva integration, link shortener, RSS automation\",\"Limitation: API requires Business plan access\"],\"summary\":\"Before launching its API, Publer's integration with automation tools was limited. Now that the Publer API is live, you can integrate with automation platforms by utilizing their API endpoints in HTTP modules. Publer has publicly stated plans to build direct integrations soon.\"}},\"verdict\":\"Integration Summary: Both Zernio and Publer can connect with Zapier, Make, and n8n – Zernio has a bit of a head start with an official n8n integration and a proactive approach to no-code support, whereas Publer is catching up, using its new API to facilitate these connections. If no-code automation is crucial and you prefer plug-and-play, Zernio (with n8n) currently has an edge.\"},\"conclusion\":{\"title\":\"Conclusion: Zernio or Publer – Which Should You Choose?\",\"intro\":\"Choosing between Zernio and Publer ultimately comes down to your priorities and use case. Both are powerful in their own right, but they cater to slightly different needs:\",\"cards\":{\"choosePubler\":{\"title\":\"Choose Publer if:\",\"items\":[\"You want a comprehensive, ready-to-use social media management platform\",\"You need rich UI features: calendar, analytics, approvals, content tools\",\"Your team prefers working in a dashboard environment\",\"You can justify the higher cost for the full feature suite\",\"You need platforms like Google Business or WordPress\",\"API access is secondary to UI functionality\"],\"summary\":\"Ideal for: Marketers, agencies, or small businesses that need a bit of everything – content planning calendar, built-in analytics, team collaboration, and now an API for custom needs.\"},\"chooseZernio\":{\"title\":\"Choose Zernio if:\",\"items\":[\"You are a developer, tech-forward agency, or product builder\",\"You need a unified social media scheduling API above all\",\"You want instant API access and generous rate limits\",\"You manage many accounts and want predictable, usage-based pricing that drops at scale\",\"You prefer embedding social posting into your own apps/workflows\",\"You value reliability (99.97% uptime SLA) and scalability\"],\"summary\":\"Ideal for: Developers, SaaS companies, and agencies who want to embed social posting capabilities into their own apps or workflows without dealing with dozens of platform-specific APIs.\"}},\"takeaway\":\"Bottom Line: For many organizations, it might not even be an either/or. You could use Publer and Zernio together: for instance, use Publer's dashboard for your social team's day-to-day scheduling on a few accounts, but use Zernio's API for a particular app integration or to handle a high-volume posting project on the side.\",\"summary\":\"However, if you're specifically looking for the most developer-friendly, automation-ready solution (perhaps you literally searched for 'Publer API alternative'), Zernio is a compelling choice. It takes the crown for scenarios where automation, integration, and scalability are top priority – offering a modern REST API with instant access, multi-platform posts in one call, and no steep pricing curve.\",\"finalCta\":{\"description\":\"Ready to try Zernio's free developer-friendly plan? Get an API key instantly and schedule posts across all your networks with just a few lines of code. With 15 platforms on tap and 99.97% uptime behind it, Zernio just might be the unified social media API solution you've been waiting for. 🚀\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio for Free\",\"secondary\":\"View API Docs\",\"footnote\":\"No credit card required • Instant API access • 15 platforms included • 99.97% uptime SLA\"}}}},\"blotato\":{\"meta\":{\"title\":\"Zernio vs Blotato: Which API is Best in 2026?\",\"description\":\"Compare Zernio vs Blotato: API-first scheduling for 15 platforms vs AI content creation. See features, pricing, automation tools for developers \u0026 agencies.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Zernio vs Blotato: API Scheduling Platform vs AI Content Suite\",\"ogDescription\":\"Compare Zernio's unified posting API for 15 platforms with Blotato's AI-powered content creation suite. See pricing, features, and which fits your automation needs.\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"Zernio vs Blotato\",\"highlight\":\"API-First Engine vs AI Studio\",\"description\":\"Zernio and Blotato take two very different approaches to social media scheduling. One is an API-first platform built for developers to post everywhere with zero headaches. The other is an all-in-one content automation toolkit with AI across writing, images, and video. This long-form comparison covers features, APIs, pricing, scalability, UX, integrations, and more so you can choose the right fit.\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View API Docs\"}},\"video\":{\"url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/JNY5XHxT3VY\"},\"comparisonTable\":{\"title\":\"Head to Head Comparison\",\"headers\":{\"feature\":\"Feature\",\"late\":\"Zernio\",\"competitor\":\"Blotato\"},\"rows\":{\"focus\":{\"feature\":\"Platform Focus\",\"late\":\"API-first social scheduling + simple UI\",\"competitor\":\"All-in-one content creation + scheduling suite\"},\"networks\":{\"feature\":\"Supported Networks\",\"late\":\"15 platforms: X, Instagram, TikTok, LinkedIn, Facebook Pages, YouTube, Threads, Reddit, Pinterest, Bluesky, Google Business, Telegram, Snapchat, WhatsApp, Discord\",\"competitor\":\"9 platforms including Pinterest and Bluesky\"},\"apiAccess\":{\"feature\":\"API Access\",\"late\":\"Included on all plans including free. Instant key issuance\",\"competitor\":\"Paid plans only. Generating a key starts a subscription\"},\"contentTools\":{\"feature\":\"Content Creation Tools\",\"late\":\"Scheduling focus. Bring your own AI or tools\",\"competitor\":\"Built-in AI for text, images, and video with voiceovers\"},\"freePlan\":{\"feature\":\"Free Plan\",\"late\":\"Yes. 2 social accounts, unlimited posts, full API\",\"competitor\":\"No ongoing free plan. 7 day trial, API excluded\"},\"pricing\":{\"feature\":\"Pricing Snapshot\",\"late\":\"Usage-based: free up to 2 accounts, then $6/$3/$1 per account, custom for 2,000+\",\"competitor\":\"$$29 Starter, $97 Creator, $499 Agency\"},\"scalability\":{\"feature\":\"Scalability\",\"late\":\"High throughput + generous rate limits\",\"competitor\":\"Posting throughput not published. TikTok capped at ~900 posts per month\"},\"userExperience\":{\"feature\":\"User Experience\",\"late\":\"Minimal UI for manual use. API-first for automation\",\"competitor\":\"Rich UI with calendar, Remix editor, AI studio\"},\"integrations\":{\"feature\":\"Integrations\",\"late\":\"Easy to connect via REST, webhooks, Zapier/n8n/Make\",\"competitor\":\"Official nodes for Make and n8n. API usable in no-code tools\"},\"developerExperience\":{\"feature\":\"Developer Experience\",\"late\":\"Modern JSON API, one call can broadcast to all platforms. SDKs and webhooks\",\"competitor\":\"Functional API but gated by paid plans. One account per call pattern\"}}},\"screenshot\":{\"title\":\"Blotato's Content Studio UI\",\"description\":\"Blotato presents an all-in-one content studio with AI writing, image generation, and video tools alongside scheduling.\",\"alt\":\"Blotato homepage showing AI content studio and faceless video examples\"},\"overview\":{\"title\":\"Platform Overview and Positioning\",\"cards\":{\"late\":{\"title\":\"Zernio at a glance\",\"items\":[\"API-first social scheduling built for developers\",\"One unified API to post across 15 platforms\",\"Lightweight dashboard for quick manual posts\",\"Focus on reliability, speed, and scale\"]},\"blotato\":{\"title\":\"Blotato at a glance\",\"items\":[\"All-in-one creator toolkit with AI text, image, and video\",\"Remix content from blogs and URLs into social posts\",\"Rich calendar and editor centric workspace\",\"More opinionated studio vs integration layer\"]},\"analogy\":\"Analogy: Zernio is the engine under the hood that gets you from draft to seven networks. Blotato is the decked out creative van with a content kitchen and AI autopilot.\"}},\"coreFeatures\":{\"title\":\"Core Features and Social Network Support\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Zernio supports fifteen major platforms via a unified API: X, Instagram, TikTok, LinkedIn, Facebook Pages, YouTube, Threads, Reddit, Pinterest, Bluesky, Google Business, Telegram, Snapchat, WhatsApp, and Discord. One API call can fan out a post to multiple networks at once and Zernio abstracts away per platform quirks for media and formats.\"],\"list\":[\"Blotato adds platforms like Pinterest and Bluesky\",\"Blotato's API targets one account per call; Zernio can broadcast\",\"Blotato media upload usually requires a first step to host the file\"],\"highlights\":{\"late\":{\"title\":\"Zernio focuses on posting\",\"items\":[\"Lean feature set; bring your own AI\",\"Unified payload across platforms\",\"Handles media quirks under the hood\"]},\"blotato\":{\"title\":\"Blotato focuses on creation\",\"items\":[\"AI writing, image, and video generation\",\"Remix content from blogs and links\",\"Studio style editor and calendar\"]}}},\"apiSection\":{\"title\":\"API Capabilities and Developer Experience\",\"cards\":{\"late\":{\"title\":\"Zernio - Built for developers\",\"items\":[\"Instant API keys on all plans, including free\",\"One payload can broadcast to all platforms\",\"Fast responses, high uptime, generous rate limits\",\"Webhooks and SDKs for common languages\"]},\"blotato\":{\"title\":\"Blotato - Developer friendly\",\"items\":[\"API requires a paid plan; key creation starts billing\",\"Posting, media upload, scheduling, AI video endpoints\",\"Typically one account per request; get IDs via UI\",\"Official nodes for Make and n8n\"]}},\"verdict\":\"Developer verdict: Zernio favors unified execution and immediate access. Blotato favors low code workflows and rich content generation.\"},\"pricing\":{\"title\":\"Pricing Structure and Scalability\",\"late\":{\"title\":\"Zernio pricing\",\"items\":[\"Free: first 2 social accounts, unlimited posts, full API access\",\"$$6/account for accounts 1-10\",\"$$3/account for accounts 11-100\",\"$$1/account for accounts 101+ (no cap)\",\"No cap: the $1 rate continues at any scale\"]},\"blotato\":{\"title\":\"Blotato pricing\",\"items\":[\"No perpetual free plan (7 day trial)\",\"$$29 Starter: 20 accounts + AI credits\",\"$$97 Creator: 40 accounts + more credits\",\"$$499 Agency: large AI credits + support\"]},\"costAngle\":{\"title\":\"Cost angle\",\"description\":\"For many profiles and pure scheduling, Zernio is usually more cost effective. If you need heavy AI generation inside the same tool, Blotato's bundle can be worth it.\"}},\"ux\":{\"title\":\"Ease of Use and User Experience\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Zernio delivers a minimalist dashboard for connecting accounts and manual posting, with most power exposed through the API. It is low friction for developers and simple enough for non technical teammates when needed.\",\"Blotato offers a rich content studio with Remix workflows, a calendar, AI prompts, and media generation. It is mobile friendly and ideal for creators who want a one stop workspace without coding, at the cost of more complexity to learn.\"]},\"integrations\":{\"title\":\"Integration and Automation Support\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Both Zernio and Blotato can be wired into Zapier, n8n, and Make. Zernio is DIY friendly via REST, webhooks, and generic HTTP modules. Blotato provides official modules for Make and an n8n community node, making it plug and play in those ecosystems.\",\"With Zernio, common patterns include adding social posting to your app, bulk scheduling from a CMS, or triggering posts from data events. With Blotato, popular patterns include remixing content with AI, using inspiration databases, and automating text to video before scheduling.\"]},\"depth\":{\"title\":\"In Depth - Full Comparison Text\",\"sections\":[{\"title\":\"Zernio vs Blotato - Social Media Scheduling API Showdown\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Zernio and Blotato take two very different approaches to social media scheduling. One is a developer's dream - an API-first platform that promises to 'post everywhere with zero headaches.' The other is an all-in-one content automation toolkit with a splash of AI magic. If you're a developer, marketer, small business, or agency seeking a reliable, flexible way to schedule and automate social media posts, this witty yet informative comparison is for you. We'll pit Zernio against Blotato head-to-head on everything from features and APIs to pricing and user experience. By the end, you'll see which platform shines as the ultimate social media scheduling API solution (and why Zernio just might be the Blotato API alternative you've been looking for). Let's dive in to discover how each handles automated social media posting for developers and content creators alike.\"]},{\"title\":\"Head to Head Comparison Table\",\"paragraphs\":[\"To kick things off, here's a quick overview of how Zernio and Blotato compare on key points:\"],\"list\":[\"Platform Focus: Zernio (API-first) - API-first social scheduling platform for developers (zernio.com). Also offers a simple UI for manual posts. Blotato (All-in-One) - Content creation and scheduling suite ('8-apps-in-1') with AI writing, images, video, etc. (blotato.com).\",\"Supported Networks: Zernio supports 15 major platforms (X/Twitter, Instagram, TikTok, LinkedIn, Facebook Pages, YouTube, Threads, Reddit, Pinterest, Bluesky, Google Business, Telegram, Snapchat, WhatsApp, Discord) (zernio.com). Blotato supports 9 platforms including newer ones like Bluesky and Pinterest (help.blotato.com).\",\"API Access: Zernio - available on all plans including free with instant API key generation (zernio.com). Blotato - included only in paid plans (free trial excludes API). API key generation immediately triggers paid subscription to prevent abuse. Official n8n and Make.com nodes provided (help.blotato.com).\",\"Content Creation Tools: Zernio focuses on scheduling; no built in AI content generation. Blotato includes unlimited AI text, AI image generation, and AI video creation with voiceovers. Remix content from blogs/URLs and repurpose across platforms (blotato.com).\",\"Free Plan: Zernio - free forever for the first 2 social accounts with unlimited posts and full API access. No card required (zernio.com). Blotato - no free plan (7 day free trial only), trial excludes API and provides limited AI credits.\",\"Pricing (Paid Tiers): Zernio - usage-based with first 2 social accounts free. Then $6/account (1-10), $3/account (11-100), $1/account for 101+ with no cap. All 15 platforms and API access included on every account, no separate plans (zernio.com). Blotato - Starter $29/mo with 20 social accounts and 1,250 AI credits, Creator $97/mo with 40 accounts and 5,000 AI credits, Agency $499/mo with 40+ accounts focus and 28,000 AI credits plus support (blotato.com).\",\"Scalability: Zernio handles high volume (e.g., 600+ API requests/min on mid tier plans). Blotato's posting throughput is not publicly documented; TikTok posting limited to ~900 posts/month even on paid plans (blotato.com).\",\"User Experience: Zernio has a minimalistic UI primarily designed for integration with a simple REST API. Blotato has a rich UI with a content calendar, Remix editor, and media generation studio; ideal for creators who want an all in one workspace without coding (help.blotato.com).\",\"Integrations: Zernio is built to plug into anything via direct REST calls and webhooks, and is easy to wire into Zapier, n8n, Make. Blotato provides official modules for Zapier/Make/n8n and can be triggered via API or webhooks (help.blotato.com).\",\"Developer Experience: Zernio is developer centric with a modern JSON REST API, clear docs, broadcast posting, SDKs, high rate limits, and 99.97% uptime SLA (zernio.com). Blotato is developer friendly but not primary focus; API is functional and supports posting, media, and video generation but requires UI setup and paid access (help.blotato.com).\"]},{\"title\":\"Platform Overview and Positioning\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Zernio positions itself as a lean, mean social media scheduling API machine. It is the API-first upstart built from the ground up for developers (zernio.com). The philosophy is simple: provide one unified API to post across all popular social networks with minimal hassle. Zernio supplements its API with a lightweight UI for occasional manual uploads or status checks, but automation is king. Zernio's positioning is that it handles the posting infrastructure while you handle content.\",\"Blotato is an 8 apps in 1 content automation toolkit built by and for content creators (blotato.com). Founded by a creator who scaled from 0 to 500k followers in 6 months using the tool herself, Blotato helps solopreneurs, small businesses, and agencies create and distribute content at scale without a big team. It combines AI writing, image generation, video creation, and scheduling. It is a content studio that also handles scheduling.\",\"Witty analogy: Think of Zernio as a powerful engine under the hood - you might not see all the bells and whistles, but it will reliably get you from point A to B with minimal fuss. Blotato is like a decked out custom van - equipped with a content kitchen, AI autopilot, and a built in GPS for trends.\"]},{\"title\":\"Core Features and Social Network Support\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Zernio currently supports fifteen major social networks via its unified API: Twitter/X, Instagram, TikTok, LinkedIn, Facebook Pages, YouTube, Threads, Reddit, Pinterest, Bluesky, Google Business, Telegram, Snapchat, WhatsApp, and Discord (zernio.com).\",\"Scheduling and posting: Zernio's API can do one call to fan out a post to multiple networks at once (zernio.com). Blotato's API generally handles one account per call (help.blotato.com). Both support scheduling for future publication.\",\"Media support: Zernio abstracts media handling for each platform. Blotato requires you to upload media first to get a hosted URL, then attach that URL to your post payload (help.blotato.com). Both approaches work; Zernio streamlines it more for developers.\",\"Content creation and AI: Zernio does not include content creation tools. Blotato offers unlimited AI copywriting, AI images, and AI video creation with voiceovers (blotato.com). Blotato can also remix content from blogs or URLs. Zernio integrates easily with external AI tools.\"]},{\"title\":\"API Capabilities and Developer Experience\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Zernio - Built for developers from day one: Sign up free, generate an API key within minutes (zernio.com). The API is designed to be simple and uniform. Posting to different platforms uses the same endpoint and one payload can target all platforms. Zernio's infrastructure is fast and highly available with generous rate limits, webhooks, and SDKs (zernio.com).\",\"Blotato - Developer friendly, but not just for devs: Access requires a paid account. The API allows publishing posts, scheduling, uploading media, and even triggering AI video generation. It embraces no code integrations strongly with an official Make.com module and n8n node (help.blotato.com). You will connect accounts via the UI and then retrieve account IDs for API calls and typically loop calls for multi account posting.\",\"Developer experience verdict: If you live and breathe APIs, Zernio feels tailored to you. Blotato's API is useful especially for leveraging its content creation powers in low code tools, but is a bit more gated and granular.\"]},{\"title\":\"Pricing Structure and Scalability\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Zernio's pricing: usage-based, no tiered plans. The first 2 social accounts are free with unlimited posts and full API access. Beyond that you pay $6/account for accounts 1-10, $3/account for 11-100, $1/account for 101+ with no cap. Every account includes full API access and all 15 platforms (zernio.com).\",\"Blotato's pricing: No perpetual free tier. 7 day free trial includes all features except API. Starter at $29/month with 20 social accounts and AI credits. Creator at $97/month with 40 accounts and more credits. Agency at $499/month with high touch support and 28,000 AI credits. The Agency plan emphasizes support over higher account counts (blotato.com).\",\"Scalability and cost considerations: For pure scheduling capacity and many accounts, Zernio is more cost effective. For heavy AI generation needs, Blotato's bundle can justify the price.\"]},{\"title\":\"Ease of Use and User Experience (UI vs API-First)\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Zernio's UI and workflow: Minimalistic dashboard to connect profiles, create posts, attach media, and schedule. Designed to be dead simple and to complement automation. Developers can work entirely via API while non devs can use the UI when needed (zernio.com).\",\"Blotato's UI and workflow: A content creation workshop with sources, AI prompts, inspiration, and a Remix editor. Drafts autosave in the cloud and the app is mobile friendly. It provides tutorials and support like weekly office hours (blotato.com, help.blotato.com). It is more complex under the hood but rich for daily use.\",\"Team collaboration: Zernio supports agencies through higher plan capacities; Blotato offers team access in settings (help.blotato.com). Neither is primarily a collaboration suite like legacy enterprise tools.\"]},{\"title\":\"Integration and Automation Support\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Zapier, n8n, Make: Zernio is easy to wire up via REST, webhooks, or generic HTTP modules. Blotato provides official modules for Make and an n8n community node, making it plug and play for non developers (help.blotato.com).\",\"Webhooks and callbacks: Zernio supports native webhooks for events like post status. Blotato mentions an API dashboard but not explicit outgoing webhooks; polling or no code flows may be used instead.\"]},{\"title\":\"Platform Limitations and Special Considerations\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Zernio's limitations: It does not create content and adheres to official APIs, so unsupported features like posting to Facebook personal profiles are not offered. Plans have per account daily caps to align with platform policies.\",\"Blotato's limitations: No tagging people in posts yet; Published by Blotato attribution where required; no auto link shortening; platform API quirks apply; TikTok post caps; no ongoing free tier; intended for serious content creation, not spam (help.blotato.com).\"]},{\"title\":\"Which Should You Choose\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Choose Zernio if you want a clean, developer friendly solution for multi platform scheduling via API, with predictable pricing and a simple UI as needed. It fits teams with content ready to publish and those who value programmatic control, scalability, and reliability (zernio.com).\",\"Choose Blotato if you want an all in one content creation and scheduling platform leveraging AI to save time, prefer a visual interface with templates and prompts, and can invest at least $29/month for the bundle (blotato.com).\"]},{\"title\":\"Conclusion - The API First Advantage for Modern Teams\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Both Zernio and Blotato bring value, but they cater to different philosophies. Blotato deserves applause for AI driven content automation and can help creators punch above their weight. If you want more automation and integration rather than a studio, Zernio is built for you - a unified scheduling API that is reliable, fast, affordable at scale, and easy to plug into existing workflows (zernio.com).\",\"Ready to try Zernio's free developer friendly plan? Get started at no cost, obtain an API key instantly, and see how it fits with zero risk. If you want a Blotato API alternative that offers more flexibility or if you identify as a developer first, Zernio is tailored for you.\",\"The bottom line: Zernio vs Blotato isn't about good vs bad - it's about choosing the right tool for your needs. If your needs include a scalable, no BS, API first approach to social scheduling, then Zernio might be the perfect match.\"]}]},\"limitations\":{\"title\":\"Platform Limitations and Special Considerations\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Zernio keeps scope tight: it does not include content generation and adheres to official platform APIs. Posting frequency caps per plan are in place to align with platform policies.\",\"Blotato currently does not support tagging people in posts and adds third party attribution labels like Published by Blotato where platforms require it. TikTok posting has explicit caps and link shortening is not automatic. The API requires a paid plan and initial setup in the UI to obtain account IDs.\"]},\"choose\":{\"title\":\"Which Should You Choose\",\"sections\":{\"late\":{\"title\":\"Choose Zernio if:\",\"items\":[\"You want a social media scheduling API you can integrate fast\",\"You manage many accounts and want predictable pricing\",\"You value unified multi platform posting and high reliability\",\"You already have content and just need efficient distribution\",\"You prefer automation with a simple UI for manual backups\",\"You want a free plan to start without risk\"]},\"blotato\":{\"title\":\"Choose Blotato if:\",\"items\":[\"You want an all in one creative studio with AI for text, image, and video\",\"You prefer a visual interface with templates and prompts\",\"You heavily repurpose content across formats and platforms\",\"You want official no code modules and are fine with paid only API access\",\"You can justify the higher price thanks to bundled AI credits and support\"]}}},\"conclusion\":{\"title\":\"Conclusion - The API First Advantage\",\"paragraphs\":[\"Blotato pushes the envelope with AI driven content creation and a studio style UI. For creators who want ideas, assets, and scheduling in one place, it can be a superpower.\",\"If you want more automation and integration rather than an all in one studio, Zernio is a compelling choice. It focuses on being a unified, reliable scheduling API with a simple UI when you need it and pricing that scales cleanly as you add profiles. For teams who identify as developer first and marketer second, Zernio fits like a glove.\"],\"highlight\":{\"title\":\"Bottom line:\",\"description\":\"Choosing between Zernio and Blotato is not about good vs bad. It is about picking the right tool for your needs. If your needs include a scalable, no BS, API first approach to social scheduling, Zernio might be the perfect match.\"},\"final\":{\"description\":\"Ready to try Zernio's free developer friendly plan and get an API key instantly with no risk?\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Start Free Trial\",\"secondary\":\"View Pricing\",\"footnote\":\"No credit card required • Get API access instantly • All 15 platforms included\"}}}},\"whatsapp\":{\"hero\":{\"title\":\"Ship Your WhatsApp Integration\",\"highlight\":\"In Minutes, Not Months\",\"subtitle\":\"Meta's WhatsApp API means navigating 5+ products, opaque template approvals, silent webhook failures, and docs that contradict themselves. Zernio abstracts all of it into one clean REST API.\"},\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Start Free Trial\",\"secondary\":\"View API Docs\",\"docsLink\":\"View Complete API Documentation\"},\"comparison\":{\"title\":\"Why Zernio?\",\"subtitle\":\"Meta's API is a developer nightmare. We fixed it.\",\"officialTitle\":\"WhatsApp Cloud API (Direct)\",\"lateTitle\":\"Zernio API\",\"painPoints\":{\"oauth\":\"Navigate 5+ Meta products just to send one message (Business Manager, App Dashboard, WABA, phone setup, verification)\",\"templates\":\"Template approval is slow and opaque. \\\"Utility\\\" templates silently reclassified as \\\"marketing\\\" (the most expensive tier)\",\"webhooks\":\"Webhooks silently fail with no replay, no logs, and minimal error feedback. You build retry infrastructure from scratch\",\"maintenance\":\"New accounts start at 250 messages/day. Phone numbers permanently locked to API. Breaking changes ship without warning\",\"platforms\":\"Pay Twilio 3-5x markup for a usable DX, or suffer Meta's broken docs and zero developer tooling yourself\"},\"benefits\":{\"auth\":\"One API key. No Meta Business verification maze. Start sending in 30 seconds\",\"templates\":\"Full template CRUD via API. We handle submission to Meta and category tracking\",\"webhooks\":\"Reliable webhook delivery with built-in retry logic. Same format across all platforms\",\"window\":\"24h window, rate limits, messaging tiers: all handled automatically. You just call POST\",\"platforms\":\"Same REST API for WhatsApp + 14 other platforms. Learn once, ship everywhere\"},\"timeSaving\":\"Save 4-6 weeks of fighting Meta's developer portal.\",\"timeSavingText\":\"Ship WhatsApp API integration today, not next quarter.\"},\"notice\":{\"title\":\"No Meta Developer App Required\",\"description\":\"Zernio handles WABA provisioning through Meta Embedded Signup. No need to create a Meta app, configure webhooks, or pass App Review. Connect in one click from our dashboard.\",\"conversionTip\":\"💡 Meta charges per conversation, not per message. Replies within 24h are free. We pass through Meta pricing with zero markup.\"},\"contentTypes\":{\"title\":\"Every WhatsApp Message Type Supported\",\"items\":{\"text\":{\"label\":\"Text Messages\"},\"templates\":{\"label\":\"Template Messages\"},\"media\":{\"label\":\"Media (Images, Videos, Docs)\"},\"interactive\":{\"label\":\"Interactive (Buttons, Lists)\"},\"location\":{\"label\":\"Location Sharing\"},\"contacts\":{\"label\":\"Contact Cards\"}}},\"howItWorks\":{\"title\":\"Three Steps. No Meta Developer Portal.\",\"steps\":{\"connect\":{\"title\":\"Connect in One Click\",\"description\":\"Meta Embedded Signup handles WABA creation and phone number linking. No Business Manager navigation, no App Review, no verification dance.\"},\"build\":{\"title\":\"Send Your First Message\",\"description\":\"One POST request to send templates, media, or interactive messages. Webhooks deliver replies in a consistent format across all platforms.\"},\"scale\":{\"title\":\"Scale with Broadcasts\",\"description\":\"Bulk send to 100 recipients per request with per-user personalization. Schedule, track delivery and read receipts, cancel before send.\"}}},\"features\":{\"title\":\"Everything Meta Makes Hard, Made Simple\",\"cards\":{\"broadcasts\":{\"title\":\"Broadcast Campaigns\",\"description\":\"Send personalized template messages to up to 100 recipients per request. Schedule sends, track per-recipient delivery, cancel before send.\"},\"templates\":{\"title\":\"Template Management\",\"description\":\"Full CRUD via API: create, list, update, delete templates. We submit to Meta for approval and track category changes so you don't get surprise billing.\"},\"contacts\":{\"title\":\"Contact CRM\",\"description\":\"Import WhatsApp contacts in bulk, organize with tags and custom fields, track opt-in status. Search, filter, and segment your audience for broadcasts.\"},\"phoneNumbers\":{\"title\":\"Phone Number Provisioning\",\"description\":\"Search and purchase WhatsApp-ready US numbers through our API. No manual Meta developer setup. Automatic verification, no OTP required.\"},\"tracking\":{\"title\":\"Delivery \u0026 Read Tracking\",\"description\":\"Track sent, delivered, read status for every message. Webhooks fire for each status change in the same format as all other platforms.\"},\"profile\":{\"title\":\"Business Profile API\",\"description\":\"Read and update your WhatsApp Business profile (about, description, address, email, websites) programmatically. No Meta Business Manager needed.\"}}},\"codeExample\":{\"title\":\"Three Steps. One API.\",\"snippetTitle\":\"Send a WhatsApp Broadcast\",\"snippet\":\"$15\"},\"useCases\":{\"title\":\"Built for Modern Use Cases\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Frequently Asked Questions\",\"items\":{\"waba\":{\"question\":\"Do I need a Meta developer app for WhatsApp?\",\"answer\":\"No. Zernio handles WABA provisioning through Meta Embedded Signup. One-click connect from our dashboard - no Meta Business Manager navigation required.\"},\"window\":{\"question\":\"How does Zernio handle the 24-hour messaging window?\",\"answer\":\"Automatically. When a user messages you, you have 24 hours to reply freely. Outside that window, only approved template messages work (Meta charges for these). Zernio tracks windows per conversation and returns clear errors if you try to send outside it, so you never get silent failures.\"},\"pricing\":{\"question\":\"How does pricing compare to Twilio or other BSPs?\",\"answer\":\"Zernio passes through Meta's conversation-based pricing with zero markup on message fees. No per-message surcharge, no BSP tax. You pay Zernio's platform fee plus Meta's standard rates, which are typically 3-5x cheaper than Twilio's WhatsApp pricing.\"},\"verification\":{\"question\":\"What about Meta Business verification?\",\"answer\":\"Meta requires business verification to go beyond 250 messages/day. Zernio's Embedded Signup flow handles the verification request as part of onboarding. If Meta needs additional documents, we surface clear instructions, not a black box rejection with no explanation.\"},\"chatbots\":{\"question\":\"Can I build chatbots with Zernio?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Webhooks deliver incoming messages in a consistent JSON format (same as Instagram, Telegram, and all other platforms). Send replies via our API. Works with any AI backend: OpenAI, Claude, custom logic.\"},\"breaking\":{\"question\":\"What happens when Meta ships breaking changes?\",\"answer\":\"We absorb them. Meta is known for pushing breaking changes to the WhatsApp Cloud API without warning. Zernio maintains compatibility at the API layer, so your integration keeps working even when Meta's underlying API changes.\"}}},\"errorReference\":{\"title\":\"WhatsApp API Error Reference\",\"description\":\"Comprehensive guide to WhatsApp API error codes. Find solutions and troubleshoot common integration issues.\",\"cta\":\"View Error Reference\"},\"learnMore\":{\"title\":\"Learn More\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"WhatsApp API Guide\",\"description\":\"Complete developer guide\",\"link\":\"/blog/whatsapp-api-tutorial-how-to-send-messages-and-templates\"},{\"title\":\"Zernio vs Twilio\",\"description\":\"Twilio WhatsApp alternative\",\"link\":\"/alternatives/twilio\"},{\"title\":\"ChatSDK Adapter\",\"description\":\"Build a chatbot for WhatsApp\",\"link\":\"/chat-sdk\"}]},\"otherPlatforms\":{\"title\":\"One API, 15 Platforms\",\"subtitle\":\"Same integration pattern for all platforms\"},\"finalCta\":{\"title\":\"Stop Fighting Meta's Developer Portal\",\"subtitle\":\"37 WhatsApp endpoints. Zero Meta headaches. Join developers who shipped in days instead of months.\",\"primary\":\"Start Free Trial\",\"secondary\":\"Read Documentation\",\"footnote\":\"No credit card required • Zero markup on Meta message fees • No Meta developer app needed\"}},\"sectionLabels\":{\"features\":\"Features\",\"messageTypes\":\"Message Types\",\"codeExample\":\"Code Example\",\"codeExamples\":\"Code Examples\",\"contentTypes\":\"Content Types\",\"howItWorks\":\"How It Works\",\"keyFeatures\":\"Key Features\",\"relatedFeatures\":\"Related Features\",\"viewFullApiDocumentation\":\"View Full API Documentation\",\"heroNote\":\"No credit card required\",\"viewApiReference\":{\"tiktok\":\"View TikTok API Reference →\",\"instagram\":\"View Instagram API Reference →\",\"linkedin\":\"View LinkedIn API Reference →\",\"twitter\":\"View Twitter API Reference →\",\"youtube\":\"View YouTube API Reference →\",\"facebook\":\"View Facebook API Reference →\",\"threads\":\"View Threads API Reference →\",\"pinterest\":\"View Pinterest API Reference →\",\"bluesky\":\"View Bluesky API Reference →\",\"reddit\":\"View Reddit API Reference →\",\"googlebusiness\":\"View Google Business API Reference →\",\"telegram\":\"View Telegram API Reference →\",\"snapchat\":\"View Snapchat API Reference →\",\"whatsapp\":\"View WhatsApp API Reference →\"}}},\"comparisonPages\":{\"buffer\":{\"meta\":{\"title\":\"Buffer Has No API. We Do. | Buffer Alternative 2026\",\"description\":\"Looking for a Buffer alternative with API access? Buffer has no public API. Zernio is API-first with instant access and usage-based pricing: free up to 2 accounts, then $6/$3/$1 per account, custom for 2,000+ vs Buffer's $250+ for 50 channels.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Buffer Has No API. We Do. | Buffer Alternative 2026\",\"ogDescription\":\"Buffer deprecated its API in 2019. Zernio has a production-grade API with 99.97% uptime SLA.\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"The\",\"highlight\":\"Buffer Alternative\",\"subtitle\":\"That Actually Has an API\",\"description\":\"Buffer deprecated its public API in 2019. It's rebuilding one, but it's not public yet. Zernio is API-first with instant access, 99.97% uptime SLA, and usage-based pricing that scales smoothly past Buffer's $5/channel model.\",\"subtitle2\":\"No credit card required • Instant API key • Buffer has no API\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View API Docs\"}},\"fatalFlaw\":{\"title\":\"The Fatal Flaw: Buffer Has No Public API\",\"description\":\"In 2019, Buffer deprecated its public API that had served 47,000+ API clients. As of December 2025, Buffer has no public API available. They're rebuilding a GraphQL API, but it's only in early access - not publicly available.\",\"quote\":\"\\\"We don't currently have a public API available, but we're actively working on building a new one...\\\"\",\"footnote\":\"Zernio: Sign up → Settings → API → Copy key. Available NOW on all plans including free.\"},\"comparison\":{\"label\":\"API vs No API\",\"title\":\"A working API vs \\\"coming soon\\\"\",\"bufferTitle\":\"Buffer\",\"bufferItems\":[\"NO PUBLIC API - deprecated in 2019\",\"New GraphQL API in development - not public yet\",\"Per-channel pricing: $5/channel adds up fast\",\"50 channels = $250+/month (vs Zernio's $168/mo, usage-based)\",\"No published rate limits for new API\",\"No uptime SLA - rebuilding from scratch\",\"6+ year API gap (2019-2025+)\"],\"lateTitle\":\"Zernio\",\"lateItems\":[\"Production-grade API - available NOW\",\"Instant API key on all plans (even free)\",\"Usage-based: free up to 2 accounts, then $6/$3/$1 per account, custom for 2,000+\",\"Volume tiers built in - costs drop as you scale\",\"Published rate limits: 60-1200 req/min\",\"99.97% uptime SLA - publicly documented\",\"2+ years battle-tested (2023+)\"],\"savingsHighlight\":\"Zernio wins by default\",\"savingsText\":\"- Buffer has no public API. Zernio has a production-grade API with instant access.\"},\"table\":{\"label\":\"Feature Comparison\",\"title\":\"Head-to-head comparison\",\"headers\":{\"feature\":\"Feature\",\"late\":\"Zernio\",\"buffer\":\"Buffer\"},\"rows\":[{\"feature\":\"Public API\",\"late\":\"Yes (all plans)\",\"buffer\":\"NO - deprecated 2019\"},{\"feature\":\"API status\",\"late\":\"Production (2+ years)\",\"buffer\":\"Rebuilding (not public)\"},{\"feature\":\"API access time\",\"late\":\"30 seconds\",\"buffer\":\"N/A - no public API\"},{\"feature\":\"50 accounts cost\",\"late\":\"$$168/mo\",\"buffer\":\"$$250+/mo\"},{\"feature\":\"Pricing model\",\"late\":\"Usage-based ($6/$3/$1 tiers, custom for 2,000+)\",\"buffer\":\"Per-channel ($5/ch)\"},{\"feature\":\"Rate limits\",\"late\":\"60-1200 req/min\",\"buffer\":\"None published\"},{\"feature\":\"Uptime SLA\",\"late\":\"99.97% (published)\",\"buffer\":\"None\"},{\"feature\":\"Free plan\",\"late\":\"Yes (with API)\",\"buffer\":\"Yes (no API)\"},{\"feature\":\"UI dashboard\",\"late\":\"Basic\",\"buffer\":\"Excellent\"},{\"feature\":\"AI assistant\",\"late\":\"No\",\"buffer\":\"Yes (paid)\"},{\"feature\":\"Analytics\",\"late\":\"Bundled (no add-on)\",\"buffer\":\"Built-in (Team+)\"},{\"feature\":\"Social Ads API\",\"late\":\"Yes\",\"buffer\":\"No\"}]},\"history\":{\"label\":\"The Buffer API Tragedy\",\"title\":\"What happened to Buffer's API?\",\"sections\":{\"deprecated\":{\"title\":\"2019: API Deprecated\",\"description\":\"Buffer made the controversial decision to shut down its public API that had served 47,000+ API clients. Reasons included Cambridge Analytica fallout, compliance burden, and competitive concerns about third-party tools.\",\"quote\":\"After an audit of existing API integrations, we've chosen to revoke access to third-party tools that provide similar functionality to Buffer's core product...\"},\"rebuilding\":{\"title\":\"2025: Rebuilding (Not Public)\",\"description\":\"In July 2025, Buffer announced it's rebuilding a new GraphQL-based API. Current status: early access only, not publicly available, no published rate limits or SLA, uncertain timeline (\\\"2025-2026\\\").\",\"footnote\":\"For production use today, Zernio is the only option with a working API.\"}}},\"features\":{\"label\":\"Production-Ready API\",\"title\":\"What Zernio offers that Buffer can't\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"Working API Today\",\"description\":\"Zernio has a production-grade REST API available right now. Buffer's API was deprecated in 2019 and isn't public yet. For any automation or integration, Zernio is the only choice.\"},{\"title\":\"Instant API Access\",\"description\":\"Sign up for Zernio, go to Settings, copy your API key. 30 seconds. Buffer requires waiting for early access to an API that isn't public yet.\"},{\"title\":\"99.97% Uptime SLA\",\"description\":\"Zernio publishes a 99.97% uptime guarantee. Buffer is rebuilding from scratch - no SLA, no guarantees, no production track record for the new API.\"},{\"title\":\"Cheaper at Scale\",\"description\":\"Zernio: $168/mo for 50 accounts (usage-based, first 2 free). Buffer: $5/channel × 50 = $250+/mo. Zernio gets cheaper per account as you grow; Buffer's per-channel pricing stays linear.\"},{\"title\":\"Published Rate Limits\",\"description\":\"Zernio: 60-1200 req/min by tier, publicly documented. Buffer: no published limits for the new API. Old API was 60 req/min.\"},{\"title\":\"2+ Years Battle-Tested\",\"description\":\"Zernio's API has been in production since 2023. Buffer's new API hasn't launched publicly yet. Maturity matters for production apps.\"}]},\"choose\":{\"label\":\"Which One?\",\"title\":\"API platform vs UI-only dashboard\",\"lateTitle\":\"Choose Zernio if you:\",\"lateItems\":[\"Need API automation today\",\"Can't wait for Buffer's API rebuild\",\"Want 7-15x lower costs at scale\",\"Value published uptime guarantees\",\"Need programmable posting for SaaS\",\"Want predictable, usage-based pricing that drops at scale\",\"Prefer instant API access\"],\"competitorTitle\":\"Stay with Buffer if you:\",\"competitorItems\":[\"Only need UI-based scheduling\",\"Value Buffer's world-class support\",\"Want AI writing assistance\",\"Don't need API access\",\"Prefer established brand reputation\",\"Can accept per-channel pricing\",\"Are willing to wait for API rebuild\"]},\"migration\":{\"title\":\"Need API automation?\",\"description\":\"If you're a Buffer user who needs API access, Zernio is your only option. Buffer's API doesn't exist publicly. Sign up for Zernio, copy your API key, and start automating - today, not \\\"someday.\\\"\",\"tip\":\"Zernio's free plan includes API access. Test it before you commit.\"},\"pricing\":{\"label\":\"Simple Pricing\",\"title\":\"Flat pricing vs per-channel chaos\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Common Questions\",\"items\":{\"hasBufferApi\":{\"question\":\"Does Buffer have an API?\",\"answer\":\"Not a public one. Buffer had a public API that served 47,000+ clients but deprecated it in 2019. In July 2025 they announced a new GraphQL API in early access, but as of late 2025 it's not publicly available - no signup, no public rate limits, no pricing, no SLA. For any production use today you need an alternative; Zernio is the closest drop-in with instant API access.\"},\"bufferApiAccess\":{\"question\":\"How do I get access to the Buffer API?\",\"answer\":\"You can't today. Buffer's new GraphQL API is invite-only early access with no public signup path. Their docs point you to a contact form. If you need API access now, Zernio gives you a production API key in 30 seconds on the free plan.\"},\"noApi\":{\"question\":\"Does Buffer really have no API?\",\"answer\":\"Correct - no public API. Buffer deprecated its public API in 2019 that served 47,000+ clients. They announced in July 2025 they're rebuilding a GraphQL API, but as of December 2025, it's only in early access, not publicly available. For production use, Zernio is the only option.\"},\"why\":{\"question\":\"Why did Buffer kill its API?\",\"answer\":\"Buffer cited Cambridge Analytica fallout (2018), compliance burden, and competitive concerns. They admitted they couldn't offer the developer experience customers deserved without massive investment. The practical result: 6+ years without a public API.\"},\"pricing\":{\"question\":\"How does Zernio compare to Buffer's per-channel pricing at scale?\",\"answer\":\"Buffer charges $5/channel flat, so 50 channels = $250+/mo. Zernio is usage-based with the first 2 accounts free, then $6/account (1-10), $3/account (11-100), $1/account for 101+ with no cap. 50 accounts on Zernio: $6×8 + $3×40 = $168/mo. The deeper you scale, the wider the gap.\"},\"whenBufferApi\":{\"question\":\"When will Buffer's new API launch?\",\"answer\":\"Buffer announced a 2025-2026 window but hasn't committed to a specific date. The API is in early access with no published rate limits, SLA, or pricing. If you need API access today, Zernio is the only production-ready option.\"},\"bufferUi\":{\"question\":\"Is Buffer better for UI-only use?\",\"answer\":\"For UI-focused teams who don't need API access, Buffer has an excellent reputation. Their visual calendar, AI assistant, and customer support are world-class. If you only need manual scheduling for 1-5 accounts, Buffer works well.\"},\"switching\":{\"question\":\"Can I switch from Buffer to Zernio easily?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Zernio's free plan includes API access so you can test before committing. The setup takes 30 seconds - sign up, copy your API key, and start posting. No waiting lists, no approval process.\"}}},\"final\":{\"title\":\"Ready for an API that exists?\",\"subtitle\":\"Start with the free plan. Get an instant API key. Don't wait for Buffer's \\\"coming soon.\\\"\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View Pricing\"},\"footnote\":\"No credit card required • Instant API key • 99.97% uptime SLA\"}},\"metricool\":{\"meta\":{\"title\":\"Metricool Alternative - The Choice for Builders | Zernio\",\"description\":\"Looking for a Metricool alternative with a powerful API? Zernio is a free social media API that offers posting, scheduling, analytics, and ads with one REST call.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Metricool Alternative - The Choice for Builders | Zernio\",\"ogDescription\":\"Zernio and Metricool serve different markets. Zernio is a posting API. Metricool is a planner/analytics suite.\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"The\",\"highlight\":\"Metricool Alternative\",\"subtitle\":\"Built API-First\",\"description\":\"Metricool is an all-in-one planner with analytics and reporting. Zernio is an API-first posting engine. They serve different markets - one isn't a replacement for the other.\",\"subtitle2\":\"No credit card required • Instant API key • API on free plan\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View API Docs\"}},\"keyInsight\":{\"title\":\"Key Insight: These Are NOT Direct Competitors\",\"description\":\"Zernio is API-first - the entire product is a unified posting API. Metricool is planner-first - a visual calendar with built-in analytics, and the API is secondary for data export. They serve fundamentally different needs.\",\"quote\":\"\\\"If you need deep reporting and a planning workspace, Metricool fits well. If you need a programmable posting layer you can integrate in minutes, Zernio is built for that.\\\"\",\"footnote\":\"Many teams use BOTH: Zernio for posting infrastructure, Metricool for planning and analytics.\"},\"comparison\":{\"label\":\"API-First vs Planner-First\",\"title\":\"Different philosophies, different strengths\",\"metricoolTitle\":\"Metricool Strengths\",\"metricoolItems\":[\"Visual content calendar - industry-leading planner\",\"Comprehensive analytics \u0026 reporting built-in\",\"Best time to post - AI-powered suggestions\",\"Competitor analysis and benchmarking\",\"White-label reporting for agencies\",\"Team approval workflows and permissions\",\"Ad performance tracking (Google, FB, TikTok)\"],\"lateTitle\":\"Zernio Strengths\",\"lateItems\":[\"Production API - core product, 2+ years battle-tested\",\"Instant API access on all plans (even free)\",\"Unified posting - one API call to all 15 platforms\",\"Published rate limits: 60-1200 req/min by tier\",\"99.97% uptime SLA - publicly documented\",\"Flat pricing by profiles - no surprise costs\",\"Unlimited team members on all paid plans\"],\"keyHighlight\":\"Key difference\",\"keyText\":\"Zernio's API is the core product. Metricool's API is for data export to Zapier/n8n - not for unified posting.\"},\"table\":{\"label\":\"Feature Comparison\",\"title\":\"Head-to-head comparison\",\"headers\":{\"feature\":\"Feature\",\"late\":\"Zernio\",\"metricool\":\"Metricool\"},\"rows\":[{\"feature\":\"Core product\",\"late\":\"Posting API\",\"metricool\":\"Planner + Analytics\"},{\"feature\":\"API access (free)\",\"late\":\"Yes\",\"metricool\":\"No ($67+ required)\"},{\"feature\":\"API purpose\",\"late\":\"Unified posting\",\"metricool\":\"Data export\"},{\"feature\":\"Rate limits\",\"late\":\"Published (60-1200/min)\",\"metricool\":\"Not published\"},{\"feature\":\"Uptime SLA\",\"late\":\"99.97%\",\"metricool\":\"Not published\"},{\"feature\":\"Visual calendar\",\"late\":\"Basic\",\"metricool\":\"Excellent\"},{\"feature\":\"Analytics\",\"late\":\"Bundled (no add-on)\",\"metricool\":\"Built-in\"},{\"feature\":\"Competitor analysis\",\"late\":\"No\",\"metricool\":\"Yes\"},{\"feature\":\"10 accounts + API\",\"late\":\"$$48/mo (usage-based, first 2 free)\",\"metricool\":\"$$20/mo Starter (5 brands)\"},{\"feature\":\"X/Twitter surcharge\",\"late\":\"Pass-through (no markup)\",\"metricool\":\"$$5/account\"},{\"feature\":\"Social Ads API\",\"late\":\"Yes\",\"metricool\":\"Limited (Meta, Google, TikTok)\"}]},\"apiLimitations\":{\"label\":\"API Reality Check\",\"title\":\"Metricool's API is for data export, not posting\",\"limitations\":{\"title\":\"Instagram API Limitations\",\"items\":[\"Cannot tag users/products in posts\",\"Cannot add carousel ads\",\"Cannot publish Stories (Creator only)\",\"Cannot create polls\",\"Cannot use GIFs\"]}},\"choose\":{\"label\":\"Which One?\",\"title\":\"Choose based on your primary need\",\"lateTitle\":\"Choose Zernio if you:\",\"lateItems\":[\"Build SaaS or need programmable posting\",\"Manage 10-50+ client accounts via API\",\"Value API reliability (99.97% SLA)\",\"Want instant API access (free tier included)\",\"Need unified cross-platform posting\",\"Prefer affordable at-scale pricing\",\"Can't wait hours for API integration\"],\"competitorTitle\":\"Choose Metricool if you:\",\"competitorItems\":[\"Need visual planning calendar for teams\",\"Require analytics + reporting built-in\",\"Want competitor analysis tools\",\"Need team approval workflows\",\"Value best-time-to-post AI suggestions\",\"Want white-label client reports\",\"Can accept per-brand pricing model\"]},\"complementary\":{\"title\":\"Use Both Together\",\"description\":\"Many teams use Zernio for posting infrastructure (API reliability, unified posting, SaaS integration) and Metricool for planning and analytics (visual calendar, reports, competitor analysis). They're complementary, not competitive.\",\"tip\":\"Zernio handles the posting. Metricool handles the planning and reporting.\"},\"pricing\":{\"label\":\"Pricing Comparison\",\"title\":\"Profile-based vs brand-based pricing\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Common Questions\",\"items\":{\"direct\":{\"question\":\"Are Zernio and Metricool direct competitors?\",\"answer\":\"No. Zernio is API-first - the entire product is a unified posting API. Metricool is planner-first with analytics and reporting. Their API is for data export, not unified posting. They serve different needs and are often used together.\"},\"apiAccess\":{\"question\":\"Does Metricool have a posting API?\",\"answer\":\"Metricool's API is for data export and Zapier/n8n integrations. It's gated to Advanced+ plans ($67+/mo) and doesn't offer unified cross-platform posting like Zernio does. Zernio's API is the core product with instant access on all plans.\"},\"useBoth\":{\"question\":\"Can I use Zernio and Metricool together?\",\"answer\":\"Absolutely. Many teams use Zernio for posting infrastructure (API reliability, unified posting, SaaS integration) and Metricool for planning and analytics (visual calendar, reports, competitor analysis). They're complementary.\"},\"pricing\":{\"question\":\"How does pricing compare?\",\"answer\":\"Zernio: usage-based, free up to 2 accounts, then $6/account (1-10), $3/account (11-100), $1/account for 101+ with no cap. API is included on every account at every tier. Metricool: $20/mo Starter for 5 brands (annual billing) with API gated behind Advanced+ ($67+). For pure posting API access, Zernio is far more affordable. For planner + analytics, Metricool's tiered approach is competitive.\"},\"twitter\":{\"question\":\"Does Metricool charge extra for X/Twitter?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Metricool charges $5/month per X/Twitter account on top of plan pricing. Zernio passes X's API cost through at cost - no markup, no hidden margin.\"},\"analytics\":{\"question\":\"Does Zernio include analytics?\",\"answer\":\"Yes - analytics are bundled with Zernio at no extra cost. For comprehensive analytics, competitor analysis, and white-label reporting, Metricool is still the better choice. Many teams pair Zernio's posting with Metricool's analytics.\"}}},\"final\":{\"title\":\"Need a posting API?\",\"subtitle\":\"Zernio is API-first. Instant access, 99.97% uptime SLA. Free plan includes API.\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View Pricing\"},\"footnote\":\"No credit card required • Instant API key • 99.97% uptime SLA\"}},\"ayrshare\":{\"meta\":{\"title\":\"Ayrshare Pricing 2026: $149-599/mo vs Zernio (free up to 2 accounts) | Compare\",\"description\":\"Ayrshare pricing in 2026: Free (20 posts, images only), Premium $149/mo, Launch $299/mo, Business $599/mo. Compare vs Zernio: usage-based, free up to 2 accounts then $6/$3/$1 per account, custom for 2,000+, unlimited team members. Overlapping platform coverage, plus paid ads on 6 ad networks.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Ayrshare Pricing 2026 vs Zernio: Full Cost Comparison\",\"ogDescription\":\"Ayrshare: $149-599/mo. Zernio: usage-based - free up to 2 accounts. Same platforms, far less cost. Unlimited team members included.\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"The\",\"highlight\":\"Ayrshare Alternative\",\"subtitle\":\"at up to 82% Less Cost\",\"description\":\"For an agency managing 30 client profiles, Zernio costs $108/month (usage-based, first 2 free). Ayrshare's Business plan? $599/month. That's 82% savings with overlapping platform coverage, plus paid-ad management that Ayrshare doesn't offer.\",\"subtitle2\":\"No credit card required\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View API Docs\"}},\"comparison\":{\"label\":\"Why Switch?\",\"title\":\"Same API power. Fraction of the cost.\",\"ayrshareTitle\":\"Ayrshare\",\"ayrshareItems\":[\"$$149/month Premium - video, analytics, single user\",\"$$299/month Launch - 10 profiles\",\"$$599/month Business - required for team access (30 profiles)\",\"Free tier: 20 posts/month, branded, images only\",\"Fair-use rate limits (thresholds unpublished)\",\"Multi-step developer setup process\",\"Dashboard is developer-focused, not client-facing\"],\"lateTitle\":\"Zernio\",\"lateItems\":[\"Free up to 2 social accounts - unlimited posts, full API\",\"Usage-based: $6/$3/$1 per account, custom for 2,000+, no fixed plans\",\"Unlimited team members at every account count\",\"30-second setup - instant API key, no approval\",\"Published rate limits: 60-1200 req/min by tier\",\"Client-facing calendar UI included\"],\"savingsHighlight\":\"82% cost savings\",\"savingsText\":\"for agencies managing 30+ client profiles ($108/mo usage-based vs $599/mo Business).\"},\"table\":{\"label\":\"Feature Comparison\",\"title\":\"Head-to-head comparison\",\"headers\":{\"feature\":\"Feature\",\"late\":\"Zernio\",\"competitor\":\"Ayrshare\"},\"rows\":[{\"feature\":\"Free tier\",\"late\":\"2 accounts, unlimited posts, full API\",\"competitor\":\"20 posts, branded, images only\"},{\"feature\":\"Entry price\",\"late\":\"$$6 first paid account (free up to 2)\",\"competitor\":\"$$149/mo (single user)\"},{\"feature\":\"50 accounts + unlimited posts\",\"late\":\"$$168/mo (usage-based)\",\"competitor\":\"$$599/mo (Business)\"},{\"feature\":\"Team access\",\"late\":\"Unlimited (all plans)\",\"competitor\":\"Business tier only\"},{\"feature\":\"Setup time\",\"late\":\"30 seconds\",\"competitor\":\"Multi-step developer setup\"},{\"feature\":\"Platforms\",\"late\":\"15\",\"competitor\":\"15 (same)\"},{\"feature\":\"Uptime SLA\",\"late\":\"99.97% (published)\",\"competitor\":\"\\\"High availability\\\"\"},{\"feature\":\"Rate limits\",\"late\":\"60-1200/min (published)\",\"competitor\":\"Fair use (unpublished)\"},{\"feature\":\"Client-facing UI\",\"late\":\"Calendar included\",\"competitor\":\"Dev dashboard only\"},{\"feature\":\"First comment scheduling\",\"late\":\"Yes\",\"competitor\":\"No\"},{\"feature\":\"Built-in analytics API\",\"late\":\"Bundled (no add-on)\",\"competitor\":\"Premium+ included\"},{\"feature\":\"Comment/DM management\",\"late\":\"No\",\"competitor\":\"Business tier\"},{\"feature\":\"Social Ads API\",\"late\":\"Yes\",\"ayrshare\":\"Facebook limited\"}]},\"features\":{\"label\":\"What You Get\",\"title\":\"Everything you need to post everywhere\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"Modern REST Architecture\",\"description\":\"Clean, predictable API design. Consistent patterns across all platforms. Auto-generated SDKs for major languages.\"},{\"title\":\"Published Rate Limits\",\"description\":\"Zernio: 60-1200 req/min by tier, documented. Ayrshare: Rates not publicly documented in the same detail.\"},{\"title\":\"99.97% Uptime SLA\",\"description\":\"Zernio publishes explicit uptime guarantees. Production-grade infrastructure built for reliability.\"},{\"title\":\"Instant API Access\",\"description\":\"Sign up, get your API key immediately. No credit card required for free tier. Start building in 30 seconds.\"},{\"title\":\"Usage-Based Pricing\",\"description\":\"Zernio: free up to 2 accounts, then $6/$3/$1 per account, custom for 2,000+. Unlimited posts at every tier - you only pay for connected accounts, not for activity.\"},{\"title\":\"Unified Cross-Platform Posting\",\"description\":\"One API call posts to all 15 platforms. Consistent response format, error handling, and media support.\"}]},\"choose\":{\"label\":\"Which One?\",\"title\":\"Choose based on what you're building\",\"lateTitle\":\"Choose Zernio if you:\",\"lateItems\":[\"Want instant API access (no credit card required)\",\"Want usage-based pricing that scales with you\",\"Value modern REST architecture\",\"Require published rate limits and SLA\",\"Building SaaS or automation tools\",\"Need unified cross-platform posting\",\"Prefer transparent, simple pricing\"],\"competitorTitle\":\"Choose Ayrshare if you:\",\"competitorItems\":[\"Need RSS automation built-in\",\"Want AI caption generation\",\"Require Google Business Profile support\",\"Prefer usage-based pricing model\",\"Need link shortening included\",\"Want comment management features\",\"Can accept variable monthly costs\"]},\"migration\":{\"title\":\"Switching from Ayrshare?\",\"description\":\"Already using the Ayrshare SDK? Just swap the npm package. Our drop-in replacement SDK has identical method signatures, so you only change the import and API key. Zero code changes required.\",\"sdkCode\":\"npm uninstall social-media-api\\nnpm install @zernio/social-media-api\",\"tip\":\"The SDK supports all 51 Ayrshare methods. 34 are fully implemented, the rest return clear 501 responses as Zernio adds support.\",\"guideLink\":\"View SDK on npm\",\"guideLinkUrl\":\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@zernio/social-media-api\",\"docsLink\":\"Read the migration guide\",\"docsLinkUrl\":\"https://docs.zernio.com/resources/migrations/migrating-from-ayrshare\"},\"pricing\":{\"label\":\"Simple Pricing\",\"title\":\"No per-seat fees. No surprises.\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Common Questions\",\"items\":{\"howHard\":{\"question\":\"How hard is it to switch from Ayrshare?\",\"answer\":\"About 30 seconds to get your API key, then 15 minutes to migrate. Zernio uses standard REST patterns with a single unified endpoint. If you've integrated with Ayrshare, you'll find Zernio simpler. Most of your existing code structure works with minimal changes.\"},\"platforms\":{\"question\":\"Does Zernio support all the platforms I need?\",\"answer\":\"Zernio supports 15 platforms: Instagram, TikTok, X, LinkedIn, Facebook, YouTube, Threads, Reddit, Pinterest, Bluesky, Google Business, Telegram, Snapchat, WhatsApp, and Discord. Ayrshare covers most of the same platforms minus Discord and WhatsApp. Zernio also adds paid-ad management on Meta Ads, Google Ads, TikTok Ads, LinkedIn Ads, Pinterest Ads, and X Ads, which Ayrshare doesn't support. Together that's enough coverage for 95%+ of commercial social-media use.\"},\"whyCheaper\":{\"question\":\"Why is Zernio so much cheaper?\",\"answer\":\"We focus on reliable multi-platform posting. Ayrshare bundles analytics, comment management, DMs, auto-hashtags, and media libraries - features many teams don't need. We keep our scope focused, which keeps prices low. Plus, unlimited team members are included on all paid plans.\"},\"videoFree\":{\"question\":\"Can I post videos on Zernio's free plan?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Video posting is included on all plans, including free. Ayrshare's free tier only supports images - video requires the $149/month Premium tier.\"},\"analytics\":{\"question\":\"What about analytics?\",\"answer\":\"Analytics are bundled with Zernio - no add-on, no extra fee. If you're building in-app analytics dashboards, Ayrshare's built-in analytics APIs (included on Premium+) are still richer. For most teams, Zernio's bundled analytics plus native platform tools cover the job at a fraction of the cost.\"},\"reliability\":{\"question\":\"Is Zernio reliable enough for production?\",\"answer\":\"We publish a 99.97% uptime SLA and have delivered millions of posts. Our rate limits are documented (60-1200 req/min by tier). Ayrshare advertises \\\"high availability\\\" without specific numbers and uses fair-use rate limits with unpublished thresholds.\"}}},\"final\":{\"title\":\"Ready to switch?\",\"subtitle\":\"Start with the free plan. No credit card required. See why agencies save up to 82% by switching from Ayrshare.\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View Pricing\"},\"footnote\":\"No credit card required • Free plan available • Cancel anytime\"}},\"postbridge\":{\"meta\":{\"title\":\"No API Add-on Fees | Postbridge Alternative 2026\",\"description\":\"Looking for a Postbridge alternative? Zernio is API-first with 99.97% uptime SLA. No API add-on fees. Free up to 2 accounts, usage-based pricing beyond that.\",\"ogTitle\":\"No API Add-on Fees | Postbridge Alternative 2026\",\"ogDescription\":\"Switch from Postbridge to Zernio. 99.97% uptime SLA, no cross-posting restrictions, API included in all plans.\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"The\",\"highlight\":\"Postbridge Alternative\",\"subtitle\":\"Without Cross-Posting Restrictions\",\"description\":\"Postbridge is a UI scheduler with an API tacked on. Zernio is API-first with a 99.97% uptime SLA. No $5/mo API add-on, no cross-posting restrictions. Free up to 2 accounts, usage-based after that.\",\"subtitle2\":\"No credit card required • Free up to 2 accounts • API included\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View API Docs\"}},\"fatalFlaw\":{\"title\":\"The Fatal Flaw: Cross-Posting Restrictions\",\"description\":\"Postbridge blocks posting the same content to multiple accounts on the same platform. If you manage 5 franchise Instagram accounts and want to post the same promo - Postbridge won't let you.\",\"quote\":\"Post Bridge restricts posting identical content to multiple accounts on the same social media platform to protect all users from losing API access...\",\"footnote\":\"Zernio has zero such restrictions. You control what you post where.\"},\"comparison\":{\"label\":\"API-First vs UI-First\",\"title\":\"Built for developers vs built for creators\",\"postbridgeTitle\":\"Postbridge\",\"postbridgeItems\":[\"API is $5/mo add-on on top of $29-49/mo base plan\",\"No free tier - 7-day trial only\",\"No published uptime SLA or status page\",\"Cross-posting to multiple accounts blocked\",\"Rate limits undocumented (100 posts/hour max)\",\"No documented webhook support\",\"API \\\"finally live\\\" in 2025 - recently launched\"],\"lateTitle\":\"Zernio\",\"lateItems\":[\"API included in all plans - no add-on fees\",\"Free tier: 2 social accounts, unlimited posts, full API\",\"99.97% uptime SLA - publicly documented\",\"No cross-posting restrictions - you're in control\",\"Published rate limits: 60-1200 req/min by tier\",\"Webhook support on all plans\",\"Production-proven 2+ years, thousands of developers\"],\"savingsHighlight\":\"Free up to 2 accounts\",\"savingsText\":\"with full API access on every account. Postbridge is cheaper at 10 accounts ($34/mo vs $48/mo on Zernio), but charges a $5/mo API add-on on top of the $29/mo plan, blocks cross-posting, and lacks a real free tier.\"},\"table\":{\"label\":\"Feature Comparison\",\"title\":\"Head-to-head comparison\",\"headers\":{\"feature\":\"Feature\",\"late\":\"Zernio\",\"competitor\":\"Postbridge\"},\"rows\":[{\"feature\":\"API access\",\"late\":\"All plans (free included)\",\"competitor\":\"$$5/mo add-on\"},{\"feature\":\"Free tier\",\"late\":\"2 accounts, unlimited posts\",\"competitor\":\"7-day trial only\"},{\"feature\":\"Entry price (API)\",\"late\":\"Free up to 2 accounts (then $6/account)\",\"competitor\":\"$$34/mo ($29+$5)\"},{\"feature\":\"Uptime SLA\",\"late\":\"99.97% (published)\",\"competitor\":\"Not published\"},{\"feature\":\"Cross-posting\",\"late\":\"No restrictions\",\"competitor\":\"Blocked same-platform\"},{\"feature\":\"Rate limits\",\"late\":\"60-1200/min (published)\",\"competitor\":\"100/hour (system limit)\"},{\"feature\":\"Webhook support\",\"late\":\"All paid plans\",\"competitor\":\"Not documented\"},{\"feature\":\"API maturity\",\"late\":\"2+ years production\",\"competitor\":\"Recently launched (2025)\"},{\"feature\":\"AI content\",\"late\":\"No\",\"competitor\":\"Yes (built-in)\"},{\"feature\":\"Desktop app\",\"late\":\"No\",\"competitor\":\"Yes (macOS/Windows)\"},{\"feature\":\"Social Ads API\",\"late\":\"Yes\",\"postbridge\":\"No\"}]},\"features\":{\"label\":\"Production-Ready API\",\"title\":\"Built for developers who ship\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"Instant API Access\",\"description\":\"Sign up, get API key, start posting. No waiting for activation, no manual review process. Live in 30 seconds.\"},{\"title\":\"Published Rate Limits\",\"description\":\"60-1200 req/min by tier, documented publicly. No guessing, no surprise throttling mid-campaign.\"},{\"title\":\"99.97% Uptime SLA\",\"description\":\"Explicit uptime guarantees. Postbridge doesn't publish comparable SLA metrics.\"},{\"title\":\"No API Add-on Fee\",\"description\":\"API included on all plans, including free. Postbridge requires $5/mo add-on for API access.\"},{\"title\":\"Cross-Platform Posting\",\"description\":\"Post to multiple platforms in one API call. Postbridge blocks cross-posting on some platforms.\"},{\"title\":\"Modern REST Design\",\"description\":\"Clean, predictable patterns. Consistent error handling. Auto-generated SDKs available.\"}]},\"choose\":{\"label\":\"Which One?\",\"title\":\"API developers vs content creators\",\"lateTitle\":\"Choose Zernio if you:\",\"lateItems\":[\"Need production-ready API infrastructure\",\"Want transparent, published rate limits\",\"Require 99.97% uptime SLA guarantee\",\"Building SaaS or developer tools\",\"Value instant API access on all plans\",\"Need cross-platform posting without blocks\",\"Prefer transparent usage-based pricing\"],\"competitorTitle\":\"Choose Postbridge if you:\",\"competitorItems\":[\"Want lifetime deal pricing option\",\"Need AI content generation built-in\",\"Prefer desktop app experience\",\"Require n8n/Make/Zapier templates\",\"Can accept $5/mo API add-on cost\",\"Don't need cross-platform posting\",\"Value media management tools\"]},\"migration\":{\"title\":\"Switching from Postbridge?\",\"description\":\"Zernio's API is simpler than Postbridge's. Sign up (free), get your instant API key, reconnect your social accounts via OAuth, and update your endpoint URL. Most developers are live in under 30 minutes.\",\"tip\":\"The biggest difference: Zernio's API just works. No $5 add-on, no cross-posting blocks, no guessing about rate limits.\"},\"pricing\":{\"label\":\"Simple Pricing\",\"title\":\"API included. No add-on fees.\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Common Questions\",\"items\":{\"whyNotPostbridge\":{\"question\":\"Why choose Zernio over Postbridge?\",\"answer\":\"Postbridge is a UI-first scheduler that added an API as an afterthought. Zernio is API-first - our entire business depends on API reliability. We have a 99.97% uptime SLA, published rate limits, webhooks on all plans, and no cross-posting restrictions. Plus, API access is included in all plans instead of a $5/mo add-on.\"},\"crossPosting\":{\"question\":\"What's the cross-posting restriction about?\",\"answer\":\"Postbridge blocks you from posting the same content to multiple accounts on the same platform. This breaks legitimate use cases like franchise operations or multi-brand portfolios. Zernio has no such restriction - you control what you post where.\"},\"pricing\":{\"question\":\"How does pricing compare?\",\"answer\":\"Postbridge's $29/mo Creator plan requires a $5/mo API add-on = $34/mo just for 1-10 accounts. Zernio is usage-based with API included on every account: free up to 2 accounts, then $6/account (1-10), $3/account (11-100), $1/account for 101+ with no cap. 10 accounts on Zernio: $48/mo. Postbridge can be cheaper at certain scales, but Zernio gives you a real free tier, no $5 add-on gate, no cross-posting blocks, and a 99.97% SLA.\"},\"reliability\":{\"question\":\"Is Zernio more reliable than Postbridge?\",\"answer\":\"Zernio publishes a 99.97% uptime SLA and has rate limits documented by tier (60-1200 req/min). Postbridge has no published SLA, no status page, and only documents \\\"100 posts/hour per user\\\" as system protection. For production apps, this transparency matters.\"},\"webhooks\":{\"question\":\"Does Zernio support webhooks?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, webhooks are included on all paid plans. You get real-time status updates for post events (pending, published, failed). Postbridge has no documented webhook support.\"},\"maturity\":{\"question\":\"How mature is Zernio's API vs Postbridge?\",\"answer\":\"Zernio's API has been production-proven for 2+ years with thousands of developers. Postbridge's API was \\\"finally live\\\" in 2025 per their founder's tweet - it was previously in closed beta. Zernio's entire business model depends on API reliability; Postbridge's is UI scheduling.\"}}},\"final\":{\"title\":\"Ready for a real API?\",\"subtitle\":\"Start with the free plan. No credit card required. See why developers choose Zernio over Postbridge.\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View Pricing\"},\"footnote\":\"No credit card required • Free plan available • API included\"}},\"blotato\":{\"meta\":{\"title\":\"The Blotato Alternative for Developers | 2026\",\"description\":\"Looking for a Blotato alternative? Zernio is API-first with 99.97% uptime SLA. No TikTok throttling, 40x faster rate limits. Free up to 2 accounts, usage-based pricing beyond.\",\"ogTitle\":\"The Blotato Alternative for Developers | 2026\",\"ogDescription\":\"Switch from Blotato to Zernio. 99.97% uptime SLA, no TikTok account limits, 1200 req/min vs 30 req/min.\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"The\",\"highlight\":\"Blotato Alternative\",\"subtitle\":\"For Developers\",\"description\":\"Blotato is an AI content studio with posting bolted on. Zernio is API-first with 99.97% uptime SLA. No TikTok throttling, 40x faster rate limits, and free up to 2 accounts before usage-based pricing kicks in.\",\"subtitle2\":\"No credit card required • Free up to 2 accounts • API included\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View API Docs\"}},\"fatalFlaw\":{\"title\":\"The Fatal Flaw: TikTok Account Throttling\",\"description\":\"Blotato's Starter plan ($29/mo) limits you to posting to only 3 TikTok accounts per 24 hours. Even if you have 20 accounts connected, you can only touch 3 per day. It takes 6+ days to post to all your accounts once.\",\"quote\":\"TikTok (Starter Plan): 3 unique accounts per 24h, 10 posts per account\",\"footnote\":\"Zernio has zero such restrictions. Post to unlimited TikTok accounts at 60-1200 posts/min.\"},\"comparison\":{\"label\":\"Posting API vs Content Studio\",\"title\":\"Built for reliability vs built for creation\",\"blotatoTitle\":\"Blotato\",\"blotatoItems\":[\"$$29/mo Starter - includes AI credits you may not need\",\"30 posts/min global rate limit (undocumented)\",\"TikTok: 3 accounts per 24h on Starter plan\",\"No published uptime SLA or status page\",\"API recently launched from closed beta\",\"Designed for n8n/Make, not standalone REST\",\"Trustpilot complaints about platform stability\"],\"lateTitle\":\"Zernio\",\"lateItems\":[\"Free up to 2 accounts, then usage-based - pure posting, no bundled AI\",\"60-1200 req/min by tier (published, enforced)\",\"Zero TikTok restrictions - unlimited accounts\",\"99.97% uptime SLA - publicly documented\",\"2+ years production-tested, 2.3M+ posts delivered\",\"Standalone REST API - no n8n/Make dependency\",\"Enterprise-grade reliability guarantees\"],\"savingsHighlight\":\"40x faster rate limits\",\"savingsText\":\"and free up to 2 accounts - usage-based pricing beats Blotato's $29/mo flat AI bundle for pure posting.\"},\"table\":{\"label\":\"Feature Comparison\",\"title\":\"Head-to-head comparison\",\"headers\":{\"feature\":\"Feature\",\"late\":\"Zernio\",\"competitor\":\"Blotato\"},\"rows\":[{\"feature\":\"Core product\",\"late\":\"Posting API\",\"competitor\":\"AI Content Studio\"},{\"feature\":\"Entry price\",\"late\":\"Free up to 2 accounts (then $6/account)\",\"competitor\":\"$$29/mo\"},{\"feature\":\"Rate limits\",\"late\":\"60-1200/min\",\"competitor\":\"1.5 posts/min\"},{\"feature\":\"TikTok accounts\",\"late\":\"No daily cap\",\"competitor\":\"3/day (Starter)\"},{\"feature\":\"Uptime SLA\",\"late\":\"99.97% (published)\",\"competitor\":\"Not published\"},{\"feature\":\"API type\",\"late\":\"Standalone REST\",\"competitor\":\"n8n/Make focused\"},{\"feature\":\"Free tier\",\"late\":\"Yes (2 accounts, unlimited posts)\",\"competitor\":\"No\"},{\"feature\":\"AI content\",\"late\":\"No\",\"competitor\":\"Yes (included)\"},{\"feature\":\"Production track record\",\"late\":\"2+ years\",\"competitor\":\"Recently launched\"},{\"feature\":\"Desktop app\",\"late\":\"No\",\"competitor\":\"Yes (macOS)\"},{\"feature\":\"Social Ads API\",\"late\":\"Yes\",\"blotato\":\"No\"}]},\"features\":{\"label\":\"Production-Ready API\",\"title\":\"Built for developers who ship\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"40x Faster Rate Limits\",\"description\":\"Zernio: 60 req/min on free tier. Blotato: 1.5 posts/min. For high-volume posting, Zernio wins by a massive margin.\"},{\"title\":\"Pure REST API\",\"description\":\"Direct API access without n8n/Make middleware. Blotato requires automation platform setup for API-like usage.\"},{\"title\":\"Published Limits\",\"description\":\"60-1200 req/min by tier, documented publicly. Blotato's limits are buried in different contexts.\"},{\"title\":\"99.97% Uptime SLA\",\"description\":\"Explicit uptime guarantees for production reliability. Blotato doesn't publish comparable metrics.\"},{\"title\":\"Instant API Key\",\"description\":\"Sign up, Settings → API, copy key. 30 seconds. No waiting for activation or approval.\"},{\"title\":\"API on Free Tier\",\"description\":\"Full API access included on free plan. Blotato's API requires paid automation platform.\"}]},\"choose\":{\"label\":\"Which One?\",\"title\":\"Posting infrastructure vs content studio\",\"lateTitle\":\"Choose Zernio if you:\",\"lateItems\":[\"Need API-first posting infrastructure\",\"Want 40x faster rate limits (60/min vs 1.5/min)\",\"Require transparent, published limits\",\"Building SaaS or automation tools\",\"Value production-grade reliability\",\"Need instant API access (free tier)\",\"Prefer pure REST without n8n/Make setup\"],\"competitorTitle\":\"Choose Blotato if you:\",\"competitorItems\":[\"Need AI content generation suite\",\"Want visual content studio experience\",\"Prefer macOS desktop app\",\"Require thread/carousel design tools\",\"Can accept 1.5 posts/min rate limit\",\"Value all-in-one content creation\",\"Don't need direct API access\"]},\"migration\":{\"title\":\"Switching from Blotato?\",\"description\":\"Zernio's API is simpler than Blotato's. No n8n/Make setup required - just pure REST. Sign up (free), get your instant API key, reconnect your social accounts, and start posting. Most developers are live in under 30 minutes.\",\"tip\":\"The biggest difference: Zernio is posting infrastructure, not a content studio. If you have content elsewhere, you can run on the free tier (2 accounts) or only pay for the accounts you actually connect.\"},\"pricing\":{\"label\":\"Simple Pricing\",\"title\":\"Pay for posting, not AI credits.\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Common Questions\",\"items\":{\"whyNotBlotato\":{\"question\":\"Why choose Zernio over Blotato?\",\"answer\":\"Blotato is a content studio first, posting platform second. Zernio is API-first - our entire business depends on posting reliability. We have a 99.97% uptime SLA, published rate limits (60-1200 req/min vs Blotato's 30 req/min), and no TikTok account throttling. Plus, you pay for posting only, not bundled AI credits.\"},\"tiktokThrottling\":{\"question\":\"What's the TikTok throttling about?\",\"answer\":\"Blotato's Starter plan ($29/mo) limits you to posting to only 3 TikTok accounts per 24 hours. Even with 20 accounts connected, you can only touch 3 per day. Agencies managing multiple TikTok accounts find this unusable. Zernio has zero such restrictions - post to unlimited TikTok accounts.\"},\"pricing\":{\"question\":\"How is Zernio cheaper if Blotato has more features?\",\"answer\":\"Blotato's $29/mo bundles AI generation credits (image/video creation) that you may not need. If you already have content and just need posting, you're paying for unused features. Zernio is usage-based: free up to 2 accounts, then $6/account (1-10), $3/account (11-100), $1/account for 101+ with no cap. For most teams that's far cheaper than Blotato's flat $29/mo AI bundle.\"},\"rateLimits\":{\"question\":\"What about rate limits?\",\"answer\":\"Zernio publishes clear rate limits, scaling from 60 req/min on the free tier up to 1200 req/min for high-volume customers. Blotato caps at 30 posts/min globally, regardless of plan - up to a 40x difference at scale. For production SaaS, this matters enormously.\"},\"reliability\":{\"question\":\"Is Zernio more reliable than Blotato?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Zernio publishes a 99.97% uptime SLA backed by 2.3 million posts delivered. Blotato has no published SLA or status page, and Trustpilot reviews cite platform stability issues, integration failures, and support wait times exceeding 48 hours.\"},\"n8nDependency\":{\"question\":\"Does Zernio require n8n or Make?\",\"answer\":\"No. Zernio is a standalone REST API - you control retry logic, error handling, and orchestration directly in your code. Blotato's API is designed for n8n/Make workflows, which adds latency, cost stacking, and vendor lock-in. Zernio has zero such dependencies.\"}}},\"final\":{\"title\":\"Ready for real API reliability?\",\"subtitle\":\"Start with the free plan. No credit card required. See why developers choose Zernio over Blotato.\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View Pricing\"},\"footnote\":\"No credit card required • Free plan available • 99.97% uptime SLA\"}},\"hootsuite\":{\"meta\":{\"title\":\"Free up to 2 accounts | Hootsuite Alternative 2026\",\"description\":\"Looking for a Hootsuite alternative? Zernio is dramatically cheaper with instant API access. Free up to 2 accounts, then usage-based pricing - vs Hootsuite's $99/mo minimum. No approval process, no per-user fees.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Free up to 2 accounts | Hootsuite Alternative 2026\",\"ogDescription\":\"Switch from Hootsuite to Zernio. Instant API access, 99.97% uptime SLA, usage-based pricing vs $99/mo minimum.\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"The\",\"highlight\":\"Hootsuite Alternative\",\"subtitle\":\"Without $99/mo Minimums\",\"description\":\"Hootsuite is a 17-year-old enterprise dashboard where the API is an outdated afterthought. Zernio is API-first with instant access. Free up to 2 accounts, usage-based after that, modern architecture, no approval process.\",\"subtitle2\":\"No credit card required • Instant API key • No approval process\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View API Docs\"}},\"fatalFlaw\":{\"title\":\"The Fatal Flaw: API Requires Approval\",\"description\":\"Hootsuite requires you to register as a developer, create an application, submit for API access approval, and wait for Hootsuite support to activate your access. This takes hours to days. Zernio gives you an API key in 30 seconds.\",\"quote\":\"To activate API access for your Hootsuite application, contact Hootsuite support.\",\"footnote\":\"Zernio: Sign up → Settings → API → Copy key. Total time: 30 seconds.\"},\"comparison\":{\"label\":\"Modern API vs Legacy Dashboard\",\"title\":\"API-first vs dashboard-first\",\"hootsuiteTitle\":\"Hootsuite\",\"hootsuiteItems\":[\"$$99/mo minimum - often requires $15,000+/year Enterprise\",\"API requires developer registration + approval process\",\"Per-user fees: $35-45/user/month on top of base plan\",\"Legacy API architecture - \\\"hasn't kept up with the times\\\"\",\"TikTok not supported in API (only in dashboard)\",\"Complex OAuth 2.0 only - no simple API key auth\",\"No published uptime SLA\"],\"lateTitle\":\"Zernio\",\"lateItems\":[\"Free up to 2 accounts, usage-based after - API included, no hidden costs\",\"Instant API key - no approval, no waiting\",\"Unlimited team members on ALL paid plans\",\"Modern REST API - actively maintained, current platforms\",\"TikTok, Threads, all 15 platforms fully supported\",\"Simple API key auth - no OAuth dance required\",\"99.97% uptime SLA - publicly documented\"],\"savingsHighlight\":\"Dramatically cheaper\",\"savingsText\":\"with instant API access - free up to 2 accounts then usage-based, vs Hootsuite's $99/mo minimum (often $15,000+/year for Enterprise).\"},\"table\":{\"label\":\"Feature Comparison\",\"title\":\"Head-to-head comparison\",\"headers\":{\"feature\":\"Feature\",\"late\":\"Zernio\",\"hootsuite\":\"Hootsuite\"},\"rows\":[{\"feature\":\"Entry price\",\"late\":\"Free up to 2 accounts (API included)\",\"hootsuite\":\"$$99/mo (API often gated)\"},{\"feature\":\"Enterprise scale\",\"late\":\"$$1/account at any scale, self-service\",\"hootsuite\":\"$$15,000+/year\"},{\"feature\":\"API access\",\"late\":\"Instant (30 seconds)\",\"hootsuite\":\"Approval required (hours/days)\"},{\"feature\":\"Per-user fees\",\"late\":\"None (unlimited team)\",\"hootsuite\":\"$$35-45/user/month\"},{\"feature\":\"Uptime SLA\",\"late\":\"99.97% (published)\",\"hootsuite\":\"Not published\"},{\"feature\":\"API architecture\",\"late\":\"Modern REST\",\"hootsuite\":\"Legacy (\\\"outdated\\\")\"},{\"feature\":\"TikTok in API\",\"late\":\"Yes\",\"hootsuite\":\"No (UI only)\"},{\"feature\":\"Threads support\",\"late\":\"Yes (added quickly)\",\"hootsuite\":\"API lags behind\"},{\"feature\":\"Authentication\",\"late\":\"Simple API key\",\"hootsuite\":\"OAuth 2.0 only\"},{\"feature\":\"Free tier\",\"late\":\"Yes (2 accounts, unlimited posts)\",\"hootsuite\":\"Eliminated in 2021\"},{\"feature\":\"Social listening\",\"late\":\"No\",\"hootsuite\":\"Yes (Enterprise)\"},{\"feature\":\"Approval workflows\",\"late\":\"No\",\"hootsuite\":\"Yes (Enterprise)\"},{\"feature\":\"Social Ads API\",\"late\":\"Yes\",\"hootsuite\":\"No\"}]},\"features\":{\"label\":\"Modern API Architecture\",\"title\":\"Built for today's developers\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"30-Second Integration\",\"description\":\"Sign up, Settings → API, copy key. Done. Hootsuite requires developer registration, OAuth setup, and approval.\"},{\"title\":\"Published Rate Limits\",\"description\":\"Zernio: 60-1200 req/min by tier. Hootsuite: Rate limits exist but aren't as clearly documented for all scenarios.\"},{\"title\":\"99.97% Uptime SLA\",\"description\":\"Explicit uptime guarantees. Hootsuite's API reliability depends on your Enterprise tier.\"},{\"title\":\"No Per-User Fees\",\"description\":\"Unlimited team members on all paid plans. Hootsuite charges per seat, per month.\"},{\"title\":\"Massive Cost Savings\",\"description\":\"Usage-based vs $99-15,000+/mo. Same API functionality, fraction of the cost. Pay only for the accounts you connect.\"},{\"title\":\"Active API Maintenance\",\"description\":\"Zernio's API keeps pace with platform changes. Hootsuite's API often lags new features.\"}]},\"choose\":{\"label\":\"Which One?\",\"title\":\"API platform vs enterprise dashboard\",\"lateTitle\":\"Choose Zernio if you:\",\"lateItems\":[\"Need production-grade API for posting (not dashboard)\",\"Want fast integration (30 seconds vs hours/days)\",\"Require transparent, affordable pricing (free up to 2 accounts, usage-based after)\",\"Building SaaS platform or white-label solution\",\"Value modern API architecture and active maintenance\",\"Cannot wait for \\\"API activation approval\\\"\",\"Need unlimited team members without per-user fees\"],\"competitorTitle\":\"Choose Hootsuite if you:\",\"competitorItems\":[\"Need all-in-one enterprise dashboard (not API)\",\"Require social listening and brand monitoring\",\"Want complex approval workflows\",\"Have 20+ marketing team members needing UI access\",\"Budget is $15,000+/year minimum\",\"Prefer established brand (17+ years) over modern tech\",\"Can tolerate outdated API that lags platform changes\"]},\"migration\":{\"title\":\"Switching from Hootsuite?\",\"description\":\"Zernio is dramatically simpler than Hootsuite's API. No developer registration, no approval process, no OAuth complexity. Sign up, copy your API key from Settings, and start posting. Most developers are live in under 15 minutes.\",\"tip\":\"The cost savings alone justify switching: free up to 2 accounts, then $6/account vs Hootsuite's $99/mo minimum - and no per-user fees ever.\"},\"pricing\":{\"label\":\"Simple Pricing\",\"title\":\"No per-user fees. No hidden costs.\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Common Questions\",\"items\":{\"hasHootsuiteApi\":{\"question\":\"Does Hootsuite have an API?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, but access is gated. You need to register as a developer, create an application, submit for approval, and wait for Hootsuite support to activate access. The API itself is widely described as legacy and lags behind new platforms (TikTok is dashboard-only, not in the API). For most teams a modern alternative like Zernio is faster - instant API key, no approval process, and full support for TikTok, Threads, and all 15 platforms.\"},\"hootsuiteApiCost\":{\"question\":\"How much does the Hootsuite API cost?\",\"answer\":\"Hootsuite doesn't publish API-specific pricing; API access effectively requires at least a Team plan ($99/mo minimum) and in practice production API use often pushes teams to the Enterprise tier ($15,000+/year) because of rate limits and support needs. Zernio is free up to 2 accounts, then usage-based ($6/$3/$1 per account, custom for 2,000+) with full API included on every account - dramatically cheaper, no per-user fees.\"},\"whyNotHootsuite\":{\"question\":\"Why choose Zernio over Hootsuite?\",\"answer\":\"Hootsuite is a 17-year-old enterprise dashboard where the API is a neglected afterthought. Reviews describe it as \\\"legacy\\\" and \\\"outdated.\\\" Zernio is API-first - our entire business depends on API reliability. We offer instant access (30 seconds vs hours/days), modern architecture, and dramatically lower pricing (free up to 2 accounts, usage-based after that vs $99/mo minimum).\"},\"apiApproval\":{\"question\":\"What's the Hootsuite API approval process about?\",\"answer\":\"Hootsuite requires developer registration, application creation, and approval from Hootsuite support to activate API access. This takes hours to days. Zernio gives you an API key in 30 seconds - sign up, go to Settings, copy your key, done.\"},\"pricing\":{\"question\":\"How does pricing compare to Hootsuite?\",\"answer\":\"Zernio is usage-based with the first 2 social accounts free (full API included). Beyond that: $6/account (1-10), $3/account (11-100), $1/account for 101+ with no cap. Unlimited team members at every tier. Hootsuite starts at $99/mo and charges $35-45/user/month on top. For a team of 5, Hootsuite costs $274-324/mo before you add extra profiles. For Enterprise (often required for API access), Hootsuite is $15,000+/year.\"},\"tiktok\":{\"question\":\"Does Hootsuite's API support TikTok?\",\"answer\":\"No. Hootsuite's API doesn't support TikTok even though their dashboard does. The API has lagged behind platform changes for years - when Threads launched, Zernio added support quickly while Hootsuite's API still struggles to keep up.\"},\"reliability\":{\"question\":\"Is Zernio more reliable than Hootsuite?\",\"answer\":\"Zernio publishes a 99.97% uptime SLA. Hootsuite publishes no uptime guarantees, and Ayrshare's review notes \\\"reports of the API being down for hours or even days.\\\" For production apps, Zernio's published SLA and modern architecture provide confidence Hootsuite can't match.\"},\"enterprise\":{\"question\":\"What about Hootsuite's enterprise features?\",\"answer\":\"Hootsuite offers social listening, approval workflows, and comprehensive dashboards - features Zernio doesn't have. If you're an enterprise marketing team with 20+ users who need dashboard access and a $15,000+/year budget, Hootsuite makes sense. For API posting, Zernio is the clear choice.\"}}},\"final\":{\"title\":\"Ready for a modern API?\",\"subtitle\":\"Start with the free plan. No credit card required. See why developers choose Zernio over Hootsuite.\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View Pricing\"},\"footnote\":\"No credit card required • Instant API key • 99.97% uptime SLA\"}},\"publer\":{\"meta\":{\"title\":\"Free API Access (Publer: $21/mo) | Publer Alternative 2026\",\"description\":\"Looking for a Publer alternative? Zernio is API-first with instant access on every plan, free up to 2 accounts, and pay only for what you use beyond that. Per-account rate drops to $1 past 100 accounts.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Free API Access (Publer: $21/mo) | Publer Alternative 2026\",\"ogDescription\":\"Switch from Publer to Zernio. No $21/mo API paywall, 12x faster rate limits, 99.97% uptime SLA.\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"The\",\"highlight\":\"Publer Alternative\",\"subtitle\":\"With API on Every Plan\",\"description\":\"Publer is a 12-year-old UI dashboard that only recently added an API as a high-tier add-on. Zernio is API-first with instant access on all plans. Dramatically cheaper at scale, 12x faster rate limits.\",\"subtitle2\":\"No credit card required • Instant API key • Free plan with API access\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View API Docs\"}},\"fatalFlaw\":{\"title\":\"The Fatal Flaw: API Requires $21+/mo Business Plan\",\"description\":\"Publer gates API access to Business and Enterprise tiers. You cannot prototype or experiment without paying $21+/month minimum. Zernio provides instant API access on ALL plans - including the free tier.\",\"quote\":\"\\\"The Publer API is available exclusively to Business and Enterprise customers.\\\"\",\"footnote\":\"Zernio: Sign up → Settings → API → Copy key. Free plan included. Total time: 30 seconds.\"},\"comparison\":{\"label\":\"API-First vs Dashboard-First\",\"title\":\"Built for developers vs bolted-on API\",\"publerTitle\":\"Publer\",\"publerItems\":[\"API requires $21+/mo Business plan - no free access\",\"Business: $21/mo base + per-account add-on (rate scales with volume; 50 accounts typically lands $200–$350/mo)\",\"API launched 2025 - less than 1 year in production\",\"50 requests/minute global cap - no tier scaling\",\"No published uptime SLA or guarantees\",\"Per-account pricing scales linearly with each extra account on Business\",\"Per-user fees ($3/user) for team members\"],\"lateTitle\":\"Zernio\",\"lateItems\":[\"API access on ALL plans - including free tier\",\"$$168/mo for 50 accounts - usage-based, first 2 free\",\"API production-tested since 2023 - 2+ years mature\",\"Up to 600 req/min for high volume - 12x Publer's limit\",\"99.97% uptime SLA - publicly documented\",\"Tiered usage-based pricing - cost per account drops as you scale\",\"Unlimited team members at every account count\"],\"savingsHighlight\":\"Cheaper at scale, drops further past 100 accounts\",\"savingsText\":\"Zernio is $168/mo at 50 accounts and drops to $1/account past 100. Publer scales linearly per account, so the gap widens with team size.\"},\"table\":{\"label\":\"Feature Comparison\",\"title\":\"Head-to-head comparison\",\"headers\":{\"feature\":\"Feature\",\"late\":\"Zernio\",\"competitor\":\"Publer\"},\"rows\":[{\"feature\":\"API access\",\"late\":\"All plans (free included)\",\"competitor\":\"Business+ only ($21+/mo)\"},{\"feature\":\"50 accounts cost\",\"late\":\"$$168/mo (usage-based)\",\"competitor\":\"$$21 base + per-account add-on (rate scales; ~$200–350/mo at this volume)\"},{\"feature\":\"Rate limits\",\"late\":\"60-1200/min by tier\",\"competitor\":\"50/min (global)\"},{\"feature\":\"Uptime SLA\",\"late\":\"99.97% (published)\",\"competitor\":\"Not published\"},{\"feature\":\"API maturity\",\"late\":\"2+ years production\",\"competitor\":\"Beta exited 2025\"},{\"feature\":\"Free tier\",\"late\":\"Yes (with API)\",\"competitor\":\"Yes (no API)\"},{\"feature\":\"Platforms\",\"late\":\"15\",\"competitor\":\"14 (+WordPress)\"},{\"feature\":\"Visual calendar\",\"late\":\"Basic\",\"competitor\":\"Excellent\"},{\"feature\":\"AI assistant\",\"late\":\"No\",\"competitor\":\"Yes\"},{\"feature\":\"Social Ads API\",\"late\":\"Yes\",\"publer\":\"No\"}]},\"features\":{\"label\":\"Production-Grade API\",\"title\":\"Built for scale from day one\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"API on All Plans\",\"description\":\"Full API access from free tier. Publer locks API behind their Business plan ($21+/mo minimum).\"},{\"title\":\"Published Rate Limits\",\"description\":\"60-1200 req/min by tier, documented. Publer's API limits aren't publicly detailed.\"},{\"title\":\"99.97% Uptime SLA\",\"description\":\"Explicit production guarantees. Publer doesn't publish comparable uptime metrics.\"},{\"title\":\"Instant API Key\",\"description\":\"Sign up, Settings → API, copy key. 30 seconds. No Business plan upgrade required.\"},{\"title\":\"Cheaper at Scale\",\"description\":\"Zernio is $168/mo for 50 accounts (usage-based, first 2 free). Publer's per-account add-on rate isn't published in a flat table, but at 50 accounts the cost typically lands $200–$350/mo. The gap widens further past 100 accounts where Zernio drops to $1/account.\"},{\"title\":\"Modern REST Design\",\"description\":\"Clean patterns, consistent responses. Built for developers, not as an afterthought.\"}]},\"choose\":{\"label\":\"Which One?\",\"title\":\"API platform vs UI dashboard\",\"lateTitle\":\"Choose Zernio if you:\",\"lateItems\":[\"Need API access without Business plan\",\"Want transparent, published rate limits\",\"Require 99.97% uptime SLA guarantee\",\"Building SaaS or automation tools\",\"Want usage-based pricing where bigger accounts get cheaper rates\",\"Need instant API key (30 seconds)\",\"Managing 50+ accounts at scale\"],\"competitorTitle\":\"Choose Publer if you:\",\"competitorItems\":[\"Need visual content calendar\",\"Want AI content assistant\",\"Prefer drag-and-drop scheduling\",\"Require team collaboration UI\",\"Can accept API locked behind Business+ plan\",\"Don't need programmatic automation\",\"Value browser extension features\"]},\"migration\":{\"title\":\"Switching from Publer?\",\"description\":\"Zernio's API is simpler and more accessible than Publer's. No Business plan required - sign up, copy your API key, and start posting. Most developers are live in under 15 minutes.\",\"tip\":\"Zernio is $168/mo at 50 accounts (usage-based). Publer's per-account add-on rate isn't published in a flat table, so exact savings depend on the negotiated rate, but the gap widens past 100 accounts where Zernio drops to $1/account.\"},\"pricing\":{\"label\":\"Simple Pricing\",\"title\":\"No per-account fees. No API paywall.\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Common Questions\",\"items\":{\"whyNotPubler\":{\"question\":\"Why choose Zernio over Publer?\",\"answer\":\"Publer is a 12-year-old UI dashboard that added an API in 2025. The API is gated to Business+ tier ($21+/mo minimum), limited to 50 req/min globally, and has no published uptime SLA. Zernio is API-first with instant access on all plans, 600-1200 req/min, and 99.97% uptime SLA.\"},\"apiAccess\":{\"question\":\"Why is Publer's API access gated?\",\"answer\":\"Publer's core product is their UI dashboard. The API is an add-on for power users, not a first-class product. They gate it to Business+ tier to upsell. Zernio is the opposite - our API is the product, available on every plan including free.\"},\"pricing\":{\"question\":\"How does pricing compare at scale?\",\"answer\":\"Publer Business is $21/mo for 3 accounts and adds a per-extra-account charge that scales with volume; the exact rate isn't shown in a flat public table. Zernio is usage-based: free up to 2 accounts, then $6/account (1-10), $3/account (11-100), $1/account for 101+ with no cap. 50 accounts on Zernio: $6×8 + $3×40 = $168/mo. Zernio's rate drops sharply past 100 accounts; at agency scale this is where the gap becomes large.\"},\"rateLimits\":{\"question\":\"What about rate limits?\",\"answer\":\"Publer caps all tiers at 50 requests/minute globally. Zernio rate limits scale with usage, from 60 req/min on the free tier up to 1200 req/min for high-volume customers. That's 12-24x more capacity when you need burst posting.\"},\"reliability\":{\"question\":\"Is Zernio more reliable than Publer's API?\",\"answer\":\"Zernio publishes a 99.97% uptime SLA and has been production-tested since 2023. Publer's API just exited beta in 2025 and publishes no uptime guarantees. For production apps, maturity and SLAs matter.\"},\"platforms\":{\"question\":\"What platforms does Zernio support vs Publer?\",\"answer\":\"Zernio supports 15 platforms including Reddit and Telegram. Publer supports 15 including WordPress and Mastodon. For most SaaS/agency use cases, Zernio's coverage is sufficient. If you specifically need WordPress or Mastodon, Publer has the edge.\"}}},\"final\":{\"title\":\"Ready for a production-grade API?\",\"subtitle\":\"Start with the free plan. No credit card required. See why developers choose Zernio over Publer.\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View Pricing\"},\"footnote\":\"No credit card required • Instant API key • 99.97% uptime SLA\"}},\"socioboard\":{\"meta\":{\"title\":\"Managed API, Zero Maintenance | Socioboard Alternative 2026\",\"description\":\"Cloud-native API vs open-source self-hosted. Zernio: 30-second setup, zero maintenance. Socioboard: Full control, full responsibility.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Managed API, Zero Maintenance | Socioboard Alternative 2026\",\"ogDescription\":\"Zernio and Socioboard serve opposite markets. Zernio is managed SaaS. Socioboard is self-hosted open source.\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"The\",\"highlight\":\"Socioboard Alternative\",\"subtitle\":\"Without Self-Hosting Headaches\",\"description\":\"Zernio is a cloud-native, managed SaaS API for developers who want zero ops. Socioboard is an open-source platform for teams who want complete control and self-hosting.\",\"subtitle2\":\"No credit card required • 30-second setup • Zero maintenance\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View API Docs\"}},\"keyInsight\":{\"title\":\"The Fundamental Divide: Cloud vs Self-Hosted\",\"description\":\"This isn't a feature comparison - it's a philosophical choice. Zernio says \\\"We manage everything. You focus on your business.\\\" Socioboard says \\\"You control everything. We provide the source code.\\\"\",\"footnote\":\"These are not competitors - they serve completely different markets.\",\"boxes\":[{\"label\":\"Zernio's philosophy:\",\"text\":\"“We manage everything. You focus on your business.”\"},{\"label\":\"Socioboard's philosophy:\",\"text\":\"“You control everything. We provide the source code.”\"}]},\"comparison\":{\"label\":\"Managed SaaS vs Open Source\",\"title\":\"Opposite approaches to the same problem\",\"socioboardTitle\":\"Socioboard Strengths\",\"socioboardItems\":[\"Complete data sovereignty - your servers, your data\",\"Full source code access - modify anything\",\"No vendor lock-in - open source on GitHub\",\"Rich visual calendar and planning interface\",\"Comprehensive CRM and content discovery\",\"Perfect for regulated industries (fintech, healthcare)\",\"Zero recurring SaaS costs (just infrastructure)\"],\"lateTitle\":\"Zernio Strengths\",\"lateItems\":[\"30-second setup - sign up, get API key, post\",\"Zero maintenance - no servers, databases, updates\",\"99.97% uptime SLA - we manage reliability\",\"TikTok, Threads, Bluesky - modern platform support\",\"Production API - core product, battle-tested\",\"Affordable at scale - $168/mo for 50 accounts (usage-based, first 2 free)\",\"Unified posting - one API call to all platforms\"],\"keyHighlight\":\"Critical gap\",\"keyText\":\"Socioboard does NOT support TikTok - one of the top 3 platforms in 2026. For modern social media, this is a significant limitation.\"},\"cost\":{\"label\":\"Total Cost of Ownership\",\"title\":\"\\\"Free\\\" isn't always cheaper\",\"description\":\"True cost comparison for 50 accounts, 3 users, with API access:\",\"footnote\":\"Socioboard self-hosted saves money ONLY if you have internal engineering capacity and accept operational burden.\",\"comparisonRows\":[{\"label\":\"Monthly plan\",\"zernio\":\"$$168 (usage-based)\",\"competitor\":\"$$199.98\",\"extra\":\"Free software\"},{\"label\":\"Infrastructure\",\"zernio\":\"Included\",\"competitor\":\"Included\",\"extra\":\"$$100-200/mo\"},{\"label\":\"Setup/maintenance\",\"zernio\":\"Zero\",\"competitor\":\"Zero\",\"extra\":\"5-10 hrs/mo\"},{\"label\":\"Dev time cost\",\"zernio\":\"-\",\"competitor\":\"-\",\"extra\":\"$$250-1,000/mo\"},{\"label\":\"API access\",\"zernio\":\"Included\",\"competitor\":\"Included\",\"extra\":\"Requires setup\"},{\"label\":\"Uptime SLA\",\"zernio\":\"99.97%\",\"competitor\":\"Included\",\"extra\":\"You manage\"},{\"label\":\"TRUE MONTHLY COST\",\"zernio\":\"$$168\",\"competitor\":\"$$199.98\",\"extra\":\"$$350-1,200+\",\"highlight\":true}]},\"platforms\":{\"label\":\"Platform Support\",\"title\":\"Zernio has TikTok. Socioboard doesn't.\",\"lateList\":[\"X/Twitter\",\"Instagram\",\"TikTok\",\"LinkedIn\",\"Facebook\",\"YouTube\",\"Threads\",\"Reddit\",\"Pinterest\",\"Bluesky\",\"Google Business\",\"Telegram\"],\"lateHighlight\":\"TikTok\",\"lateFootnote\":\"Full modern platform support including TikTok, Threads, Bluesky\",\"competitorList\":[\"Facebook\",\"Twitter\",\"LinkedIn\",\"Instagram\",\"YouTube\",\"Pinterest\",\"Tumblr\",\"Telegram\"],\"competitorBadge\":\"No TikTok, Threads, Bluesky, or Reddit support\"},\"choose\":{\"label\":\"Which One?\",\"title\":\"Choose based on your constraints\",\"lateTitle\":\"Choose Zernio if you:\",\"lateItems\":[\"Need instant API access (30 seconds)\",\"Want managed, hosted solution\",\"Require TikTok posting support\",\"Value 99.97% uptime SLA guarantee\",\"Building SaaS or agency tools\",\"Prefer transparent usage-based pricing\",\"Cannot self-host infrastructure\"],\"competitorTitle\":\"Choose Socioboard if you:\",\"competitorItems\":[\"Want fully open source solution\",\"Can self-host and maintain\",\"Don't need TikTok support\",\"Have DevOps team available\",\"Prefer one-time server cost\",\"Need full source code access\",\"Value data sovereignty\"]},\"devExp\":{\"label\":\"Developer Experience\",\"title\":\"30 seconds vs hours to first API call\",\"footnote\":\"For fast-moving SaaS teams, self-hosting friction is disqualifying.\",\"lateSteps\":[\"Sign up for account\",\"Settings → API → Copy key\",\"Make first API call\",\"Done!\"],\"lateBadge\":\"Total: 30 seconds\",\"competitorSteps\":[\"Clone GitHub repository\",\"Install Node.js, MongoDB, dependencies\",\"Configure environment variables\",\"Set up database\",\"Install SSL certificates\",\"Deploy to cloud infrastructure\",\"Configure API authentication\",\"Test endpoints\",\"Done!\"],\"competitorBadge\":\"Total: Hours to days\"},\"table\":{\"label\":\"Feature Comparison\",\"headers\":{\"feature\":\"Feature\",\"late\":\"Zernio\",\"socioboard\":\"Socioboard\"},\"rows\":[{\"feature\":\"Setup time\",\"late\":\"30 seconds\",\"socioboard\":\"Hours to days\"},{\"feature\":\"Maintenance\",\"late\":\"Zero (managed)\",\"socioboard\":\"5-10 hrs/month\"},{\"feature\":\"Uptime SLA\",\"late\":\"99.97% guaranteed\",\"socioboard\":\"You manage\"},{\"feature\":\"TikTok support\",\"late\":\"Supported\",\"socioboard\":\"Not supported\"},{\"feature\":\"Threads support\",\"late\":\"Supported\",\"socioboard\":\"Not supported\"},{\"feature\":\"Bluesky support\",\"late\":\"Supported\",\"socioboard\":\"Not supported\"},{\"feature\":\"Open source\",\"late\":\"No (proprietary)\",\"socioboard\":\"Yes (GitHub)\"},{\"feature\":\"Self-hosting\",\"late\":\"No (cloud-only)\",\"socioboard\":\"Yes\"},{\"feature\":\"Total platforms\",\"late\":\"15 platforms\",\"socioboard\":\"8 platforms\"},{\"feature\":\"50 accounts cost\",\"late\":\"$$168/mo (usage-based)\",\"socioboard\":\"$$200/mo (cloud) or $350-1,200+ (self-hosted)\"},{\"feature\":\"Social Ads API\",\"late\":\"Yes\",\"socioboard\":\"No\"}]},\"pricing\":{\"label\":\"Pricing Comparison\",\"title\":\"All-inclusive vs hidden costs\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Common Questions\",\"items\":{\"selfHost\":{\"question\":\"Can I self-host Zernio like Socioboard?\",\"answer\":\"No, Zernio is a managed cloud service. We handle all infrastructure, updates, and scaling so you can focus on building features instead of maintaining servers. This is a philosophical choice - we believe developers shouldn't manage social media infrastructure.\"},\"tiktok\":{\"question\":\"Does Socioboard support TikTok?\",\"answer\":\"No. Socioboard does NOT support TikTok, which is one of the top 3 platforms in 2026. Zernio supports 15 platforms including TikTok, Threads, Bluesky, and Reddit.\"},\"trueCost\":{\"question\":\"Is Socioboard really free?\",\"answer\":\"The software is free, but you pay for cloud infrastructure ($50-200/mo), setup time (hours to days), and ongoing maintenance (5-10 hours/month). For most teams, Zernio's usage-based pricing (free up to 2 accounts, then $6/$3/$1 per account, custom for 2,000+) is cheaper than 'free' once you factor in DevOps time.\"},\"migration\":{\"question\":\"Can I migrate from Socioboard to Zernio?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Zernio's API can integrate alongside or replace Socioboard. Many teams start with our free plan to test the migration before fully switching over. Setup takes 30 seconds.\"},\"compliance\":{\"question\":\"What if I need data sovereignty for compliance?\",\"answer\":\"If you have strict compliance requirements (fintech, healthcare) that mandate self-hosting, Socioboard may be the better fit. For most teams, Zernio's managed approach eliminates 90% of infrastructure concerns.\"},\"enterprise\":{\"question\":\"Which is better for enterprise?\",\"answer\":\"It depends on your constraints. If you have a dedicated DevOps team and compliance requirements, Socioboard offers full control. If you want to move fast without infrastructure overhead, Zernio's 99.97% SLA and zero-maintenance approach is ideal.\"}}},\"final\":{\"title\":\"Want managed, not self-hosted?\",\"subtitle\":\"Zernio: 30-second setup, zero maintenance, 99.97% uptime SLA. Free plan includes API.\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View Pricing\"},\"footnote\":\"No credit card required • 30-second setup • Zero maintenance\"}},\"storrito\":{\"meta\":{\"title\":\"15 Platforms vs Instagram Only | Storrito Alternative 2026\",\"description\":\"Multi-platform API vs Instagram Stories specialist. Zernio: 15 platforms, instant API. Storrito: Instagram-only, no API.\",\"ogTitle\":\"15 Platforms vs Instagram Only | Storrito Alternative 2026\",\"ogDescription\":\"Zernio and Storrito serve opposite markets. Zernio is multi-platform API. Storrito is Instagram Stories editor.\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"The\",\"highlight\":\"Storrito Alternative\",\"subtitle\":\"For Multi-Platform Posting\",\"description\":\"Zernio is a unified multi-platform API for developers and agencies (15 platforms). Storrito is a niche Instagram Stories desktop scheduler for influencers. These are completely different products.\",\"subtitle2\":\"No credit card required • Instant API key • 15 platforms in one API\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View API Docs\"}},\"keyInsight\":{\"title\":\"These Are Fundamentally Incomparable Products\",\"description\":\"Zernio is a multi-platform API for developers (15 platforms, instant API access). Storrito is an Instagram Stories desktop editor for influencers (1 platform, no API). They serve opposite user bases with completely different products.\",\"footnote\":\"For API users or multi-platform needs, Storrito is not an option. For Instagram Stories creators, Zernio may be overkill.\",\"boxes\":[{\"label\":\"Zernio's philosophy:\",\"text\":\"“One unified API posts to 15 platforms reliably and affordably.”\"},{\"label\":\"Storrito's philosophy:\",\"text\":\"“Master Instagram Stories scheduling on desktop with the richest editor possible.”\"}]},\"comparison\":{\"label\":\"Breadth vs Depth\",\"title\":\"What each tool does best\",\"storritoTitle\":\"Storrito's Exclusive Strengths\",\"storritoItems\":[\"Desktop Stories editor - industry-leading tool\",\"All interactive stickers - polls, quizzes, questions\",\"True auto-posting - Stories post without notifications\",\"Video segmentation - auto-cuts videos into 15s segments\",\"Cross-post to Facebook Stories - one-click\",\"Stock image library - integrated Unsplash access\",\"7+ years in business - 152,000+ accounts connected\"],\"lateTitle\":\"Zernio's Exclusive Strengths\",\"lateItems\":[\"Multi-platform API - 15 platforms in one endpoint\",\"Instant API access - free tier includes API\",\"Programmable automation - REST API + webhooks\",\"Usage-based pricing - per-account rate drops as you scale\",\"99.97% uptime SLA - production-grade reliability\",\"Unlimited team members - costs don't scale with headcount\",\"Unified posting - one API call to all platforms\"],\"keyHighlight\":\"Critical limitation\",\"keyText\":\"Storrito has NO public API. All workflows go through their desktop UI. No programmatic automation, no custom integrations.\"},\"cost\":{\"label\":\"Pricing at Scale\",\"title\":\"Zernio scales transparently for agencies\",\"description\":\"Cost comparison for managing 50 accounts:\",\"footnote\":\"Storrito moved to a usage-based wallet/credits model in 2025; exact per-account rates aren't publicly listed. Their historical EUR 25/account/mo flat model scaled poorly for agencies.\",\"comparisonRows\":[{\"label\":\"Base plan\",\"zernio\":\"Free up to 2 accounts\",\"competitor\":\"Wallet/credits (top up as needed)\"},{\"label\":\"Account scaling\",\"zernio\":\"$$6/$3/$1 per account, custom for 2,000+ (drops by tier)\",\"competitor\":\"Wallet model (rates not publicly listed; historically EUR 25/account)\"},{\"label\":\"50 accounts cost\",\"zernio\":\"$$168/mo (usage-based)\",\"competitor\":\"Not publicly priced (was ~EUR 1,250/mo at EUR 25/account)\",\"highlight\":true},{\"label\":\"Platforms covered\",\"zernio\":\"15 platforms\",\"competitor\":\"Instagram only\"},{\"label\":\"API access\",\"zernio\":\"Instant, included\",\"competitor\":\"None available\"},{\"label\":\"PRICE DIFFERENCE\",\"zernio\":\"-\",\"competitor\":\"Storrito's old flat per-account model was ~8x at 50 accounts; new wallet model isn't publicly priced\",\"highlight\":true}]},\"platforms\":{\"label\":\"Platform Coverage\",\"title\":\"15 platforms vs 1 platform\",\"list\":[\"X/Twitter\",\"Instagram\",\"TikTok\",\"LinkedIn\",\"Facebook\",\"YouTube\",\"Threads\",\"Reddit\",\"Pinterest\",\"Bluesky\",\"Google Business\"],\"competitorItems\":[{\"text\":\"Instagram Stories\",\"icon\":\"check\"},{\"text\":\"Facebook Stories (cross-post)\",\"icon\":\"dash\"}],\"competitorBadge\":\"No TikTok, YouTube, LinkedIn, Twitter, or any other platform\"},\"scenarios\":{\"label\":\"Real-World Scenarios\",\"title\":\"Which tool wins for your use case?\",\"items\":[{\"emoji\":\"📱\",\"title\":\"Influencer: 3 Stories/day\",\"description\":\"A creator posts Instagram Stories daily and wants desktop scheduling with stickers.\",\"result\":\"Winner: Storrito ✓\",\"reason\":\"Purpose-built for this exact workflow\",\"winner\":\"Storrito\"},{\"emoji\":\"🏢\",\"title\":\"Agency: 30 clients, multi-platform\",\"description\":\"An agency manages 30 clients across Instagram, TikTok, LinkedIn, and YouTube.\",\"result\":\"Winner: Zernio ✓\",\"reason\":\"Zernio: $108/mo (usage-based, 30 clients). Storrito's old per-account model would have been ~$810/mo at this scale; their new wallet model isn't publicly priced.\",\"winner\":\"Zernio\"},{\"emoji\":\"🧑‍💻\",\"title\":\"SaaS: Adding social posting\",\"description\":\"A SaaS platform needs to add programmatic social posting via API.\",\"result\":\"Winner: Zernio ✓ (only option)\",\"reason\":\"Storrito has no API\",\"winner\":\"Zernio\"},{\"emoji\":\"🚀\",\"title\":\"Startup: Instagram + TikTok\",\"description\":\"A startup needs to post to both Instagram and TikTok consistently.\",\"result\":\"Winner: Zernio ✓ (eliminates fragmentation)\",\"reason\":\"Storrito is Instagram-only\",\"winner\":\"Zernio\"}]},\"choose\":{\"label\":\"Which One?\",\"title\":\"Choose based on your needs\",\"lateTitle\":\"Choose Zernio if you:\",\"lateItems\":[\"Need API-first social posting\",\"Want instant access (no manual review)\",\"Require production-grade reliability\",\"Building SaaS or automation tools\",\"Value transparent rate limits\",\"Need unified cross-platform posting\",\"Prefer transparent usage-based pricing\"],\"competitorTitle\":\"Choose Storrito if you:\",\"competitorItems\":[\"Focus exclusively on Instagram Stories\",\"Need Instagram-specific templates\",\"Want browser-based Story editor\",\"Require Instagram analytics\",\"Can accept limited platform support\",\"Don't need API automation\",\"Value Instagram-specialized features\"]},\"table\":{\"label\":\"Feature Comparison\",\"headers\":{\"feature\":\"Feature\",\"late\":\"Zernio\",\"storrito\":\"Storrito\"},\"rows\":[{\"feature\":\"Platforms\",\"late\":\"15 platforms\",\"storrito\":\"Instagram only (+FB cross-post)\"},{\"feature\":\"API access\",\"late\":\"Instant, included\",\"storrito\":\"None available\"},{\"feature\":\"Uptime SLA\",\"late\":\"99.97% guaranteed\",\"storrito\":\"Not published\"},{\"feature\":\"TikTok\",\"late\":\"Supported\",\"storrito\":\"Not supported\"},{\"feature\":\"YouTube\",\"late\":\"Supported\",\"storrito\":\"Not supported\"},{\"feature\":\"LinkedIn\",\"late\":\"Supported\",\"storrito\":\"Not supported\"},{\"feature\":\"Instagram Stories editor\",\"late\":\"Not included\",\"storrito\":\"Industry-leading\"},{\"feature\":\"Auto-posting Stories\",\"late\":\"Not supported\",\"storrito\":\"True auto-post\"},{\"feature\":\"50 accounts cost\",\"late\":\"$$168/mo (usage-based)\",\"storrito\":\"Wallet model (not publicly priced)\"},{\"feature\":\"Pricing model\",\"late\":\"Usage-based ($6/$3/$1 per account, custom for 2,000+)\",\"storrito\":\"Usage-based wallet/credits (2025+); was €25/account\"},{\"feature\":\"Social Ads API\",\"late\":\"Yes\",\"storrito\":\"No\"}]},\"pricing\":{\"label\":\"Pricing Comparison\",\"title\":\"Flat tiers vs per-account chaos\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Common Questions\",\"items\":{\"stories\":{\"question\":\"Does Zernio support Instagram Stories?\",\"answer\":\"Zernio supports Instagram Posts and Reels via API. Instagram Stories have platform-level Meta API restrictions that prevent third-party automated posting. For specialized Stories workflows, Storrito's desktop editor is purpose-built for this.\"},\"api\":{\"question\":\"Does Storrito have an API?\",\"answer\":\"No. Storrito has no public API. All functionality goes through their desktop web interface. This is a fundamental limitation for developers, agencies, and SaaS platforms who need programmatic access.\"},\"multiPlatform\":{\"question\":\"Can Storrito post to TikTok or YouTube?\",\"answer\":\"No. Storrito is Instagram-only (with Facebook Stories cross-posting). If you need multi-platform posting, you'll need a separate tool for each platform - or Zernio's unified API for all 15 platforms.\"},\"cost\":{\"question\":\"Why is Zernio so much cheaper at scale?\",\"answer\":\"Zernio uses usage-based pricing: free up to 2 accounts, then $6/account (1-10), $3/account (11-100), $1/account for 101+ with no cap. 50 accounts on Zernio: $168/mo. Storrito moved to a usage-based wallet/credits model in 2025; exact per-account rates aren't publicly listed. Historically billed €25/account/month, which scaled poorly for agencies (50 accounts ≈ €1,250/mo).\"},\"useBoth\":{\"question\":\"Can I use Zernio and Storrito together?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Many agencies use Zernio for multi-platform API needs and Storrito for specialized Instagram Stories workflows. They're complementary, not competitive tools serving different purposes.\"},\"influencer\":{\"question\":\"I'm an influencer posting 3 Stories/day. Which should I use?\",\"answer\":\"Storrito. If you ONLY post Instagram Stories and want the best desktop editor with stickers, polls, and auto-posting, Storrito is purpose-built for you. Zernio would be overkill.\"}}},\"final\":{\"title\":\"Need multi-platform posting?\",\"subtitle\":\"Zernio: 15 platforms, instant API, 99.97% uptime. Storrito's new wallet-based pricing isn't publicly listed; their old flat €25/account model scaled poorly past a few accounts.\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View Pricing\"},\"footnote\":\"No credit card required • Instant API key • 15 platforms included\"}},\"postiz\":{\"meta\":{\"title\":\"Postiz API Alternative - Full Social Layer | Zernio\",\"description\":\"Zernio includes Comments, DMs, Analytics \u0026 Ads APIs in one integration. Postiz API is publishing-only with a 100 req/hr limit. Compare both.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Postiz API Alternative - Full Social Layer | Zernio\",\"ogDescription\":\"Zernio includes Comments, DMs, Analytics \u0026 Ads APIs in one integration. Postiz API is publishing-only with a 100 req/hr limit.\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"The\",\"highlight\":\"Postiz Alternative\",\"subtitle\":\"With the Full Social Layer\",\"description\":\"Postiz is a creator dashboard with a public API attached - capped at 100 requests per hour. Zernio is an API and MCP server engineered for production: 1200 req/min, 99.97% uptime SLA, webhooks on every plan.\",\"subtitle2\":\"No credit card required · SOC 2 + GDPR · Comments, DMs, Analytics \u0026 Ads included\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View API Docs\"}},\"keyInsight\":{\"title\":\"The 720x gap\",\"description\":\"Postiz's documented API rate limit is 100 requests per hour on cloud. Zernio's is up to 1200 requests per minute - about 72,000 per hour. If you're building anything with real traffic, that single number ends the comparison.\",\"footnote\":\"For any integration that posts more than once a minute per account, Postiz's 100 req/hour cap makes the headline price irrelevant.\"},\"comparison\":{\"label\":\"One runs the whole operation. Another publishes.\",\"title\":\"What each tool does best\",\"lateTitle\":\"What you get with Zernio\",\"lateItems\":[\"1200 req/min rate limit (~72,000/hour) - published\",\"99.97% uptime SLA with public status page\",\"MCP server included - drop into any AI agent\",\"Ads API across 6 networks (Meta, Google, TikTok, LinkedIn, Pinterest, X)\",\"Webhooks on every plan - no upgrade required\",\"One auth model, one request shape across 15+ platforms\"],\"postizTitle\":\"What Postiz adds (if you're a creator, not an integrator)\",\"postizItems\":[\"Canva-like visual editor\",\"AI Copilot + image/video gen - gated to Team plan and up\",\"In-app calendar and team seats - for human users, not API callers\",\"Self-hosting option - you own ops, OAuth rotation, platform breakage\",\"100 req/hour API cap (cloud) - fine for hobby, not for SaaS\",\"No Ads API, no MCP server, no published uptime SLA\"],\"keyHighlight\":\"The 720x gap\",\"keyText\":\"Postiz's documented API rate limit is 100 requests per hour on cloud. Zernio's is up to 1200 requests per minute - about 72,000 per hour. If you're building anything with real traffic, that single number ends the comparison.\"},\"mcpComparison\":{\"label\":\"Build automations with MCPs\",\"title\":\"Build automations with MCPs\",\"description\":\"If you're building an AI agent that acts on social, the MCP server is your entry point. Postiz's MCP server is built for content production: generate, schedule, publish. Zernio's 280+ tools cover the full social and messaging layer: publishing, comments, DMs, analytics, and ads.\",\"rows\":[{\"capability\":\"Tools exposed\",\"zernio\":\"280+\",\"postiz\":\"9\"},{\"capability\":\"Publish \u0026 schedule\",\"zernio\":\"Yes\",\"postiz\":\"Yes\"},{\"capability\":\"Generate images/video\",\"zernio\":\"Via your own model\",\"postiz\":\"Yes (built in)\"},{\"capability\":\"Read/reply to comments\",\"zernio\":\"Yes\",\"postiz\":\"No\"},{\"capability\":\"Send DMs\",\"zernio\":\"Yes\",\"postiz\":\"No\"},{\"capability\":\"Pull analytics\",\"zernio\":\"Yes\",\"postiz\":\"No\"},{\"capability\":\"Manage ads\",\"zernio\":\"Yes\",\"postiz\":\"No\"}]},\"cost\":{\"label\":\"Pricing\",\"title\":\"Smooth per-account pricing vs channel-locked tiers\",\"description\":\"Postiz tiers lock you to 5, 10, 30, or 100 channels. Need account #31? Pay for 100. Need a team seat on Standard? Upgrade. Zernio: every feature included, pay only for what you connect.\",\"footnote\":\"For any integration that posts more than once a minute per account, Postiz's 100 req/hour cap makes the headline price irrelevant.\",\"comparisonRows\":[{\"scale\":\"2 accounts, solo dev\",\"late\":\"Free\",\"postiz\":\"$$29/mo (Standard, no team seats, no AI)\",\"winner\":\"Zernio\"},{\"scale\":\"10 accounts, want webhooks + team\",\"late\":\"$$48/mo, full feature set\",\"postiz\":\"$$39/mo Team (no analytics on smaller plans, capped 100 req/hr)\",\"winner\":\"Zernio (no cliffs, no caps)\"},{\"scale\":\"31 accounts\",\"late\":\"$$111/mo (smooth pricing)\",\"postiz\":\"$$99/mo Ultimate, forced jump from $49\",\"winner\":\"Zernio (no tier cliff)\"},{\"scale\":\"100 accounts\",\"late\":\"$$318/mo, every feature\",\"postiz\":\"$$99/mo capped at 100 req/hr, no SLA\",\"winner\":\"Postiz looks cheaper, until you hit the rate limit on day one\"},{\"scale\":\"500 accounts\",\"late\":\"$$718/mo\",\"postiz\":\"Custom, Ultimate maxes at 100\",\"winner\":\"Zernio (Postiz can't price this without a sales call)\"}]},\"apiMaturity\":{\"label\":\"API Maturity\",\"title\":\"API since day one vs API bolted on\",\"late\":{\"title\":\"Zernio: API since day one (2023)\",\"items\":[\"Launched 2023 as an API product, 2+ years in production\",\"Unified REST: one request shape across 15+ platforms\",\"Rate limits: 60-1200 req/min, published per endpoint\",\"99.97% uptime SLA with public status page\",\"MCP server for AI agents\",\"OpenAPI 3.1 spec, LLM-friendly docs\"],\"badge\":\"Production-grade for SaaS\"},\"postiz\":{\"title\":\"Postiz: API bolted on (2024)\",\"items\":[\"Public API shipped 2024 alongside a UI-first creator app\",\"Platform-specific endpoints, not unified\",\"Rate limit: 100 req/hour cloud, 90/hour self-hosted\",\"No published uptime SLA, community-supported\",\"MCP server with 8 tools\",\"No Ads API\"],\"badge\":\"Secondary feature on a UI product\"}},\"scenarios\":{\"label\":\"Real-World Scenarios\",\"title\":\"Which tool wins for your use case?\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"SaaS embedding social posting\",\"description\":\"You're shipping a feature in your product that posts on behalf of customers. You need predictable rate limits, an SLA, and webhooks.\",\"winner\":\"Zernio\",\"result\":\"Winner: Zernio ✓\",\"reason\":\"1200 req/min, 99.97% SLA, webhooks on every plan. Postiz caps at 100 req/hour.\"},{\"title\":\"AI agent that posts on command\",\"description\":\"You're building an agent (Claude, Cursor, internal copilot) that schedules content as a tool call.\",\"winner\":\"Zernio\",\"result\":\"Winner: Zernio ✓\",\"reason\":\"Zernio ships an MCP server. Postiz has none.\"},{\"title\":\"Agency platform with ads + organic\",\"description\":\"You manage 30-100 client accounts and need both organic posting and ad campaign control.\",\"winner\":\"Zernio\",\"result\":\"Winner: Zernio ✓\",\"reason\":\"Zernio includes Ads API across 6 networks. Postiz has no Ads API.\"},{\"title\":\"Internal creator tool for one brand\",\"description\":\"You want a finished UI, AI image gen, and a calendar, not an API.\",\"winner\":\"Postiz\",\"result\":\"Winner: Postiz ✓\",\"reason\":\"If you don't need an integration, you don't need Zernio. Postiz ships the dashboard you'd otherwise build.\"}]},\"choose\":{\"label\":\"Which One?\",\"title\":\"Choose based on your priorities\",\"lateTitle\":\"You're a fit for Zernio if you:\",\"lateItems\":[\"Need production-grade managed API\",\"Want 99.97% uptime SLA guarantee\",\"Require instant API access (30 sec)\",\"Building SaaS or commercial tools\",\"Value transparent, published rate limits\",\"Need Comments, DMs, Analytics, and Ads in one integration\",\"Use AI agents and want MCP server support\"],\"competitorTitle\":\"You're not a fit for Zernio (and that's fine) if you:\",\"competitorItems\":[\"Are a solo creator looking for a posting dashboard, not an API\",\"Want a Canva-like editor built into the tool\",\"Are happy to host, patch, and maintain a Node app yourself\",\"Don't need an SLA, webhooks at scale, or an Ads API\",\"Post less than 100 times an hour across your whole account base\"]},\"openSource\":{\"title\":\"\\\"Open source\\\" means you're on call\",\"description\":\"Postiz being open source is real, and it sounds free. The hidden bill: you maintain the OAuth apps for 30+ platforms, you patch when Meta or TikTok ship breaking changes, you wake up when your queue jams, you handle token refresh and rate-limit backoff. Zernio's whole reason for existing is that we do that so you don't. If you wanted to be in the social-API maintenance business, you wouldn't be reading a comparison page.\",\"footnote\":\"Self-hosting Postiz makes sense for one team: people who want to build Postiz, not use it.\"},\"table\":{\"label\":\"Feature Comparison\",\"headers\":{\"feature\":\"Feature\",\"late\":\"Zernio\",\"postiz\":\"Postiz\"},\"rows\":[{\"feature\":\"API rate limit\",\"late\":\"1200 req/min (~72,000/hr)\",\"postiz\":\"100 req/hour (cloud)\"},{\"feature\":\"Uptime SLA\",\"late\":\"99.97% guaranteed\",\"postiz\":\"Not published\"},{\"feature\":\"MCP server\",\"late\":\"280+ tools\",\"postiz\":\"9 tools (publish only)\"},{\"feature\":\"Comments \u0026 DMs API\",\"late\":\"Yes\",\"postiz\":\"No\"},{\"feature\":\"Ads API\",\"late\":\"6 networks\",\"postiz\":\"No\"},{\"feature\":\"Webhooks\",\"late\":\"All plans\",\"postiz\":\"Available\"},{\"feature\":\"AI content generation\",\"late\":\"Not included\",\"postiz\":\"AI Copilot, image \u0026 video gen\"},{\"feature\":\"Visual editor\",\"late\":\"Not included (API-only)\",\"postiz\":\"Canva-like editor\"},{\"feature\":\"Setup time\",\"late\":\"30 seconds\",\"postiz\":\"Minutes (cloud) or hours (self-hosted)\"},{\"feature\":\"Pricing model\",\"late\":\"Per-account, no cliffs\",\"postiz\":\"Channel-locked tiers\"}]},\"pricing\":{\"label\":\"Pricing Comparison\",\"title\":\"Smooth per-account pricing vs channel-locked tiers\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Common Questions\",\"items\":{\"apiMaturity\":{\"question\":\"How mature is Postiz's API compared to Zernio's?\",\"answer\":\"The rate limit gap says it first: Postiz caps at 100 req/hour on cloud; Zernio allows up to 1200 req/min, roughly 720x more headroom. Beyond that: Zernio launched as an API product in 2023 with a 99.97% uptime SLA; Postiz bolted on an API in 2024 alongside a UI-first creator app with no published SLA. For production SaaS, that's not a close call.\"},\"openSource\":{\"question\":\"Is Postiz really open source?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, Postiz is genuinely open source on GitHub (gitroomhq/postiz-app). That's real. But for most integrators the question isn't 'can I read the source', it's 'who's on call when Instagram changes their auth flow.' With Postiz self-hosted, that's you. OAuth rotation, platform breakage, queue jams, rate-limit backoff. All yours. Zernio exists so you don't have to deal with any of that.\"},\"pricing\":{\"question\":\"How does pricing compare?\",\"answer\":\"Postiz tiers lock you to channel counts: $29 (5 channels), $39 (10), $49 (30), $99 (100). Need account #31? You jump from $49 to $99. Zernio is per-account with no cliffs: free up to 2, then $6/account (1-10), $3/account (11-100), $1/account (101+). The Postiz headline price also becomes irrelevant the moment your integration posts more than once a minute per account. The 100 req/hour cap kicks in before any meaningful traffic.\"},\"aiFeatures\":{\"question\":\"Does Zernio have AI features like Postiz?\",\"answer\":\"Zernio doesn't bundle AI, because integrators already have an LLM in their stack and don't want a second vendor charging per-image. If you're building with Claude, Cursor, or a custom agent, the MCP server is your integration point. Postiz's AI (Copilot, image gen, video gen) is gated to Team plan and up. It's a creator-facing feature, not an API-facing one.\"},\"selfHosting\":{\"question\":\"Can I self-host Zernio like Postiz?\",\"answer\":\"No. Zernio is cloud-only and proprietary. Postiz can be self-hosted, giving you full control over data and customization. If self-hosting is required, Zernio is not an option, but read the open source answer first to understand what self-hosting Postiz actually involves.\"},\"whichIsBetter\":{\"question\":\"Which is better overall?\",\"answer\":\"If you're building software, Zernio. If you're using software as a creator, Postiz. They're not competing for the same customer, which is why this page exists: to save you the eval.\"}}},\"final\":{\"title\":\"Ship the integration this week.\",\"subtitle\":\"Free up to 2 accounts. No card. 30 seconds to your first API call. 99.97% SLA from the first request.\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Get an API key\",\"secondary\":\"Read the OpenAPI spec\"},\"footnote\":\"No credit card required · SOC 2 + GDPR · Comments, DMs, Analytics \u0026 Ads included\"}},\"uploadpost\":{\"meta\":{\"title\":\"99.97% Uptime SLA | Upload-Post Alternative 2026\",\"description\":\"Zernio includes Google Business Profile + 99.97% SLA. Upload-Post has TikTok 15/day limit, no Google Business. Compare platforms, pricing, daily caps.\",\"ogTitle\":\"99.97% Uptime SLA | Upload-Post Alternative 2026\",\"ogDescription\":\"Zernio: 15 platforms including Google Business, 99.97% SLA. Upload-Post: No Google Business, TikTok 15/day cap.\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"The\",\"highlight\":\"Upload-Post Alternative\",\"subtitle\":\"With Production-Grade Reliability\",\"description\":\"Zernio includes Google Business Profile (critical for local SEO) with 99.97% uptime SLA. Upload-Post has platform-specific daily limits (TikTok: 15/day) and no Google Business support.\",\"subtitle2\":\"No credit card required • 99.97% uptime SLA • Instant API key\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View API Docs\"}},\"keyInsight\":{\"title\":\"Google Business Profile: The Critical Difference\",\"description\":\"Zernio supports Google Business Profile posting - essential for local businesses, restaurants, retail stores, and agencies managing local SEO. Upload-Post does not support Google Business Profile at all. If you need to post updates to Google Maps/Search listings, Zernio is your only option.\",\"footnote\":\"Plus: Zernio has 99.97% SLA, no strict daily platform caps.\",\"boxes\":[{\"label\":\"Zernio:\",\"text\":\"Google Business Profile included • 99.97% SLA • No strict daily caps\"},{\"label\":\"Upload-Post:\",\"text\":\"No Google Business • No SLA • TikTok 15/day, Instagram 50/day\"}]},\"comparison\":{\"label\":\"Head-to-Head\",\"title\":\"Feature comparison\",\"uploadpostTitle\":\"Upload-Post Limitations\",\"uploadpostItems\":[\"No Google Business Profile support\",\"TikTok limited to 15 posts/day\",\"Instagram limited to 50 posts/day\",\"No Reddit video support (text/photos only)\",\"No published uptime SLA\",\"Per-upload pricing model\"],\"lateTitle\":\"Zernio Advantages\",\"lateItems\":[\"Google Business Profile included on all plans\",\"Higher rate limits across all platforms\",\"99.97% uptime SLA guaranteed\",\"Full Reddit support including video\",\"15 platforms in one unified API\",\"Flat per-profile pricing, predictable costs\"],\"keyHighlight\":\"Critical gap\",\"keyText\":\"Upload-Post does not support Google Business Profile. For agencies managing local businesses, this is a dealbreaker.\"},\"platforms\":{\"label\":\"Platform Support\",\"title\":\"Zernio: 15 platforms • Upload-Post: 9-10\",\"lateItems\":[{\"text\":\"TikTok\",\"icon\":\"check\"},{\"text\":\"Instagram (Reels, Stories, Posts)\",\"icon\":\"check\"},{\"text\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"check\"},{\"text\":\"Facebook\",\"icon\":\"check\"},{\"text\":\"LinkedIn\",\"icon\":\"check\"},{\"text\":\"X (Twitter)\",\"icon\":\"check\"},{\"text\":\"Threads\",\"icon\":\"check\"},{\"text\":\"Pinterest\",\"icon\":\"check\"},{\"text\":\"Bluesky\",\"icon\":\"check\"},{\"text\":\"Reddit (all media)\",\"icon\":\"check\"},{\"text\":\"Google Business Profile\",\"icon\":\"check\",\"highlight\":true,\"note\":\"← Exclusive\"}],\"competitorItems\":[{\"text\":\"TikTok\",\"icon\":\"check\",\"note\":\"(15/day limit)\"},{\"text\":\"Instagram (Reels, Stories, Posts)\",\"icon\":\"check\",\"note\":\"(50/day limit)\"},{\"text\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"check\"},{\"text\":\"Facebook\",\"icon\":\"check\"},{\"text\":\"LinkedIn\",\"icon\":\"check\"},{\"text\":\"X (Twitter)\",\"icon\":\"check\"},{\"text\":\"Threads\",\"icon\":\"check\"},{\"text\":\"Pinterest\",\"icon\":\"check\"},{\"text\":\"Bluesky\",\"icon\":\"check\"},{\"text\":\"Reddit (text/photos only)\",\"icon\":\"check\",\"note\":\"No video\"},{\"text\":\"Google Business Profile\",\"icon\":\"x\",\"note\":\"Not supported\"}]},\"dailyLimitsCallout\":{\"title\":\"For agencies managing multiple clients on TikTok:\",\"description\":\"Upload-Post's 15 posts/day TikTok limit may be restrictive. If you manage 10 clients posting 2x daily each, you'll hit the cap.\"},\"featureComparison\":{\"label\":\"Head-to-Head\",\"rows\":[{\"label\":\"Google Business Profile\",\"zernio\":\"✓ Included\",\"competitor\":\"✕ Not supported\"},{\"label\":\"Uptime SLA\",\"zernio\":\"✓ 99.97% guaranteed\",\"competitor\":\"✕ None published\"},{\"label\":\"TikTok daily limit\",\"zernio\":\"Higher limits\",\"competitor\":\"15 posts/day\"},{\"label\":\"Instagram daily limit\",\"zernio\":\"Higher limits\",\"competitor\":\"50 posts/day\"},{\"label\":\"Reddit video\",\"zernio\":\"✓ Supported\",\"competitor\":\"✕ Text/photos only\"},{\"label\":\"Total platforms\",\"zernio\":\"15 platforms\",\"competitor\":\"9-10 platforms\"},{\"label\":\"Instagram Reels/Stories\",\"zernio\":\"✓ Supported\",\"competitor\":\"✓ Supported\"},{\"label\":\"Webhooks\",\"zernio\":\"✓ All plans\",\"competitor\":\"✓ Available\"},{\"label\":\"White-label/Multi-user\",\"zernio\":\"✓ Supported\",\"competitor\":\"✓ Supported\"},{\"label\":\"Analytics\",\"zernio\":\"✓ Bundled (no add-on)\",\"competitor\":\"✓ Included\"},{\"label\":\"SDKs\",\"zernio\":\"REST API\",\"competitor\":\"Python, JavaScript\"},{\"label\":\"Pricing model\",\"zernio\":\"Per-account (usage-based, free up to 2)\",\"competitor\":\"Per-upload\"},{\"feature\":\"Social Ads API\",\"late\":\"Yes\",\"uploadpost\":\"No\"}]},\"strengths\":{\"label\":\"Upload-Post Strengths\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"SDKs Included\",\"description\":\"Official Python and JavaScript SDKs with npm/PyPI packages. Zernio is REST-only.\"},{\"title\":\"Analytics Built-in\",\"description\":\"Analytics API included at no extra cost. Zernio also bundles analytics with no add-on, but Upload-Post's analytics surface area is broader.\"},{\"title\":\"FFmpeg Editor API\",\"description\":\"Video editing/processing capabilities via API. Unique feature not offered by Zernio.\"},{\"title\":\"White-label Support\",\"description\":\"Multi-user profiles with JWT generation for SaaS integrations. Well-documented.\"}]},\"pricingComparison\":{\"label\":\"Pricing Models\",\"late\":{\"title\":\"Zernio: Per-Account, Usage-Based\",\"items\":[\"Free (first 2 social accounts, unlimited posts, full API)\",\"$$6/account (1-10), $3/account (11-100)\",\"$$1/account for 101+ with no cap\"],\"badge\":\"Includes Google Business Profile + 99.97% SLA on all plans\"},\"competitor\":{\"title\":\"Upload-Post: Per-Upload\",\"items\":[\"Free (10 uploads/mo)\",\"Basic (~€8.40/mo, 120 uploads/mo)\",\"Professional (~€25/mo, ~5 posts/day)\"],\"badge\":\"No Google Business • No SLA • Daily platform caps apply\"}},\"dailyLimits\":{\"label\":\"Daily Platform Limits\",\"title\":\"Upload-Post enforces strict daily caps\",\"description\":\"Upload-Post enforces platform-specific daily upload caps using rolling 24-hour windows. Exceeding these results in 429 Too Many Requests errors.\",\"tableRows\":[{\"platform\":\"TikTok\",\"uploadpost\":\"15 posts/day\",\"late\":\"Higher limits\",\"highlight\":true},{\"platform\":\"Instagram\",\"uploadpost\":\"50 posts/day\",\"late\":\"Higher limits\",\"highlight\":false},{\"platform\":\"YouTube\",\"uploadpost\":\"Quota-based\",\"late\":\"Managed\",\"highlight\":false},{\"platform\":\"Google Business\",\"uploadpost\":\"Not supported ✗\",\"late\":\"✓ Supported\",\"highlight\":true},{\"platform\":\"Reddit Video\",\"uploadpost\":\"Not supported ✗\",\"late\":\"✓ Supported\",\"highlight\":true}]},\"useCases\":{\"label\":\"Which One?\",\"title\":\"Choose based on your needs\"},\"table\":{\"label\":\"Feature Comparison\",\"headers\":{\"feature\":\"Feature\",\"late\":\"Zernio\",\"uploadpost\":\"Upload-Post\"},\"rows\":[{\"feature\":\"Google Business Profile\",\"late\":\"Supported\",\"uploadpost\":\"Not supported\"},{\"feature\":\"Uptime SLA\",\"late\":\"99.97% guaranteed\",\"uploadpost\":\"Not published\"},{\"feature\":\"TikTok daily limit\",\"late\":\"Higher limits\",\"uploadpost\":\"15 posts/day\"},{\"feature\":\"Instagram daily limit\",\"late\":\"Higher limits\",\"uploadpost\":\"50 posts/day\"},{\"feature\":\"Reddit video\",\"late\":\"Supported\",\"uploadpost\":\"Text/photos only\"},{\"feature\":\"Total platforms\",\"late\":\"15 platforms\",\"uploadpost\":\"9-10 platforms\"},{\"feature\":\"Analytics\",\"late\":\"Bundled (no add-on)\",\"uploadpost\":\"Included\"},{\"featu