Bio (Linkin.bio) tool\",\"Need creator/brand collaboration features\",\"Don't need any API access\",\"Managing 1-3 social sets manually\",\"Want UGC content management\"]},\"migration\":{\"title\":\"Need API automation?\",\"description\":\"If you're a Later user who needs API access, Zernio is your only option. Later doesn't have a public API at any tier. Sign up for Zernio, copy your API key, and start automating - today, not never.\",\"tip\":\"Zernio's free plan includes API access. Test it before you commit.\"},\"pricing\":{\"label\":\"Simple Pricing\",\"title\":\"Flat pricing vs social set complexity\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Common Questions\",\"items\":{\"noApi\":{\"question\":\"Does Later really have no API?\",\"answer\":\"Correct. Later is designed as a visual content scheduler for creators. They do not offer a public API for third-party integrations, custom automation, or programmatic posting. If you need API access, Later is not an option.\"},\"platforms\":{\"question\":\"What platforms does Later support vs Zernio?\",\"answer\":\"Later supports 9 platforms: Instagram, Facebook, Twitter/X, TikTok, Pinterest, LinkedIn, YouTube, Threads, and YouTube Shorts. Zernio supports 15: all of those plus Reddit, Bluesky, Google Business Profile, Telegram, Snapchat, WhatsApp, and Discord.\"},\"pricing\":{\"question\":\"How does pricing compare?\",\"answer\":\"Later's pricing (annual) starts at $18.75/mo Starter, $37.50/mo Growth, up to $82.50/mo Scale for social sets ($25/$50/$110 monthly). Zernio is usage-based: free up to 2 accounts, then $6/account (1-10), $3/account (11-100), $1/account for 101+ with no cap - full API included on every account. For small teams (≤5 accounts) Zernio is much cheaper; at 50 accounts Zernio is $168/mo vs Later's $82.50/mo Scale, but Zernio is the only one with an actual API.\"},\"visual\":{\"question\":\"Is Later's visual calendar better?\",\"answer\":\"Yes, Later has an excellent visual content calendar with grid preview, Linkin.bio, and creator collaboration features. If you only need manual scheduling and don't need API access, Later's UI is superior. Zernio focuses on API reliability, not visual planning.\"},\"switching\":{\"question\":\"Can I use both Later and Zernio?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Some teams use Later for visual content planning and Zernio's API for programmatic automation. They serve different purposes - Later is for creators who schedule manually, Zernio is for developers who automate.\"},\"whyNoApi\":{\"question\":\"Why doesn't Later have an API?\",\"answer\":\"Later is built for creators and small businesses who schedule posts manually via their app and web interface. Their business model is visual scheduling, not developer infrastructure. Zernio is the opposite - API-first from day one.\"}}},\"final\":{\"title\":\"Ready for an API that exists?\",\"subtitle\":\"Start with the free plan. Get an instant API key. Don't wait for Later's API - it doesn't exist.\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View Pricing\"},\"footnote\":\"No credit card required • Instant API key • 99.97% uptime SLA\"}},\"planoly\":{\"meta\":{\"title\":\"15 Platforms, One API | Planoly Alternative 2026\",\"description\":\"Looking for a Planoly alternative with API access? Planoly supports 9 platforms with no public API. Zernio offers 15 platforms with instant API access.\",\"ogTitle\":\"15 Platforms, One API | Planoly Alternative 2026\",\"ogDescription\":\"Planoly supports 9 platforms but no public API. Zernio has 15 platforms with production-grade posting API.\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"The\",\"highlight\":\"Planoly Alternative\",\"subtitle\":\"Beyond Just Instagram\",\"description\":\"Planoly is an Instagram-first visual planner supporting 9 platforms but with no public API. Zernio is API-first with 15 platforms, instant access, and 99.97% uptime SLA - including Reddit and Google Business that Planoly lacks.\",\"subtitle2\":\"No credit card required • Instant API key • Production-grade API\",