/min by tier, publicly documented. Planoly: No API, no rate limits to publish.\"}]},\"choose\":{\"label\":\"Which One?\",\"title\":\"Visual Instagram planner vs multi-platform API\",\"lateTitle\":\"Choose Zernio if you:\",\"lateItems\":[\"Need Reddit, Google Business, or Bluesky\",\"Require API access (Planoly has none)\",\"Building SaaS or automation tools\",\"Managing clients programmatically\",\"Want published uptime SLA\",\"Need programmable posting at scale\",\"Value comprehensive platform coverage\"],\"competitorTitle\":\"Choose Planoly if you:\",\"competitorItems\":[\"Don't need Reddit, Google Business, or Bluesky\",\"Only need 9 platforms manually\",\"Value visual grid planning for Instagram\",\"Want Shoplink e-commerce integration\",\"Need affiliate link tools (Stylelink.it)\",\"Are an Instagram influencer, not developer\",\"Don't need any API access\"]},\"migration\":{\"title\":\"Need API or missing platforms?\",\"description\":\"If you need Reddit, Google Business Profile, Bluesky, or API automation, Zernio is the answer. 15 platforms, instant API access, and 99.97% uptime SLA - everything Planoly doesn't offer.\",\"tip\":\"Zernio's free plan includes API access to all 15 platforms. Test the difference.\"},\"pricing\":{\"label\":\"Simple Pricing\",\"title\":\"Flat tiers vs upload limits\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Common Questions\",\"items\":{\"platforms\":{\"question\":\"How many platforms does Planoly support?\",\"answer\":\"Planoly supports 8 platforms with full auto-posting (Instagram, Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest, Threads, LinkedIn, TikTok, YouTube) plus Amazon with reminder-only posting. They're missing Reddit, Bluesky, and Google Business Profile. Zernio supports all 15 platforms with full API access.\"},\"noApi\":{\"question\":\"Does Planoly have an API?\",\"answer\":\"No. Planoly is a visual scheduling tool for creators. They do not offer a public API for third-party integrations, automation, or programmatic posting. Zernio is API-first with instant