osts/mo cap)\",\"winner\":\"Zernio (bundle's 100k-post cap and missing ads/DMs offset the headline price)\"}]},\"productionReady\":{\"label\":\"Production-Ready API\",\"title\":\"Built for the full social layer\",\"items\":[{\"title\":\"Ads and DMs are live\",\"description\":\"Boost posts, run campaigns, and send DMs across platforms through the same API today. On bundle.social, the ads and DM layers are still listed as coming soon.\"},{\"title\":\"Messaging platforms included\",\"description\":\"Add a conversational layer while shipping WhatsApp, Telegram, and Snapchat integrations with Zernio.\"},{\"title\":\"Published reliability\",\"description\":\"A 99.97% uptime SLA and documented rate limits (60–1200 req/min by tier). bundle.social runs a public status page but doesn’t advertise an SLA or rate limits.\"},{\"title\":\"8 SDKs\",\"description\":\"Node, Python, Go, Ruby, Java, PHP, .NET, and Rust. bundle.social ships a TypeScript SDK, so non-JavaScript stacks lean on the raw REST API.\"},{\"title\":\"Start free\",\"description\":\"Two accounts free with unlimited posts and full API access, no card, no trial clock. Most developers ship live connectors in under 30 minutes.\"}]},\"choose\":{\"label\":\"Which One?\",\"title\":\"Choose based on your needs\",\"lateTitle\":\"Choose Zernio if you:\",\"lateItems\":[\"Need ads or DMs as part of your product, not later\",\"Want WhatsApp, Telegram, or Snapchat coverage\",\"Post at high volume and don’t want a monthly post cap\",\"Build on Python, Go, or another non-JavaScript stack\",\"Want a published uptime SLA and rate limits for vendor review\",\"Need SOC 2 and GDPR documentation on file\"],\"competitorTitle\":\"Choose bundle.social if you:\",\"competitorItems\":[\"Connect accounts per customer at modest posting volume\",\"Only need posting, scheduling, and analytics today\",\"Need Slack or Mastodon publishing specifically\",\"Don’t need an ads or DM API yet\"]},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Common Questions\",\"items\":{\"howDifferent\":{\"question\":\"How is Zernio different from bundle.social?\",\"answer\":\"Both are API-first social media platforms, and both ship posting, scheduling, comments, and analytics. The difference is scope and pricing. Zernio also ships DMs, comment-to-DM automation, and ads across 6 networks today, covers WhatsApp/Telegram/Snapchat, and publishes a 99.97% uptime SLA. bundle.social lists its DM and ads APIs as coming soon and prices per organization and usage rather than per account.\"},\"adsApi\":{\"question\":\"Does bundle.social have an ads API?\",\"answer\":\"Not yet. bundle.social publishes a Social Media Ads API page describing future paid-social workflows, but it’s listed as coming soon. Zernio’s Ads API covers 6 networks and is live today, included at every pricing level.\"},\"pricing\":{\"question\":\"Which is cheaper, Zernio or bundle.social?\",\"answer\":\"It depends on your usage. bundle.social starts at $100/month for unlimited accounts but caps posts per plan (10,000/month on Pro). Zernio is free up to 2 accounts, then $6/account (3–10), $3/account (11–100), and $1/account (101–2,000), with unlimited posts.\"},\"whatsapp\":{\"question\":\"Does Zernio support WhatsApp and Telegram?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Zernio covers 15 platforms including WhatsApp, Telegram, and Snapchat. bundle.social’s platform list (14 platforms) includes Slack and Mastodon but not WhatsApp, Telegram, or Snapchat, so messaging-heavy use cases are a clear fit for Zernio.\"},\"aiAgents\":{\"question\":\"Do both work with AI agents?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Both offer an official MCP server, a JSON-first CLI, and an OpenAPI spec, so an agent can post through either. Zernio’s MCP server exposes 280+ tools and covers the full loop: publish, analyze, and boost.\"}}},\"final\":{\"title\":\"Ready to ship the full social layer?\",\"subtitle\":\"Start free. Add accounts as you grow. Posting, engagement, analytics, and ads through one API.\",\"ctas\":{\"primary\":\"Try Zernio Free\",\"secondary\":\"View Pricing\"},\"footnote\":\"No credit card required • Get API access instantly • 15+ platforms included\"}}},\"privacyPolicyPage\":{\"metadata\":{\"title\":\"Privacy Policy - Zernio\",\"description\":\"Zernio's privacy policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your data.\"},\"title\":\"Privacy Policy\",\"lastUpdated\":\"Last updated\",\"sections\":{\"intro\":{\"p1\":\"Thank you for using {appName} (the \\\"Service\\\"), operated by us at {domain}. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our social media scheduling API service.\",\"operatedBy\":\"The Service is operated by:\",\"p2\":\"By using our Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with our policies and practices, do not use our Service.\",\"p3\":\"Our Service uses YouTube API Services. By using our Service to interact with YouTube, you are also agreeing to be bound by the Google Privacy Policy, available at https://www.google.com/policies/privacy.\",\"relatedDocs\":\"For more information, please see our\",\"tosLink\":\"Terms of Service\",\"and\":\"and\",\"legalDisclosureLink\":\"Legal Disclosure\",\"impressumNote\":\"For company identification details (Impressum), please see our Legal Disclosure.\",\"impressumNotePrefix\":\"For company identification details (Impressum), please see our\"},\"collect\":{\"heading\":\"Information We Collect\",\"personal\":{\"heading\":\"Personal Information\",\"intro\":\"We collect the following personal information:\",\"name\":{\"label\":\"Name\",\"description\":\"To personalize your experience and for account identification\"},\"email\":{\"label\":\"Email Address\",\"description\":\"For account communication, support, and service updates\"},\"payment\":{\"label\":\"Payment Information\",\"description\":\"Processed securely through third-party payment providers (we do not store payment details)\"},\"apiUsage\":{\"label\":\"API Usage Data\",\"description\":\"To monitor usage limits and provide analytics\"},\"items\":[\"Name: To personalize your experience and for account identification\",\"Email Address: For account communication, support, and service updates\",\"Payment Information: Processed securely through third-party payment providers (we do not store payment details)\",\"API Usage Data: To monitor usage limits and provide analytics\"]},\"social\":{\"heading\":\"Social Media Account Data\",\"p1\":\"When you connect social media accounts to our Service, we collect and store access tokens and basic profile information necessary to schedule and publish posts on your behalf.\"},\"automatic\":{\"heading\":\"Automatically Collected Information\",\"ip\":\"IP addresses and device information\",\"browser\":\"Browser type and version\",\"usage\":\"Usage patterns and API request logs\",\"cookies\":\"Cookies and similar tracking technologies\",\"items\":[\"IP addresses and device information\",\"Browser type and version\",\"Usage patterns and API request logs\",\"Cookies and similar tracking technologies\"]}},\"legalBasis\":{\"heading\":\"Legal Basis for Processing\",\"intro\":\"Under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), we process your personal data based on the following lawful bases:\",\"contract\":{\"label\":\"Contractual Necessity\",\"description\":\"Processing necessary to perform our contract with you, such as providing the Service, managing your account, and processing payments.\"},\"consent\":{\"label\":\"Consent\",\"description\":\"Where you have given explicit consent to the processing of your personal data for specific purposes, such as marketing communications.\"},\"legitimate\":{\"label\":\"Legitimate Interests\",\"description\":\"Processing necessary for our legitimate interests, such as improving our Service, preventing fraud, and ensuring security, provided these interests are not overridden by your rights.\"},\"legal\":{\"label\":\"Legal Obligation\",\"description\":\"Processing necessary to comply with legal obligations, such as tax reporting and responding to lawful requests from authorities.\"}},\"use\":{\"heading\":\"How We Use Your Information\",\"intro\":\"We use your information for the following purposes:\",\"items\":{\"service\":\"Providing and maintaining our API service\",\"payments\":\"Processing payments and managing subscriptions\",\"scheduling\":\"Scheduling and publishing social media posts\",\"monitoring\":\"Monitoring API usage and enforcing rate limits\",\"support\":\"Providing customer support and technical assistance\",\"updates\":\"Sending important service updates and notifications\",\"improving\":\"Improving our Service and developing new features\",\"security\":\"Ensuring security and preventing fraud\"}},\"sharing\":{\"heading\":\"Information Sharing and Disclosure\",\"intro\":\"We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share your information only in the following circumstances:\",\"providers\":{\"label\":\"Service Providers\",\"description\":\"With trusted third-party providers who assist in operating our Service (payment processors, hosting providers)\"},\"platforms\":{\"label\":\"Social Media Platforms\",\"description\":\"To publish content on your connected social media accounts as requested\"},\"legal\":{\"label\":\"Legal Requirements\",\"description\":\"When required by law or to protect our rights and safety\"},\"business\":{\"label\":\"Business Transfers\",\"description\":\"In connection with any merger, sale of assets, or acquisition\"},\"items\":[\"Service Providers: With trusted third-party providers who assist in operating our Service (payment processors, hosting providers)\",\"Social Media Platforms: To publish content on your connected social media accounts as requested\",\"Legal Requirements: When required by law or to protect our rights and safety\",\"Business Transfers: In connection with any merger, sale of assets, or acquisition\"]},\"security\":{\"heading\":\"Data Security\",\"p1\":\"We implement appropriate technical and organizational security measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. This includes encryption of sensitive data, secure API endpoints, and regular security audits.\"},\"retention\":{\"heading\":\"Data Retention\",\"p1\":\"We retain your personal information for as long as necessary to provide our Service and comply with legal obligations. When you delete your account, we will delete or anonymize your personal information within 30 days, except as required by law.\"},\"rights\":{\"heading\":\"Your Rights (GDPR)\",\"intro\":\"Under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and other applicable data protection laws, you have the following rights regarding your personal data:\",\"access\":{\"label\":\"Right of Access\",\"description\":\"You have the right to request a copy of the personal data we hold about you.\"},\"rectification\":{\"label\":\"Right to Rectification\",\"description\":\"You have the right to request correction of inaccurate or incomplete personal data.\"},\"erasure\":{\"label\":\"Right to Erasure\",\"description\":\"You have the right to request deletion of your personal data (\\\"right to be forgotten\\\") in certain circumstances.\"},\"restriction\":{\"label\":\"Right to Restriction\",\"description\":\"You have the right to request restriction of processing of your personal data in certain circumstances.\"},\"portability\":{\"label\":\"Right to Data Portability\",\"description\":\"You have the right to receive your personal data in a structured, commonly used format and to transmit it to another controller.\"},\"objection\":{\"label\":\"Right to Object\",\"description\":\"You have the right to object to processing of your personal data based on legitimate interests or for direct marketing purposes.\"},\"withdrawal\":{\"label\":\"Right to Withdraw Consent\",\"description\":\"Where processing is based on consent, you have the right to withdraw your consent at any time without affecting the lawfulness of prior processing.\"},\"howToExercise\":\"We will respond to your request within 30 days as required by GDPR. We may need to verify your identity before processing your request.\",\"contactUs\":\"To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at\",\"orUseForm\":\"or use the form below:\",\"items\":[\"Access: Request access to your personal information\",\"Correction: Request correction of inaccurate information\",\"Deletion: Request deletion of your personal information\",\"Portability: Request transfer of your data to another service\",\"Withdrawal: Withdraw consent for data processing\"],\"p1\":\"You can revoke our Service's access to your data via the Google security settings page at https://security.google.com/settings/security/permissions. This allows you to manage and revoke access to your YouTube and other Google account data.\",\"p2\":\"To request deletion of your stored data or to exercise your other rights, please contact us at:\",\"contactSentence\":\"To exercise these rights, please contact us at:\"},\"cookies\":{\"heading\":\"Cookies and Tracking Technologies\",\"p1\":\"We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your experience, analyze usage patterns, and maintain user sessions. You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings, though this may affect Service functionality.\"},\"children\":{\"heading\":\"Children's Privacy\",\"p1\":\"Our Service is not intended for individuals under 18 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you become aware that a child has provided us with personal information, please contact us immediately.\"},\"transfers\":{\"heading\":\"International Data Transfers\",\"p1\":\"Your information may be transferred to and processed in countries other than your own. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place to protect your personal information in accordance with applicable data protection laws.\"},\"changes\":{\"heading\":\"Changes to This Privacy Policy\",\"p1\":\"We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any material changes by email and by posting the updated policy on our website. Your continued use of the Service after such modifications constitutes acceptance of the updated Privacy Policy.\"},\"contact\":{\"heading\":\"Contact Information\",\"intro\":\"If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:\",\"p1\":\"If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:\",\"emailLabel\":\"Email\",\"websiteLabel\":\"Website\"}},\"dataRequestForm\":{\"title\":\"Submit a Data Subject Request\",\"description\":\"Use this form to exercise your data protection rights. We will respond to your request within 30 days.\",\"emailLabel\":\"Email Address\",\"emailPlaceholder\":\"your@email.com\",\"nameLabel\":\"Full Name (optional)\",\"namePlaceholder\":\"Your name\",\"requestTypeLabel\":\"Request Type\",\"detailsLabel\":\"Additional Details (optional)\",\"detailsPlaceholder\":\"Please provide any additional information that may help us process your request...\",\"submitButton\":\"Submit Request\",\"submitting\":\"Submitting...\",\"successMessage\":\"Your request has been submitted successfully. You will receive a confirmation email shortly. We will respond to your request within 30 days.\",\"errorMessage\":\"Failed to submit request. Please try again or contact support.\",\"requestTypes\":{\"access\":\"Data Access Request\",\"deletion\":\"Data Deletion Request\",\"rectification\":\"Data Rectification Request\",\"portability\":\"Data Portability Request\",\"restriction\":\"Processing Restriction Request\",\"objection\":\"Processing Objection Request\"}}},\"tosPage\":{\"metadata\":{\"title\":\"Terms of Service - Zernio\",\"description\":\"Zernio's terms of service. Read our terms and conditions for using our API.\"},\"title\":\"Terms of Service\",\"lastUpdated\":\"Last updated\",\"sections\":{\"agreement\":{\"heading\":\"1. Agreement to Terms\",\"p1\":\"By accessing and using {appName} (the \\\"Service\\\"), available at {domain}, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service (\\\"Terms\\\"). If you disagree with any part of these terms, then you may not access the Service.\",\"operatedBy\":\"The Service is operated by:\",\"p2\":\"By using our Service to interact with YouTube, you agree to be bound by the YouTube Terms of Service, available at https://www.youtube.com/t/terms.\",\"p3\":\"If you disagree with any part of these terms, then you may not access the Service.\",\"impressumNote\":\"For company identification details (Impressum), please see our Legal Disclosure.\"},\"description\":{\"heading\":\"2. Description of Service\",\"p1\":\"{appName} provides a social media scheduling API for developers, enabling you to schedule posts across multiple platforms including TikTok, Instagram, Facebook, YouTube, LinkedIn, Twitter/X, and Threads through our REST API.\"},\"apiUsage\":{\"heading\":\"3. API Usage and Limits\",\"p1\":\"Your use of our API is subject to rate limits and usage quotas based on your subscription plan. You agree not to exceed these limits or attempt to circumvent them. Abuse of the API may result in immediate suspension of your account.\"},\"billing\":{\"heading\":\"4. Payment and Billing\",\"p1\":\"Fees are usage-based. At the end of each billing period, you are charged for the social accounts and usage from that period. Because billing reflects actual usage, fees are non-refundable except as required by law. If you believe a charge resulted from a billing error or service outage on our side, contact us and we'll review it on a case-by-case basis. You may stop incurring charges at any time by disconnecting accounts or canceling your subscription through your account dashboard.\"},\"privacy\":{\"heading\":\"5. Data and Privacy\",\"p1\":\"We collect and process personal data including your name, email, and payment information to provide our services. For detailed information about how we handle your data, please refer to our Privacy Policy.\",\"linkText\":\"Privacy Policy\"},\"acceptableUse\":{\"heading\":\"6. Acceptable Use\",\"p1\":\"You agree to use our Service only for lawful purposes and in accordance with these Terms. You may not use the Service to post content that is illegal, harmful, threatening, abusive, harassing, defamatory, or otherwise objectionable.\"},\"ip\":{\"heading\":\"7. Intellectual Property\",\"p1\":\"The Service and its original content, features, and functionality are and will remain the exclusive property of {appName} and its licensors. The Service is protected by copyright, trademark, and other laws.\"},\"termination\":{\"heading\":\"8. Termination\",\"p1\":\"We may terminate or suspend your account and bar access to the Service immediately, without prior notice or liability, for any reason whatsoever, including without limitation if you breach the Terms.\"},\"disclaimer\":{\"heading\":\"9. Disclaimer\",\"p1\":\"The information on this Service is provided on an \\\"as is\\\" basis. To the fullest extent permitted by law, {appName} excludes all representations, warranties, conditions and other terms which might otherwise be implied by statute, common law or the law of equity.\"},\"governingLaw\":{\"heading\":\"10. Governing Law\",\"p1\":\"These Terms shall be interpreted and governed by the laws of Spain. Any disputes arising from these Terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the Spanish courts.\"},\"changes\":{\"heading\":\"11. Changes to Terms\",\"p1\":\"We reserve the right to modify or replace these Terms at any time. If a revision is material, we will provide at least 30 days notice prior to any new terms taking effect.\"},\"contact\":{\"heading\":\"12. Contact Information\",\"p1\":\"If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:\",\"emailLabel\":\"Email\"}}},\"contentGuidelinesPage\":{\"metadata\":{\"title\":\"Content Guidelines - Zernio\",\"description\":\"Content guidelines and acceptable use policy for Zernio. Learn what content is allowed on our platform.\"},\"title\":\"Content Guidelines\",\"lastUpdated\":\"Last updated\",\"sections\":{\"overview\":{\"heading\":\"Overview\",\"p1\":\"{appName} is a social media scheduling platform designed to help users manage and publish content across multiple platforms. To maintain a safe, productive environment and comply with platform policies, we require all users to follow these content guidelines.\"},\"prohibited\":{\"heading\":\"Prohibited Content \u0026 Activities\",\"spam\":{\"heading\":\"1. Spam \u0026 Abusive Behavior\",\"intro\":\"Users are strictly prohibited from:\",\"duplicate\":{\"title\":\"Posting duplicate or substantially similar content\",\"description\":\"Repeatedly posting identical or near-identical content across multiple accounts or platforms\"},\"massPosting\":{\"title\":\"Mass posting\",\"description\":\"Publishing identical or near-identical content in rapid succession\"},\"automated\":{\"title\":\"Automated spam behavior\",\"description\":\"Including but not limited to:\",\"examples\":{\"unrelated\":\"Publishing the same content to unrelated or inappropriate channels\",\"engagement\":\"Using our service to artificially inflate engagement metrics\",\"flooding\":\"Flooding platforms with repetitive messaging\"}},\"promotional\":{\"title\":\"Promotional spam\",\"description\":\"Unsolicited advertisements, affiliate links, or commercial content posted excessively\"},\"linkSpam\":{\"title\":\"Link spam\",\"description\":\"Including shortened links that redirect to unrelated content\"},\"engagementBait\":{\"title\":\"Engagement bait\",\"description\":\"Content designed solely to manipulate platform algorithms\"}},\"harmful\":{\"heading\":\"2. Illegal or Harmful Content\",\"intro\":\"You may not use {appName} to post content that is:\",\"items\":{\"illegal\":\"Illegal under applicable laws\",\"threatening\":\"Threatening, abusive, or harassing toward any individual or group\",\"defamatory\":\"Defamatory, libelous, or fraudulent\",\"malware\":\"Contains malware, viruses, or other harmful code\",\"ip\":\"Violates intellectual property rights of others\",\"exploitation\":\"Involves child exploitation or endangerment\",\"violence\":\"Promotes violence or self-harm\"}},\"platformViolations\":{\"heading\":\"3. Platform Terms Violations\",\"intro\":\"Users must comply with the Terms of Service of all connected social media platforms, including but not limited to:\",\"note\":\"{appName} will not facilitate content that violates these platform policies.\"}},\"acceptable\":{\"heading\":\"Acceptable Use Guidelines\",\"encouraged\":{\"heading\":\"Encouraged Use\",\"items\":{\"authentic\":{\"title\":\"Authentic content\",\"description\":\"Content that provides value to your audience\"},\"scheduled\":{\"title\":\"Scheduled posting\",\"description\":\"Maintain consistent presence across platforms\"},\"customization\":{\"title\":\"Platform-specific customization\",\"description\":\"Optimize content for each channel\"},\"professional\":{\"title\":\"Professional use\",\"description\":\"Business communication and marketing\"},\"creative\":{\"title\":\"Creative content\",\"description\":\"Content that respects copyright and platform guidelines\"}}},\"bestPractices\":{\"heading\":\"Best Practices\",\"items\":{\"vary\":{\"title\":\"Vary your content\",\"description\":\"Avoid posting identical messages repeatedly\"},\"rateLimits\":{\"title\":\"Respect rate limits\",\"description\":\"Don't overwhelm your audience with excessive posts\"},\"customize\":{\"title\":\"Customize for platforms\",\"description\":\"Adapt content appropriately for each social network\"},\"engage\":{\"title\":\"Engage authentically\",\"description\":\"Use {appName} to facilitate genuine communication\"},\"copyright\":{\"title\":\"Respect copyright\",\"description\":\"Only post content you have rights to use\"}}}},\"enforcement\":{\"heading\":\"Enforcement \u0026 Actions\",\"intro\":\"We use a tiered enforcement approach. For API users with multiple profiles, violations are first enforced at the profile level. Account-level actions are reserved for severe or systematic abuse.\",\"profileLevel\":{\"heading\":\"Profile-Level Enforcement\",\"intro\":\"When a specific profile violates our guidelines:\",\"items\":{\"first\":\"First Violation: Warning notification with specific violation details\",\"second\":\"Second Violation: Temporary profile suspension (7-30 days)\",\"third\":\"Third Violation: Permanent profile termination\"},\"consequences\":{\"intro\":\"When a profile is suspended:\",\"scheduled\":\"Scheduled posts for that profile are paused\",\"posting\":\"Posting to that profile is disabled\",\"other\":\"Other profiles on your account remain unaffected\",\"data\":\"Profile data is preserved for the suspension period\"}},\"accountLevel\":{\"heading\":\"Account-Level Enforcement\",\"intro\":\"Account-level actions are reserved for severe cases:\",\"items\":{\"systematic\":\"Systematic abuse across multiple profiles\",\"illegal\":\"Posting illegal content\",\"coordinated\":\"Coordinated inauthentic behavior\",\"security\":\"Activity that threatens the security of our service or users\",\"repeated\":\"Repeated creation of violating profiles after previous terminations\"}},\"immediate\":{\"heading\":\"Immediate Suspension\",\"intro\":\"The following may result in immediate suspension without warning:\",\"items\":{\"severe\":\"Severe spam activity affecting platform reputation\",\"illegal\":\"Posting illegal content\",\"coordinated\":\"Coordinated inauthentic behavior\",\"deliberate\":\"Deliberate Terms of Service violations after previous warnings\",\"security\":\"Activity that threatens the security of our service or users\"}},\"suspension\":{\"heading\":\"Account Suspension\",\"intro\":\"When an account is suspended:\",\"consequences\":{\"scheduled\":\"All scheduled posts are paused\",\"api\":\"API access is revoked\",\"accounts\":\"Connected social accounts are disconnected\",\"data\":\"Account data is preserved for the suspension period\"}},\"termination\":{\"heading\":\"Account Termination\",\"intro\":\"Permanent termination results in:\",\"consequences\":{\"access\":\"Complete loss of account access\",\"deletion\":\"Deletion of all scheduled posts\",\"refund\":\"No refund for active subscriptions\",\"prohibition\":\"Prohibition from creating new accounts\"}}},\"appeals\":{\"heading\":\"Appeals Process\",\"intro\":\"If you believe your account was suspended or terminated in error:\",\"steps\":{\"email\":\"Email\",\"include\":\"with:\",\"details\":{\"account\":\"Your account email and user ID\",\"explanation\":\"Detailed explanation of why you believe the action was incorrect\",\"evidence\":\"Any supporting evidence or context\"},\"review\":\"Appeals will be reviewed within 3-5 business days\",\"final\":\"Our decision after appeal review is final\"}},\"recovery\":{\"heading\":\"Account Recovery\",\"intro\":\"For users whose accounts are temporarily suspended:\",\"steps\":{\"review\":\"Review these Content Guidelines thoroughly\",\"delete\":\"Delete or modify any violating scheduled content\",\"contact\":\"Contact\",\"request\":\"to request reinstatement\",\"demonstrate\":\"Demonstrate understanding of the violation and commitment to compliance\"},\"note\":\"Note: Recovery is not guaranteed and depends on the severity of the violation.\"},\"whyBlocked\":{\"heading\":\"Why Your Account Was Blocked\",\"intro\":\"If you received this document because your account was suspended for spam activity, this typically means:\",\"reasons\":{\"duplicate\":\"You posted identical or substantially similar content across multiple accounts or platforms repeatedly\",\"excessive\":\"You scheduled excessive duplicate content in violation of platform guidelines\",\"behavior\":\"You engaged in behavior that platforms identify as spam or inauthentic\",\"patterns\":\"Your posting patterns indicated automated abuse rather than authentic engagement\"}},\"reporting\":{\"heading\":\"Reporting Violations\",\"intro\":\"If you notice another user violating these guidelines:\",\"email\":\"Report to\",\"include\":\"Include\",\"details\":\"User information, violation type, and evidence if available\"},\"contact\":{\"heading\":\"Contact Us\",\"intro\":\"Questions about these guidelines?\"},\"footer\":{\"agreement\":\"By using {appName}, you agree to follow these Content Guidelines in addition to our\",\"tosLink\":\"Terms of Service\",\"and\":\"and\",\"privacyLink\":\"Privacy Policy\"}}},\"legalDisclosurePage\":{\"metadata\":{\"title\":\"Legal Disclosure - Zernio\",\"description\":\"Legal disclosure and imprint information for Zernio.\"},\"title\":\"Legal Disclosure\",\"lastUpdated\":\"Last updated\",\"sections\":{\"provider\":{\"heading\":\"Provider\"},\"contact\":{\"heading\":\"Contact\",\"emailLabel\":\"Email\",\"websiteLabel\":\"Website\"},\"notes\":{\"heading\":\"Notes\",\"body\":\"This page provides company identification information to support compliance with EU and local regulations (e.g., Impressum requirements). Additional registry or representative details will be added if provided.\"},\"related\":{\"heading\":\"Related\"}}},\"blogPage\":{\"metadata\":{\"title\":\"Social Media API Blog - Developer Tutorials \u0026 Automation Guides\",\"description\":\"Learn social media API development, automation best practices, and platform integration tutorials. Expert insights on Instagram, TikTok, Twitter, LinkedIn APIs and more.\",\"ogTitle\":\"Social Media API Blog - Developer Tutorials \u0026 Guides\",\"ogDescription\":\"Expert tutorials on social media API development, automation, and platform integrations. Learn from real-world examples and best practices.\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"Social Media API Blog\",\"description\":\"Tutorials, guides, and insights for developers building with social media APIs. Learn automation, integration patterns, and platform-specific tips.\"},\"categories\":{\"title\":\"Browse by Category\",\"allPosts\":\"All Posts\",\"openTitle\":\"Open blog categories\",\"articlesIn\":\"Articles in {category}\",\"otherCategories\":\"Other categories you might like\"},\"articles\":{\"readMore\":\"Read more\",\"publishedOn\":\"Published on\",\"author\":\"By\",\"relatedReading\":\"Related reading\",\"minuteRead\":\"min read\",\"tags\":\"Tags:\"},\"author\":{\"authors\":\"Authors\",\"authorAt\":\"Author at\",\"recentArticles\":\"Most recent articles by {author}\"},\"navigation\":{\"home\":\"Home\",\"blog\":\"Blog\",\"openMenu\":\"Open menu\",\"closeMenu\":\"Close menu\"},\"cta\":{\"bannerHeading\":\"One API. 15+ platforms.\",\"tryFree\":\"Get API Key\",\"bannerBody\":\"Ship social media features in minutes, not weeks.\",\"midHeading\":\"Build faster with Zernio\",\"midBody\":\"One API call to post everywhere. No OAuth headaches. No platform-specific code.\",\"midFoot\":\"Free tier • No credit card\",\"mobileText\":\"Post everywhere. One API.\"},\"footer\":{\"backToTop\":\"Back to top\"},\"pagination\":{\"previous\":\"Previous\",\"next\":\"Next\",\"pageOf\":\"Page {page} of {total}\"}},\"n8nTemplatesPage\":{\"metadata\":{\"title\":\"N8N Templates - Zernio | Ready-made Social Media Automation Workflows\",\"description\":\"Download ready-made N8N templates for social media automation using Zernio's API. Copy, customize, and deploy in minutes.\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"N8N Templates\",\"subtitle\":\"Ready-made automation workflows\",\"description\":\"Download and customize proven N8N workflows that integrate with Zernio's API for powerful social media automation.\",\"cta\":\"Browse Templates\"}},\"n8nTemplatesContent\":{\"heroBadge\":\"Community Templates\",\"heroTitle\":\"n8n Templates for Social Media Automation\",\"heroDescription\":\"Free workflow templates built by the community. Automate your social media across 15 platforms.\",\"heroEmphasis\":\"Copy, import, automate.\",\"ctas\":{\"browse\":\"Browse templates →\",\"submit\":\"Submit template\",\"getAccount\":\"Get Zernio account\"},\"stats\":{\"free\":\"Free\",\"freeNote\":\"all templates\",\"platforms\":\"platforms\",\"import\":\"import\",\"automation\":\"automation\"},\"howToTitle\":\"How to use templates\",\"how\":{\"step1Title\":\"1. Find template\",\"step1Desc\":\"Browse verified templates below for social media automation\",\"step2Title\":\"2. Import to n8n\",\"step2Desc\":\"Click template link → opens n8n.io → import to your workspace\",\"step3Title\":\"3. Add credentials\",\"step3Desc\":\"Get API key from dashboard → add to workflow → connect accounts\",\"step4Title\":\"4. Activate workflow\",\"step4Desc\":\"Turn on workflow → automation runs 24/7 → no manual work\"},\"ctaTitle\":\"Build your own template\",\"ctaSubtitle\":\"Submit your n8n workflow for social media automation and compete for $500\",\"ctaPrimary\":\"Join competition →\",\"ctaSecondary\":\"API docs\",\"templatesList\":{\"importTemplate\":\"Import template\",\"submitTemplate\":\"Submit template →\",\"submitFirstTemplate\":\"Submit first template →\",\"builtSomethingCool\":\"Built something cool?\",\"submitWorkflowDescription\":\"Submit your Zernio-powered n8n workflow. Compete for $500 and help the community automate better.\",\"noTemplatesMatch\":\"No templates match\",\"noTemplatesYet\":\"No templates submitted yet\"}},\"checkoutSuccessPage\":{\"metadata\":{\"title\":\"Payment Successful - Zernio | Welcome to Social Media API\",\"description\":\"Payment successful! Welcome to Zernio. Get your API key and start scheduling posts to 15 social media platforms.\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"Payment Successful!\",\"subtitle\":\"Welcome to Zernio\",\"description\":\"Your payment has been processed successfully. You now have access to Zernio's powerful social media scheduling API.\",\"cta\":\"Get Started\"},\"next